\id 1KI
\h 1 Ijeǧiden
\toc1 1 Ijeǧiden
\toc2 1 Ijeǧiden
\toc3 1 Ij.
\mt1 1 Ijeǧiden
\c 1
\s1 Suliman idweř d ajeǧid
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa ajeǧid Dawud iwsar u imɣar deg wussan. Ssduryen t s warruḍ \add maca\add* war t iřqif \add ɛad\add* řeḥmu.
\v 2 Nnan as imsexxaren nnes: “Ejj ad arzun i sidi inu ajeǧid ict n tebřiɣt d taɛzarect u ejj i-tt ad tbedd zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, ad dayes tᵉthilla. Ejj i-tt ad tᵉṭṭeṣ ɣar idmaren nnes, ḥima sidi inu ajeǧid, ad idweř iḥemma.”
\v 3 Arzun nitni di marra tammurt n Israil x ict n tebřiɣt dayes aẓri. Ufin Abicaj, Tacunamit, uca iwyen tt ɣar ujeǧid. \f ◼ \fr 1:3 \fk Tacunamit\ft - ict n temɣart zi Sunam niɣ zi Cunam, ict n tendint di temmurt n Issakar, ɣar ljanub n wedrar n Tabur, di ccamal n Israil. Qqaren as i tendint-a ɛawed ‘Culam’ u zi tendint-a i dd-teffeɣ tesřit i x neqqar deg wedlis ‘Izři x izřan’.\f*
\v 4 Tabřiɣt tuɣa dayes aẓri aṭṭas u nettat tᵉthilla dayes u tsexxar xas. Ajeǧid war tt issin ca. \f ◼ \fr 1:4 \fk war tt issin ca\ft - man aya ixs ad yini ‘war xas dd-yudef ca’.\f*
\m 
\v 5 Aduniya, mmis n Hajjit, ixs ad issuɛřa ixef nnes, inna: “Necc ad dewřeɣ d ajeǧid.” Netta iḍebbar ikarruten d imnayen uca izwaren xemsin n yeryazen s tazřa zzat i wudem nnes. \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt 2 Ṣm. 15:1\x*
\v 6 Babas tuɣa ɛemmarṣ war xas isseqseḥ \add x man aya\add* řami \add d as\add* inna: “Mayemmi i teggid aya?” Ɛawed Aduniya tuɣa ɣares ijj n waddud icna. Yemmas turuw t-i-dd awarni i Abcalum. \f ◼ \fr 1:6 \fk Yemmas\ft - ixs ad yini ‘Hajjit’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:6 \xt 1 Im. 3:2\x*
\v 7 Issiweř ak-d Yuwab, mmis n Ṣaruya, u ak-d Abyatar, akehhan, uca nitni wcin afus i Aduniya. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt 1 Ij. 2:22, 28\x*
\v 8 \add Maca\add* akehhan Ṣaduq d Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, d unabi Natan d Cimɛi d Riɛi uřa d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Dawud, war qqinen ca ixef nsen ɣar Aduniya.
\m 
\v 9 Aduniya iɣarṣ i wuǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin d řmař iṣeḥḥen ɣar weẓru n Zaḥifa wenni ɣar tařa n Rujil. Netta iɛarḍ marra aytmas, iḥenjiren n ujeǧid, u marra iryazen n Yahuda, imsexxaren n ujeǧid. \x ◘ \xo 1:9 \xt Yac. 15:7; 18:16\x*
\v 10 \add Maca\add* anabi Natan d Banaya d ayt n bu-teɣruḍt \add n Dawud\add* d umas Suliman, war ten iɛriḍ ca.
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* inna Natan i Bat-Cabaɛ, yemmas n Suliman, inna: “Ma war tesřid cem, aqa Aduniya, mmis n Hajjit, idweř d ajeǧid? Aqa Dawud, siditneɣ, war xas yargib?
\v 12 Xenni řexxu, as-dd, ejj ayi ad am wceɣ ccwar, ḥima ad tessnejmed tudart nnem d tudart n mmim Suliman.
\v 13 Uyur, adef ɣar ujeǧid Dawud, ini as: ‘\add A\add* sidi inu ajeǧid, ma war tejjuǧed i tayya nnec, tennid: S tidett, mmim Suliman ad yiři d ajeǧid awarni ayi u netta ad iqqim x řɛarc inu? Mayemmi \add idweř xenni\add* Aduniya d ajeǧid?’
\v 14 Xzar, umi cem dinni tessawařed \add ɛad\add* ak-d ujeǧid, ad adfeɣ uřa d necc ad kemmřeɣ awařen nnem.”
\m 
\v 15 Bat-Cabaɛ tudef ɣar ujeǧid deg wexxam n daxeř. Ajeǧid tuɣa iwsar aṭṭas u Abicaj, Tasunamit, tsexxar xas.
\v 16 Bat-Cabaɛ tuḍar, tbendeq i ujeǧid uca ajeǧid inna: “Min cem yuɣin?”
\v 17 Nettat tenna as: “\add A\add* sidi inu, cek tejjuǧed i tayya nnec ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnec: ‘S tidett, Suliman, mmim, ad yiři d ajeǧid awarni ayi u netta ad iqqim x řɛarc inu!
\v 18 Uca řexxu, xzar, Aduniya idweř d ajeǧid, u řexxu, sidi inu ajeǧid, cek war \add xas\add* tessargibed ca.
\v 19 Netta iɣarṣ i waṭṭas n ifunasen d řmař iṣeḥḥen d wuǧi u netta iɛarḍ x marra iḥenjiren n ujeǧid u x Abyatar, akehhan, u x Yuwab, akumandar n řɛeskar, \add maca\add* amsexxar nnec Suliman, war t iɛriḍ ca.
\v 20 Ɣarek cek, \add a\add* sidi inu ajeǧid, ɣarek cek xezzarent marra tiṭṭawin n Israil, ḥima cek ad asen tessecned man wen i ɣa iqqimen x řɛarc n sidi inu ajeǧid awarni as netta.
\v 21 Niɣ ad imsar, mařa sidi inu ajeǧid ad igg ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes, aqa necc d mmi Suliman \add ad ttwaḥesben\add* d ayt n řmuɛṣiyyet.’”
\m 
\v 22 U xzar, am tessawař nettat ɛad ak-d ujeǧid, yudef-dd anabi Natan.
\v 23 Xebbaren \add aya\add* i ujeǧid, nnan: “Xzar, aqa da anabi Natan.” Netta yusa-dd zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, ibendeq zzat i ujeǧid s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt.
\v 24 Inna Natan: “Sidi inu ajeǧid, ma tennid cek: ‘Aduniya ad yiři d ajeǧid awarni ayi u netta ad iqqim x řɛarc inu’?
\v 25 Maɣar netta ihwa ass-a u netta iɣarṣ i waṭṭas n ifunasen d řmař iṣeḥḥen d wuǧi u iɛarḍ x marra iḥenjiren n ujeǧid u x ikumandaren n řɛeskar u x ukehhan Abyatar. Xzar nitni ttᵉtten, sessen zzat i wudem nnes, qqaren: ‘Ad iddar ujeǧid Aduniya!’
\v 26 \add Maca\add* necc, necc wenni d amsexxar nnec, d ukehhan Ṣaduq d Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, d Suliman, amsexxar nnec, war d aneɣ iɛriḍ ca.
\v 27 Ma iffeɣ-dd wawař-a zi sidi inu ajeǧid? Ma \add xenni\add* war tessargibed ca amsexxar nnec, man wen i ɣa iqqimen x řɛarc n sidi inu ajeǧid awarni as?”
\b
\m 
\v 28 Ajeǧid Dawud iṭṭef deg wawař, inna: “Řaɣat ayi-dd x Bat-Cabaɛ!” Nettat tusa-dd ɣar zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, tbedd \add din\add* zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* ijjuǧ ujeǧid, inna: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, wenni ifekken řeɛmar inu zi marra řeḥṣaret,
\v 30 wah nican, am mammec d am jjuǧeɣ ɣar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, nniɣ: ‘Aqa mmim Suliman ad yiři d ajeǧid awarni ayi u netta ad iqqim x řɛarc inu deg wemcan inu!’, wah, ammu \add i-t\add* ɣa ggeɣ s tidett ass-a.”
\v 31 \add Xas uca\add* tuḍar Bat-Cabaɛ s uɣembub nnes ɣar temmurt, tbendeq i ujeǧid, tenna: “Ad iddar sidi inu, ajeǧid Dawud, i řebda!”
\m 
\v 32 Xas uca inna ujeǧid Dawud: “Řaɣat ayi-dd i ukehhan Ṣaduq d unabi Natan d Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ!” Uca nitni usin-dd zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.
\v 33 Inna asen ujeǧid: “Ksim imsexxaren n siditwem akidwem u ejj mmi Suliman ad iniy x usardun i ɣari \add iǧan\add* u sehwa t ɣar Jiḥun.
\v 34 Ejj akehhan Ṣaduq ak-d unabi Natan ad t idhen dinni d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Xenni\add* ad tsuḍem deg uyicc n icarri, ad tinim: ‘Tudart i Suliman!’
\v 35 Ittxeṣṣa ad tgeɛɛdem awarni as u netta ad dd-yas ad iqqim x řɛarc inu. Netta ad yiři d ajeǧid deg wemcan inu, \add maɣar\add* necc umureɣ as ḥima ad yiři d řḥakem x Israil u x Yahuda.”
\v 36 Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, yarra-dd x ujeǧid, inna: “Amin, ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n sidi inu ajeǧid!
\v 37 Am mammec tuɣa iǧa SIDI ak-d sidi inu ajeǧid, ammu i ɣa yiři Netta uřa ak-d Suliman. Iři Netta ad issemɣar \add ɛad\add* řɛarc nnes x řɛarc n sidi inu, ajeǧid Dawud!”
\m 
\v 38 \add Xenni\add* ihwa ukehhan Ṣaduq ak-d unabi Natan d Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, u ak-d iɛessasen n arrimet d ireqqasen n tazřa. Nitni ssenyen Suliman x usardun n ujeǧid Dawud u nedhen t ɣar Jiḥun.
\v 39 Akehhan Ṣaduq, iksi icc s zzect zeg uqiḍun uca idhen Suliman. Nitni suḍen deg uyicc n icarri u marra řgens inna: “Tudart i ujeǧid Suliman!” \x ◘ \xo 1:39 \xt 1 Ṣm. 20:24\x*
\v 40 Marra řgens igeɛɛed awarni as. Iwdan ṣeffaren di tzamarin u farḥen s ict n řefraḥet temɣar \add ařami\add* tfeǧeq temmurt s řḥess nsen. \f ◼ \fr 1:40 \fk Iwdan\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řgens’.\f*
\m 
\v 41 Isřa aya Aduniya ak-d marra inewjiwen nni ɣares \add iǧan\add*. Nitni tuɣa bḥřa mmunswen. Uřa d Yuwab isřa i usuḍi deg uyicc n icarri, inna: “Mana řḥess zi tendint ammu s zzhir aṭṭas?”
\v 42 \add Am\add* issawař netta ɛad, yusa-dd Yunatan, mmis n ukehhan Abyatar. Aduniya inna: “Adef-dd ɣar daxeř, minzi cek d ijj n weryaz imeḥḍen. Cek ad tawyeḍ \add nican\add* ijj n řexbar aṣebḥan.”
\v 43 Yunatan yarra-dd, inna i Aduniya: “S řemqřub, siditneɣ, ajeǧid Dawud, igga Suliman d ajeǧid.
\v 44 Ajeǧid issekk akides akehhan Ṣaduq d unabi Natan d Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, d iɛessasen n arrimet d ireqqasen n tazřa u ina ggin t ad iniy x usardun n ujeǧid.
\v 45 Akehhan Ṣaduq d unabi Natan dehnen t d ajeǧid di Jiḥun u ssenni geɛɛden s řefraḥet ařami tehweř tendint. Aya d řḥess i tesřim.
\v 46 Uřa d Suliman ittɣima x řɛarc n tgeldit.
\v 47 Uřa d imsexxaren n ujeǧid usin-dd, ḥima ad barken siditneɣ, ajeǧid Dawud, nnan: ‘Iři ad yarr AREBBI nnec isem n Suliman \add ɛad\add* icna x yisem nnec u ad yarr řɛarc nnes \add ɛad\add* imɣar x řɛarc nnec.’ \add Xas uca\add* ibendeq ujeǧid x tassut nnes.
\v 48 Ɛawed inna ujeǧid: ‘Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni iwcin ass-a ad iqqim \add ijjen\add* x řɛarc inu, \add umi\add* tiṭṭawin inu \add ɛad\add* zemmarent ad twařant \add aya\add*.’”
\m 
\v 49 Marra inewjiwen inni \add tuɣa iǧan\add* ɣar Aduniya nnxeřɛen, kkaren uca ffɣen, \add kuř\add* aryaz yuyur abrid nnes.
\v 50 Aduniya iggʷed zi Suliman. Netta ikkar, yuyur uca icebbar deg waccawen n uɛalṭar.
\v 51 Xebbaren man aya ɣar Suliman, nnan: “Xzar, Aduniya, iggʷed zeg ujeǧid Suliman, \add maɣar\add* aqa netta icebbar deg waccawen n uɛalṭar, iqqar: ‘Ejj ajeǧid Suliman ad ayi ijjaǧ ass-a, aqa netta war ineqq amsexxar nnes s ssif!’”
\v 52 Inna Suliman: “Mařa netta iban-dd d ijj n weryaz d amtiqqi, war xas iweṭṭi uřa d ijj n uzeṭṭu n ucuwwaf nnes, maca mařa ittwaf dayes tuɛeffna, ittxeṣṣa ad immet.”
\v 53 Ajeǧid Suliman issekk \add ca n ireqqasen\add* u nitni kessin t zeg uɛalṭar u netta yusa-dd, ibendeq zzat i ujeǧid Suliman. Inna as Suliman: “Ruḥ ɣar taddart nnec!”
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Awařen ineggura n Dawud i Suliman
\m 
\v 1 \add Umi\add* dd-udsen wussan n Dawud ad immet, iɛřem netta i mmis Suliman, inna:
\v 2 “Necc ad uyureɣ abrid n marra tammurt. Iři tmeḥḍed u iři d aryaz!
\v 3 Ḥḍa awekkeř n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, ḥima ad tuyured di tebridin nnes, maḥend ad tᵉṭṭfed di tweṣṣa nnes d řumurat nnes d lfarayiḍ nnes d cchadat nnes am mammec t yura di Ccariɛa n Musa, ḥima ad tegged s řeɛqeř di marra min ɣa tegged d mani ma i ɣa traḥed, \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Aɛwd. 17:18; 29:9; Yac. 1:7\x*
\v 4 ḥima ad ikemmeř SIDI awař nnes i xafi issiweř, \add umi\add* inna: ‘Mařa iḥenjiren nnec ad ḥḍan abrid nsen s wuř nsen marra u s řeɛmar nsen marra, ḥima ad uyuren s řaman zzat i wudem inu, \add xenni\add* war cek ittxeṣṣi weryaz x řɛarc n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 2:4 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12; Izhd. 132:12\x*
\m 
\v 5 Cek tessned ɛawed min i d ayi igga Yuwab, mmis n Ṣaruya, min igga netta i tnayen n ikumandaren n řɛeskarat n Israil, i Abnir, mmis n Nir, u i Ɛamasa, mmis n Yatir. Netta inɣa i-ten. Di \add řweqt n\add* řehna issizzeř idammen \add am di řweqt\add* n umenɣi uca \add am di řweqt\add* n umenɣi igga idammen ɣar webyas nnes i ɣares ɣar tejɛinna nnes uřa ɣar sandaliyat nnes nni x iḍaren nnes. \x ◘ \xo 2:5 \xt 2 Ṣm. 3:27; 20:10\x*
\v 6 Egg ɛlaḥsab tiɣit nnec u war ttejji acuwwaf nnes icaben ad ihwa ɣar řaxart di řehna.
\m 
\v 7 Scen tamexsiwt icewwaren i ayt n Barzillay zi Jilɛad. Nitni ad iřin jar inni i ɣa iccen zi ṭṭabřa nnec, maɣar ammu i dd-yusin ɣari umi arewřeɣ zzat i wudem n umac Abcalum. \x ◘ \xo 2:7 \xt 2 Ṣm. 17:27; 19:31\x*
\m 
\v 8 Xzar Cimɛi, mmis n Jira, zeg ayt nn Binyamin, zi Baxurim. uřa d netta akidek. Netta inɛeř ayi s ict n nneɛřet iqesḥen deg wass umi necc arewřeɣ ɣar Maḥanayim, maca immseřqa akidi ɣar L’Urdun u necc jjuǧeɣ as ɣar SIDI, nniɣ: ‘\add Ɣari\add* mařa ad cek nɣeɣ s ssif!’ \x ◘ \xo 2:8 \xt 2 Ṣm. 16:5; 19:19\x*
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, war t ḥeṣṣeb d amezdag, maɣar cek d ijj n weryaz d amiɣis u tessned min d as ɣa tegged, ḥima acuwwaf nnes icaben ad ihwa ɣar řaxart s idammen.”
\m 
\v 10 Dawud igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř di tendint n Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 2:10 \xt Řex. 2:29; 13:36\x*
\v 11 Ussan i di tuɣa iḥekkem Dawud x Israil, \add tuɣa aten\add* arebɛin n iseggʷusa. Sebɛa n iseggʷusa iḥkem di Ḥabrun u di Urcalim iḥkem třata u-třatin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt 1 Im. 29:27\x*
\b
\s1 Timegga timezwura n ujeǧid Suliman
\m 
\v 12 Suliman iqqim x řɛarc n babas Dawud u tagelda nnes tedweř tarenni di řemten aṭṭas. \x ◘ \xo 2:12 \xt 1 Im. 29:23; 2 Im. 1:1\x*
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* Aduniya, mmis n Hajjit, yusa-dd ɣar Bat-Cabaɛ, yemmas n Suliman. Nettat tenna: “Ma tawasit nnec s řehna?” Netta inna: “Řehna!”
\v 14 Netta inna: “Necc ɣari kim ijj n wawař.” Nettat tenna \add as\add*: “Siweř!”
\v 15 Inna netta: “Cem tessned, aqa tageldit tusa ayi-dd u marra Israil igga dayi tiṭṭawin, ḥima ad dewřeɣ d ajeǧid. \add Maca\add* tagelda tenneqřeb uca tedweř i uma, minzi tusa as-dd zi SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Im. 22:9; 28:5\x*
\v 16 Řexxu \add maca\add* xseɣ ad ɣarem ttareɣ ict n řḥajjet \add waha\add*. War d ayi tagi!” Nettat tenna: as: “Siweř!”
\v 17 Netta inna: “Siweř ak-d ujeǧid Suliman - maɣar netta war cem ittarri - \add ḥima\add* netta ad ayi iwc Abicaj, Tasunamit, d tamɣart.”
\v 18 Bat-Cabaɛ tenna: “Mliḥ, necc ad ssiwřeɣ ak-d ujeǧid di ṭṭweɛ nnec.”
\m 
\v 19 \add Xenni\add* tusa-dd Bat-Cabaɛ ɣar ujeǧid Suliman, ḥima akides tessiweř x Aduniya. Ajeǧid ikkar i umsagar akides, yuḍar zzates. \add Awarni man aya\add* iqqim x řɛarc, ijja ad \add din\add* ssarsen ijj n řkursi i yemmas n ujeǧid u nettat teqqim ɣar ufus afusi nnes.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* tenna \add as\add* nettat: “Necc xseɣ ad ac ttareɣ ict n řḥajjet \add waha\add*. War d ayi tagi!” Inna as ujeǧid: “Seqsa, yemma, necc war cem ttarriɣ ca.”
\v 21 Nettat tenna \add as\add*: “\add Ttzawgeɣ cek\add* ḥima ad temmewc Abicaj, Tasunamit, i umac Aduniya d tamɣart.”
\v 22 Ajeǧid Suliman yarra-dd \add xas\add*, inna i yemmas: “Mayemmi tᵉttared cem i Aduniya Abicaj, Tasunamit? Ttar \add xenni uřa d\add* tagelda, maɣar netta d uma wenni d ameqqran xafi, \add wah ttar i-tt\add* i netta u i ukehhan Abyatar d Yuwab, mmis n Ṣaruya.”
\m 
\v 23 Ajeǧid Suliman ijjuǧ ɣar SIDI, inna: “Ad ayi igg AREBBI ta d ta u \add ɛad\add* ktar zi man aya, maɣar Aduniya issiweř awař-a ḍidd i tudart nnes!
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add s tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, wenni d ayi issemtnen u wenni d ayi issɣiman x řɛarc n tgeldit n baba Dawud u wenni d ayi iggin ict n taddart am mammec tuɣa inna \add qbeř i baba Dawud\add*, s tidett, Aduniya ad ittwaneɣ ass-a!” \x ◘ \xo 2:24 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12, 13\x*
\v 25 Xas uca issekk ujeǧid Suliman \add řumur-a\add* s ufus n Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ. Wanita iwta i-t uca immut Aduniya.
\m 
\v 26 Inna ujeǧid i ukehhan Abyatar: “Uyur ɣar Ɛanatut, ɣar temmurt nnec, maɣar cek d ijj n weryaz \add isdaḥeǧ\add* řmewt. Ass-a maca war cek neqqeɣ ca, minzi cek tarbud Ttabut n Sidi inu, SIDI, zzat i wudem n baba Dawud, u minzi cek tweddbed uřa s marra i zi iweddeb baba.” \x ◘ \xo 2:26 \xt 1 Ṣm. 22:20-23; 2 Ṣm. 15:24\x*
\v 27 Suliman yuẓẓeř x Abyatar ařami netta war tuɣi ɛad d akehhan i SIDI, ḥima ad ittwakemmeř wawař n SIDI i tuɣa issiweř zi jjihet n taddart n Ɛali di Cilu. \x ◘ \xo 2:27 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:31-36\x*
\m 
\v 28 \add Umi\add* yiweḍ řexbar ɣar Yuwab - aqa Yuwab iffeɣ, iḍfar Aduniya, waxxa netta war dd-iffiɣ ca, ḥima ad iḍfar Abcalum - yarweř Yuwab ɣar Uqiḍun n SIDI uca iṭṭef accawen n uɛalṭar. \x ◘ \xo 2:28 \xt 1 Ij. 1:50\x*
\v 29 Xebbaren ajeǧid Suliman aqa Yuwab yarweř ɣar Uqiḍun n SIDI. U xzar, ibedd \add din\add* ɣar uɛalṭar. Suliman issekk \add ɣares\add* Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, inna: “Ruḥ \add din\add*, neɣ i-t!”
\v 30 Banaya yusa-dd ɣar Uqiḍun n SIDI uca inna as: “Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: ‘Ffeɣ-dd ɣar barra!’” Netta inna: “Lla, necc xseɣ ad mmteɣ da!” Banaya issiweḍ tamwarrit ɣar ujeǧid, inna: “Ammu i issiweř Yuwab u ammu xafi dd-yarra.”
\v 31 Inna as ujeǧid: “Egg min i d ac inna netta, ɣeḍř i-t uca neḍř i-t, ḥima ad taggʷejed xafi u x taddart n baba idammen i issizzeř Yuwab baṭeř.
\v 32 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa yarr SIDI idammen i issizzeř netta x uzeǧif nnes, minzi netta issḥeyyed tnayen n yeryazen, inni iseggden u iḥřan xas, uca inɣa i-ten s ssif umi baba Dawud war t issin: Abnir, mmis n Nir, akumandar n řɛeskar n Israil, u Ɛamasa, mmis n Yatir, akumandar n řɛeskar n Yahuda.
\v 33 \add Ammu\add* i ɣa ɛeqben idammen nsen x uzeǧif n Yuwab u x uzeǧif n tarwa nnes i řebda. \add Maca\add* Dawud d tarwa nnes d taddart nnes d řɛarc nnes, ad ɣarsen yiři řehna zi SIDI i řebda.”
\v 34 Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, igeɛɛed ɣar uɛalṭar, iwta i-t uca inɣa i-t. Netta ittwanḍeř di taddart nnes di řexřa.
\v 35 Ajeǧid igga \add xenni\add* Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, deg wemcan nnes x řɛeskar uca ajeǧid igga Ṣaduq, akehhan, deg wemcan n Abyatar. \x ◘ \xo 2:35 \xt 1 Ṣm. 2:35\x*
\m 
\v 36 \add Xenni\add* ijja ujeǧid ad řaɣan i Cimɛi, inna as: “Bna i yixef nnec ict n taddart di Urcalim uca zdeɣ din, war tteffeɣ ɣar da uřa ɣar diha!
\v 37 Ad imsar deg wass i di i ɣa teffɣed, ad teẓwid tiɣzart n Qidrun, aqa ad tessned nican ad temmted nhřa mma. Idammen nnec ad iřin x uzeǧif nnec.”
\v 38 Cimɛi yarra-dd x ujeǧid: “Awař-a d lemliḥ. Am mammec issiweř sidi inu ajeǧid, ammu i ɣa igg uřa d umsexxar nnec.” U Cimɛi tuɣa izeddeɣ aṭṭas n wussan di Urcalim.
\m 
\v 39 \add Maca\add* awarni i třata n iseggʷusa, imsar, aqa tnayen n imsexxaren n Cimɛi arewřen ɣar Axic, mmis n Maɛka, ajeǧid n Jat. Xebbaren aya i Cimɛi, nnan: “Xzar, imsexxaren nnec aqa aten di Jat.”
\v 40 \add Xenni\add* ikkar Cimɛi, ibardeɛ i weɣyuř nnes uca yuyur ɣar Axic ɣar Jat, ḥima ad yarzu x imsexxaren nnes. Cimɛi yuyur \add din\add* u yarra i-ten-dd zi Jat.
\v 41 Xebbaren aya i Suliman aqa Cimɛi iffeɣ zi Urcalim ɣar Jat uca iɛqeb-dd \add ɛawed\add*.
\v 42 Ajeǧid issekk ad řaɣan i Cimɛi uca inna as: “Ma war cek jjiɣ ad tejjaǧed ɣar SIDI u ɛeřmeɣ ac, nniɣ: ‘Deg wass i di i ɣa teffɣed ɣar da niɣ ɣar diha ad tessned nican, ad temmted nḥřa mma’? U cek tennid ayi: ‘Awař-a i sřiɣ, aqa-t mliḥ.’
\v 43 Mayemmi \add xenni\add* war teḥḍid ca tajaǧit n SIDI d řumur i d ac ggiɣ?”
\v 44 Inna ujeǧid ɛawed i Cimɛi: “Cek tessned deg wuř nnec marra tuɛeffna i teggid i baba Dawud. \add S uyenni\add* SIDI ad dd-yarr tuɛeffna nnec x uzeǧif nnec. \x ◘ \xo 2:44 \xt 2 Ṣm. 16:5, 6, 7\x*
\v 45 \add Maca\add* ad ittwabarek ujeǧid Suliman u řɛarc n Dawud ad ittwassemten i řebda zzat i wudem n SIDI.”
\v 46 \add Xas\add* uca iḍebbar ujeǧid x Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, u wanita yuyur ɣar barra, iwta Cimɛi ařami immut wanita. \add Ammu\add* i tᵉttwacedd tgeldit deg ufus n Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 2:46 \xt 2 Im. 1:1\x*
\b
\b
\c 3
\s1 Aḍhar amezwaru n SIDI i Suliman d tutra nnes
\m 
\v 1 Suliman idweř d aḍeggʷař n firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra. Netta yiwi yeǧis n firɛun uca issidif i-tt ɣar tendint n Dawud, ařami tuɣa isseqfeř řebni n taddart nnes d Taddart n SIDI d řḥiḍ i d as dd-innḍen i Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 3:1 \xt [2 Im. 1:1-12] — 1 Ij. 7:8\x*
\v 2 Mɣir řgens yarni ittqeddam tiɣarṣa x řegɛudi waha, minzi ař ussan nni war tᵉttwabenni ɛad Taddart i Yisem n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 3:2 \xt Aɛwd. 12:5\x*
\v 3 Suliman tuɣa ittexs SIDI umi yuyur ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa n babas Dawud. Iqeddem mɣir tiɣarṣa d řebxur x řegɛudi waha.
\m 
\v 4 \add Ammu i\add* yuyur ujeǧid \add ict n twařa\add* ɣar Jibɛun, ḥima ad dinni iɣarṣ, maɣar řgeɛɛdet nni tuɣa-tt d tameqqrant qaɛ. Issgeɛɛed Suliman x uɛalṭar nni ařef tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ. \x ◘ \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Im. 1:3\x*
\v 5 Iban-dd SIDI di Jibɛun s ǧiřet i Suliman deg ict n terjit, uca inna AREBBI: “Ttar! Min i d ac ɣa wceɣ?” \x ◘ \xo 3:5 \xt 1 Ij. 9:2\x*
\v 6 Inna Suliman:
\b
\m “Cek tessecned tamexsiwt icewwaren tameqqrant i umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud, am mammec yuyur netta zzat i wudem nnec s řaman d tsegda d řeṣfayet n wuř ɣarek, u Cek txemmřed as tamexsiwt-a icewwaren tameqqrant u tewcid as ijj n mmis, ḥima ad iqqim x řɛarc nnes, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a. \f ◼ \fr 3:6 \fk řkursi nnes igellden\ft - niɣ ‘lɛarc’ nnes (ijj n wawař ittwaksin zi Teɛrabt).\f*
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI inu, Cek teggid amsexxar nnec d ajeǧid deg wemcan n baba Dawud. \add Maca\add* necc \add ǧiɣ ɛad\add* d aḥenjir ameẓyan. Necc war ssineɣ mammec ɣa ffɣeɣ u mammec ɣa ɛeqbeɣ. \x ◘ \xo 3:7 \xt 2 Im. 2:7\x*
\v 8 Amsexxar nnec aqa-t di řwesṭ n řgens nnec nni tixḍared Cek, ijj n řgens imɣar ařami war izemmar ad ittwaqedd niɣ ad ittwaḥesseb zeg ubarru \add nnes ameqqran\add*. \x ◘ \xo 3:8 \xt 2 Im. 1:9\x*
\v 9 Ewc \add xenni\add* i umsexxar nnec ijj n wuř iften ḥima ad taf izemmar ad iḥkem di řgens u ḥima ad ifarz s řeɛqeř jar min iǧan icna d min iǧan d aɛeffan, minzi man wen izemmaren ad iḥkem x řgens-a ameqqran nnec?”
\b
\m 
\v 10 Awař-a tuɣa d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin n Sidi, řami zeɛma Suliman ittar man aya. \f ◼ \fr 3:10 \fk Sidi\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘Sidi inu’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 11 Inna as AREBBI:
\m “Minzi cek tᵉttared aya u war tᵉttared ca tudart tazirart i yixef nnec, u war tᵉttared agřa i yixef nnec u war tᵉttared ca tudart n řɛedyan nnec, \add maca\add* tᵉttared i yixef nnec řeɛqeř, ḥima ad tesřed \add mliḥ\add* ddeɛwat \add di řmeḥkama\add*, \x ◘ \xo 3:11 \xt 2 Im. 1:11\x*
\v 12 aqa \add s uya\add* Necc ggiɣ ɛlaḥṣab awařen nnec. Xzar, Necc wciɣ ac ijj n wuř d amiɣis d afehham, am mammec war tuɣi qbeř i cek u war ittiři awarni ac. \x ◘ \xo 3:12 \xt Amb. 1:16\x*
\v 13 Uřa d min war tᵉttared, ad ac t wceɣ, am wagřa am uɛuǧi, ařami marra ussan \add n tudart\add* nnec war \add din\add* ittiři weryaz am cek jar ijeǧiden. \x ◘ \xo 3:13 \xt Mt. 6:33; Afa. 3:20\x*
\v 14 Mařa cek tuyured x tebridin inu ařami ɣa teḥḍid tiweṣṣa inu d řumurat inu, am mammec yuyur babac Dawud, \add xenni\add* Necc ad sszuggareɣ \add řqedd n\add* wussan \add n tudart\add* nnec.”
\b
\m 
\v 15 Ifaq-dd Suliman, u xzar, \add tuɣa-tt d\add* ict n terjit. Netta yusa-dd ɣar Urcalim uca ibedd zzat i Ttabut n Řɛahd n Sidi u issgeɛɛed tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ u igga tiwhibin n řehna u issewjed \add ɛawed\add* ict n zzardet i marra imsexxaren nnes.
\b
\s1 Řeḥkam amiɣis n Suliman
\m 
\v 16 Xenni usint-i-dd tnayen n temɣarin ɣar ujeǧid. Tuɣa-tent d timɣarin n farq-ccɣeř, beddent zzat i wudem nnes.
\v 17 Ict n temɣart tenna: “Mařa texsed, \add a\add* sidi inu, necc zeddɣeɣ ak-d temɣart-a di taddart d ict, u necc urweɣ \add umi d ayi tuɣa\add* ɣares di taddart.
\v 18 Deg wass wiss třata awarni řami dd-urweɣ, imsar, aqa uřa d tamɣart-a turuw-dd \add ijj n uḥenjir\add*. Neccin tuɣa nmun, war tuɣi ɣarneɣ uřa d ijj n ubarrani di taddart, mɣir neccin s tnayen di taddart.
\v 19 Aḥenjir n temɣart-a immut di ǧiřet umi tezzeř xas deg iḍeṣ.
\v 20 Nettat tekkar ɣar wezyen n ǧiřet, tekkes ayi aḥenjir inu, umi tayya nnec tᵉṭṭeṣ, u tessars i-t deg weḥsin nnes uca mmis immuten tessars i-t deg weḥsin inu.
\v 21 \add Umi\add* kkareɣ ɣar tuffut, ḥima ad ssuṭṭuḍeɣ aḥenjir inu, xzar, netta immut. Di ṣṣbeḥ tuɣa ayi xezzareɣ mliḥ, ẓriɣ tuɣa-t war iǧi ca d aḥenjir inu nni dd-urweɣ.”
\v 22 \add Xas\add* uca tenna temɣart nneɣnit: “Lla, wenni iddaren d aḥenjir inu u wenni immuten d aḥenjir nnem!” Tenneɣnit tenna: “Lla, wenni immuten d aḥenjir nnem u wenni iddaren d aḥenjir inu!” Ammu i ssiwřent zzat i wudem n ujeǧid.
\m 
\v 23 Inna ujeǧid: “Tanita teqqar: ‘Wenni iddaren d aḥenjir inu u wenni immuten d aḥenjir nnem!’, uca wenneɣni teqqar: ‘Lla, wenni immuten d aḥenjir nnem u wenni iddaren d aḥenjir inu.’”
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid: “Awyem ayi-dd ijj n ssif!” Nitni iwyen ijj n ssif ɣar ujeǧid. \f ◼ \fr 3:24 \fk ɣar ujeǧid\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i wudem n ujeǧid’.\f*
\v 25 Ajeǧid inna: “Qessem aḥenjir iddaren x tnayen uca wcem ijj n wezyen i yicten \add zzaysent\add* u wcem i \add tᵉnneɣnit\add* ijj n wezyen \add nneɣni\add*.”
\v 26 \add Maca\add* řami tuɣa tacit nnes i uḥenjir nnes imɣar, tessiweř temɣart tenni ɣar iǧa uḥenjir iddar, ak-d ujeǧid, tenna: “A, sidi inu, wcet as aḥenjir nni iddaren mařa texsed, war t neqqet!” Tanita maca tenna: “War ittiři inu uřa nnem. Qesset t di řwesṭ!”
\v 27 \add Xenni\add* yarra-dd ujeǧid, inna: “Wcem as aḥenjir iddaren! War t neqqem. Nettat d yemmas.”
\v 28 Marra Israil isřa x řeḥkam i zi iḥkem ujeǧid u nitni ggʷeden zzat i wudem n ujeǧid, minzi nitni ẓrin belli tiɣit n AREBBI dayes ḥima ad yaɣ tasɣart.
\b
\b
\c 4
\s1 Řḥukkam imeqqranen n Suliman d řwulat nnes
\m 
\v 1 Tuɣa ajeǧid Suliman d ajeǧid x marra Israil.
\m 
\v 2 Ina tuɣa d řḥukkam nnes imeqqranen:
\m Ɛazarya, mmis n Ṣaduq, \add tuɣa-t d\add* akehhan d amezwaru.
\m 
\v 3 Iliḥuraf d Axiya, iḥenjiren n Cica, \add tuɣa aten d\add* imariren.
\m Yaḥucafaṭ, mmis n Axilud, tuɣa-t d amarir amezwaru. \f ◼ \fr 4:3 \fk amarir - imariren\ft - inni zemmaren x tira n řectub d umezruy.\f*
\m 
\v 4 Banaya, mmis n Yahuyadaɛ, \add tuɣa-t\add* x řɛeskar.
\m Ṣaduq d Abyatar \add tuɣa aten d\add* ikehhanen.
\m 
\v 5 Ɛazarya, mmis n Natan, \add tuɣa-t\add* x řwulat.
\m Zabud, mmis n Natan, \add tuɣa-t d\add* akehhan d ameddukkeř n ujeǧid.
\m 
\v 6 Axicar \add tuɣa-t\add* x tzeddiɣt n ujeǧid.
\m Aduniram, mmis n Abda \add tuɣa-t\add* x ljizya. \x ◘ \xo 4:6 \xt 1 Ij. 12:18\x*
\b
\m 
\v 7 Suliman ɣares tenɛac n řwulat x marra Israil, inni ibedden x řeɛweč n ujeǧid d taddart nnes. X \add kuř\add* ijj s uyur nnes deg useggʷas, tuɣa xas ad t iksi.
\v 8 Ina d ismawen nsen:
\b
\m Mmis n Ḥur x idurar n Ifrayim.
\m 
\v 9 Mmis n Daqar di Maqas u di Caɛalubbim, Bayt-Cams d Ilun-Bayt-Ḥanan.
\m 
\v 10 Mmis n Ḥasad di Arubut. Netta \add tuɣa\add* ɣares Suku d marra tammurt n Ḥafir.
\m 
\v 11 Mmis n Abinadab \add ɣares\add* marra tiwririn n Dur. Tafat, yeǧis n Suliman, \add tuɣa-tt\add* ɣares d tamɣart.
\m 
\v 12 Baɛna, mmis n Axilud, \add ɣares\add* Taɛnak, Majiddu d marra Bayt-Can i iǧan ɣar Ṣurtan, swadday n Yazraɛil, zi Bayt-Can ař Abal-Maḥula, ař uɣezdis nneɣni n Yuqmaɛam.
\m 
\v 13 Mmis n Jabar \add tuɣa\add* di Ramut-Jilɛad. Netta ɣares dcurat n Ya’ir, mmis n Manassa, tinni \add iǧan\add* di Jilɛad. \add Tuɣa\add* ɣares uřa d jjihet n Arjub, tenni di Bacan, settin n tineddam mɣarent s řḥiḍ u s weɛmud n nnḥas.
\m 
\v 14 Axinadab, mmis n Ɛiddu, \add ɣares\add* Maḥanayim.
\m 
\v 15 Aximaɛaṣ \add tuɣa-t d lwali\add* di Naftali. Netta yiwi uřa Basimat, yeǧis n Suliman, d tamɣart \add nnes\add*.
\m 
\v 16 Baɛna, mmis n Hucai, \add tuɣa-t d lwali\add* di Acir u di Baɛalut.
\m 
\v 17 Yahucafaṭ, mmis n Faruḥ, \add tuɣa-t d lwali\add* di Issakar.
\m 
\v 18 Cimɛi, mmis n Iyla, \add tuɣa-t d lwali\add* di Binyamin.
\m 
\v 19 Jabar, mmis n Uri, \add tuɣa-t d lwali\add* di temmurt n Jilɛad, tammurt n Siḥun, ajeǧid n Imuriyyen, u n Ɛuj, ajeǧid n Bacan. Netta \add tuɣa\add* d ayenni n lwali di temmurt nni.
\b
\m 
\v 20 \add Tuɣa řgens n\add* Yahuda d Israil s waṭṭas am yijdi ɣar \add tma n\add* řebḥar, ammu aṭṭas. Nitni ccin, swin u farḥen.
\b
\b
\c 5
\s1 Řemɣaret n Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Suliman iḥkem x marra tigeldiwin zeg iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add* ař tammurt n Ifilisṭiniyyen u ař aymir n Miṣra. Nitni tuɣa ttawyen tarzifin u sexxaren i Suliman, marra ussan n tudart nnes.
\v 2 Asuniy n Suliman i yijj n wass tuɣa-t třatin ikuruten n waren azdad u settin ikuruten n waren,
\v 3 ɛecra n ifunasen iṣeḥḥen, ɛicrin n ifunasen n heddu d mya n wuǧi, ahta i udaden, iɣayḍen n wezɣar, waccawen imeqqranen d iweẓẓiwen n řexřa. \f ◼ \fr 5:3 \fk iweẓẓiwen n řexřa\ft - ict n marka n ijḍaḍ am ‘iyaẓiden’.\f*
\v 4 Ammu i tuɣa iḥekkem x marra \add tammurt\add* x tma-ya n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, zi Tifsax ař Ɣazza, x marra ijeǧiden x tma-ya n iɣzar uca idweř as řehna ɣar marra jjwayeh i d as dd-innḍen.
\v 5 Yahuda d Israil tuɣa zeddɣen di řaman, kuř ijj sadu tzayart nnes u sadu wartu nnes, zi Dan ař Bi’r-Sebɛa, marra ussan n Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 5:5 \xt Lawi 26:5; Mixa 4:4; Zak. 3:10\x*
\m 
\v 6 Suliman tuɣa ɣares arebɛin-ařef n řkurit n yeysan i ikarruten nnes \add n umenɣi\add* u tenɛac-ařef n imnayen. \f ◼ \fr 5:6 \fk amnay - imnayen\ft - aryaz wenni inyin x ijj n uyis.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:6 \xt 1 Ij. 10:26; 2 Im. 1:14; 9:25\x*
\v 7 Lwulat-a, kuř ijj deg uyur nnes, tthillan deg ujeǧid Suliman u di marra inni tuɣa dd-ittasen ɣar ṭṭabřa n ujeǧid Suliman. Nitni war jjin ad ixeṣṣ walu.
\v 8 Imendi d uřum i iysan u i iysan n tazřa ttawyen ten ɣar wemcan mani ma iǧa, kuř ijj am mammec awekkeř nnes.
\m 
\v 9 SIDI iwca i Suliman tiɣit d řeɛqeř s waṭṭas uřa d ttasiɛ \add n tussna\add* deg wuř am yijdi ɣar tma n řebḥar.
\v 10 Tiɣit n Suliman tuɣa d tameqqrant x tiɣit n marra tarwa n manis i dd-tneqqar tfuct u x marra tiɣit n Imiṣriyyen.
\v 11 Netta tuɣa d amiɣis x marra iwdan, x Itan, Azraḥi, x Hayman, Kalkul d Dardaɛ, iḥenjiren n Maḥul. Isem nnes idweř \add ittwassnen\add* ɣar marra řegnus i d as dd-innḍen.
\v 12 Netta issiweř teřt-ařaf n wawařen iweznen. Ařef u-xemsa n izřan tuɣa aten zzayes.
\v 13 Netta issiweř \add ɛawed\add* x tcejjura, zi \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan ař tɛelǧet i dd-iɣemmyen zi řḥiḍ. Netta issiweř \add ɛawed\add* x řmař, x ijḍaḍ, x marra imuddaren inni ittbuɛen u x iseřman. \f ◼ \fr 5:13 \fk tɛelǧet\ft - niɣ ‘hisup’.\f*
\v 14 Zi marra řegnus usin-dd \add iwdan\add*, ḥima ad sřen tiɣit n Suliman, zi marra ijeǧiden n temmurt inni tuɣa isřan x tiɣit nnes.
\b
\s1 Asewjed n Suliman i řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 15 Ḥiram, ajeǧid n Ṣur, issekk imsexxaren nnes ɣar Suliman, maɣar netta tuɣa isřa, aqa dehnen Suliman d ajeǧid deg wemcan n babas. Iwa Ḥiram tuɣa řebda ittexs Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 5:15 \xt [2 Im. 2:1-17] — 2 Ṣm. 5:11; 1 Im. 14:1\x*
\v 16 Suliman ijja ad inin i Ḥiram:
\v 17 “Cek tessned aqa baba Dawud tuɣa war izemmar ad ibna ict n Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI nnes, zi ssibbet n imenɣan i zi i d as dd-innḍen nitni, ařami ten igga SIDI sadu iḍaren nnes. \f ◼ \fr 5:17 \fk sadu iḍaren\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘sadu aḍar nnes’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 5:17 \xt 1 Im. 28:3\x*
\v 18 \add Maca\add* řexxu iwca ayi SIDI, AREBBI inu, řehna zi marra iɣezdisen. War \add din\add* iǧi \add ɛad\add* bu weɣrim u war \add din ɛad\add* asiggʷed n tuɛeffna.
\v 19 Xzar, necc nwiɣ ad bniɣ ict n Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI inu, am mammec issiweř SIDI i baba Dawud, inna: ‘Mmic, wenni i ɣa ssɣimeɣ x řɛarc nnec, ad ibna ict n Taddart i Yisem inu.’ \x ◘ \xo 5:19 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:13; 1 Im. 22:10; 2 Im. 1:18\x*
\v 20 Umur \add xenni\add* řexxu, aqa ad ayi zedmen ticejjura n tengelt zeg \add idurar\add* n Lubnan. Imsexxaren inu ad iřin ak-d imsexxaren nnec u necc ad ac wceɣ řmunet i imsexxaren nnec ɛlaḥsab marra min d ayi ɣa tinid, minzi cek tessned aqa neccin war ɣarneɣ uřa d ijj wenni izemmaren ad izdem akeccuḍ am \add ayt n\add* Ṣidun.”
\m 
\v 21 Umi isřa Ḥiram awařen n Suliman, imsar, aqa ifarḥ aṭṭas s waṭṭas, inna: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI ass-a, maɣar Netta iwca i Dawud ijj n mmis d amiɣis x řgens-a d ameqqran!”
\v 22 Ḥiram issekk \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar Suliman, inna: “Necc sřiɣ i umi i tessekked \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣari. Necc ad ssqefřeɣ marra meẓri nnec zi jjihet n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi. \f ◼ \fr 5:22 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 23 Imsexxaren inu ad t-i-dd-awyen zeg \add idurar n\add* Lubnan ɣar řebḥar u necc ad t ssiwḍeɣ x tɣarruba n tḥenya x řebḥar ɣar wemcan i d ayi ɣa tinid. Dinni ad t ssarxuɣ u cek ad t teksid, u cek ad tessqefřed marra meẓri inu, maḥend ad tewced macca i taddart inu.”
\m 
\v 24 Uca Ḥiram iwca akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi i Suliman, marra anect meẓri nnes.
\v 25 Iwca Suliman ɛicrin-ařef ikuruten n irden i Ḥiram d macca i taddart nnes u ɛicrin ikuruten n zzect \add n zzitun\add* taḥurrect. D man aya i iwca Suliman aseggʷas x useggʷas i Ḥiram.
\v 26 SIDI iwca i Suliman tiɣit am mammec tuɣa i d as inna netta. Tuɣa \add din\add* řehna jar Ḥiram d Suliman, uca nitni s tnayen idsen ggin ijj n řɛahd. \x ◘ \xo 5:26 \xt 1 Ij. 3:12\x*
\m 
\v 27 Ajeǧid Suliman issgeɛɛed-dd zi marra Israil \add iryazen\add* i tsexxart i ittxeṣṣan. Asgeɛɛed-a yiwi-dd třatin-ařef n yeryazen i řxedmet.
\v 28 Issekk i-ten ɣar \add idurar n Lubnan\add*, ɛecra-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add* deg uyur, s nnubet: ijj n uyur tuɣa aten x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan u tnayen n iyuren tuɣa aten di taddart nsen. Aduniram \add tuɣa\add* x yeryazen i iggin řxedmet.
\v 29 Tuɣa Suliman ɣares \add ɛawed\add* sebɛin-ařef n imsexxaren i trebbut n řehmeř d tmenyin-ařef n isuydayen x idurar.
\v 30 Ahta ɛad i imeḥḍayen imeqqranen n Suliman nni \add iǧan\add* x řxedmet, tuɣa din třata u-třatin-mya \add n yeryazen\add* nni iǧan x řgens i iggin řxedmet.
\v 31 Yumur ujeǧid maḥend ad neqcen tiṣuḍar timeqqranin, tiṣuḍar iɣřan, ḥima ad ssarsen dsas n Taddart \add s\add* tiṣuḍar-a ittwassuydan.
\v 32 Ibennayen n Suliman d ibennayen n Ḥiram uřa d Ijibayliyyen neqcen tent. Nitni sswejden akeccuḍ d yeẓra, ḥima ad bnan Taddart.
\b
\b
\c 6
\s1 Řebni n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa-mya u-tmanyin awarni i uffuɣ n ayt n Israil zi temmurt n Miṣra, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n tgelda n Suliman x Israil, deg uyur n Ziw, ayur wiss tnayen, imsar, aqa netta ibda ad ibna Taddart n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 6:1 \xt [2 Im. 3:1-14] — 1 Ij. 8:65-66; 2 Im. 3:2; Řex. 7:47\x*  *
\b
\m 
\v 2 Taddart i ibna ujeǧid Suliman i SIDI tuɣa-tt settin n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart u ɛicrin \add n iɣaǧen n\add* tiru u třatin n iɣaǧen n řuɛřa.
\v 3 Asqif n wadaf ɣar zzat n \add Wexxam n\add* Zzawect Tameqqrant n Taddart, tuɣa-t ɛicrin n iɣaǧen n tezzuggart ɣar wudem n tiru n Taddart, u tiru nnes tuɣa-t ɛecra n iɣaǧen ɣar wudem n Taddart. \x ◘ \xo 6:3 \xt Yḥ. 10:23; Řex. 3:11; 5:12\x*
\v 4 Netta igga i Taddart tiburjatin, bellɛen tent s tewwura ak-d iɛumad i ubelleɛ.
\v 5 Ɣar řḥiḍ, ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes n Taddart, ibna ijj n řebni n zziyada, ɣar řeḥyuḍ i d as dd-innḍen i Taddart, \add řeḥyuḍ\add* n \add Wexxam n\add* Zzawect Tameqqrant u n \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add*. Igga řebniyyat n řeḍruf \add am wafriwen\add* ɣar iɣezdisen \add n Taddart\add* deg wenneḍ.
\v 6 Tisefři n wadday \add tuɣa-tt\add* di xemsa n iɣaǧen n tiru u tenni di řwesṭ \add tuɣa-tt di\add* setta n iɣaǧen u tenni wiss třata \add tuɣa-tt di\add* sebɛa n iɣaǧen, maɣar igga tinebdatin ɣar barra n Taddart ɣar iɣezdisen nnes, ḥima \add tisefřin\add* war ttidfent ca di řeḥyuḍ n Taddart.
\v 7 \add Umi\add* tᵉttwabna Taddart, \add aqa\add* tᵉttwabna s tṣuḍar ittwaqessen zi mani tent neqcen, ařami war ttwisřen ifḍisen, niɣ ccaqur niɣ ca zi řeqcuɛ n wuzzař di Taddart řami tᵉttwabna.
\v 8 Tawwart i řebni n řeḍruf ɣar umerwasu \add tuɣa-tt\add* ɣar uɣezdis afusi ař zzat n Taddart. X ddrujat yennḍen ttgeɛɛaden ɣar wenni deg umerwasu u zeg umerwasu ɣar wenni wiss třata.
\v 9 \add Ammu\add* i ibna Taddart, ikemmeř i-tt. Issduriy Taddart s tḥenya u s teřwiḥin n \add ukeccuḍ n\add* tneglin.
\v 10 Ibna \add ɛawed\add* řebni n zziyada ɣar marra Taddart, xemsa n iɣaǧen n řuɛřa \add i kuř ṭṭebqet\add* Wanita yarsa s \add tḥenya n\add* ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt x Taddart.
\m 
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Suliman, inna:
\v 12 “X Taddart-a i tbennid: Mařa cek tuyured ɛlaḥṣab tiweṣṣa inu u ad tegged lfarayiḍ inu u ad teḥḍid řumurat inu umi daysent tuyured, xenni Necc ad ac ssqefřeɣ awař i ssiwřeɣ ɣar babac Dawud. \x ◘ \xo 6:12 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:13; 1 Ij. 2:4; 9:4; 1 Im. 22:10, 19\x*
\v 13 Necc ad zedɣeɣ di řwesṭ n ayt n Israil u Necc war semmḥeɣ ca di řgens inu Israil.”
\m 
\v 14 Suliman ibna Taddart u ikemmeř i-tt.
\v 15 Netta ibna \add uřa d\add* admawen n řeḥyuḍ n Taddart nni iǧan ɣar daxeř s tfeřwin n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt. Zi tisi n Taddart ař řeḥyuḍ n tzeqqa iřeḥḥef i-ten s ukeccuḍ u iřeḥḥef i tisi n Taddart s ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi. \f ◼ \fr 6:15 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 16 Tuɣa ibna \add ɛad\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen \add ktar\add* zeg iɣezdisen n ḍeffar n Taddart s tfeřwin n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt, zi tisi ař \add tazeqqa n\add* řeḥyuḍ, uca igga \add ttasiɛ\add* di daxeř nnes d \add Axxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* i Netta, d Aqdas x Uqeddas.
\v 17 Taddart \add tuɣa-tt\add* arebɛin iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart, \add ixs ad yini\add* \add Axxam n\add* Zzawect Tameqqrant nni ɣar zzat.
\v 18 Tuɣa akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt \add i iǧan\add* ɣar daxeř n Taddart ittwaneqqec s tɛebbuzin d nnuwwarat ggur ad arezment. Marra tuɣa akeccuḍ n tengelt, war dd-ittbin uřa d ijj weẓru.
\v 19 Igga \add Axxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* ɣar daxeř qaɛ n Taddart, ḥima ad din issars Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI.
\m 
\v 20 \add Axxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* \add tuɣa-t\add* ɛicrin n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart ɣar uɣezdis n zzat u ɛicrin n iɣaǧen n tiru d ɛicrin n iɣaǧen n řuɛřa. Iřeḥḥef i-t s wureɣ izedgen. Iřeḥḥef \add ɛawed\add* aɛalṭar s ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt.
\v 21 Suliman iɣeǧef daxeř n Taddart s wureɣ izedgen. Ɣar zzat n \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* isseɛdu ssnaseř n wureɣ. Iɣeǧef \add Wexxam n Daxeř\add* s wureɣ.
\v 22 Iɣeǧef marra Taddart s wureɣ, ařami tkemmeř marra Taddart. Iɣeǧef marra aɛalṭar nni iǧan ɣar \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* s wureɣ.
\m 
\v 23 Deg \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* igga tnayen n ikiruben \add n ukeccuḍ\add* n uzemmur. Tiddi nsen tuɣa-tt di ɛecra n iɣaǧen. \f ◼ \fr 6:23 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 6:23 \xt Uf. 25:18\x*
\v 24 Ijj n wafriw n ukirub \add tuɣa dayes\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen u deg wafriw nneɣni n ukirub \add tuɣa dayes ɛawed\add* xemsa n iɣaǧen. Zeg ixef n \add yijj n\add* wafriw nnes ař ixef n wafriw nnes \add nneɣni\add* \add aqa\add* ɛecra n iɣaǧen.
\v 25 Akirub nneɣni \add tuɣa ɣares ɛawed řeɛbar n\add* ɛecra n iɣaǧen. Ikiruben tuɣa ɣarsen s tnayen idsen ijj n řeɛbar d ijj n waddud.
\v 26 Ijj n ukirub tuɣa řuɛřa nnes ɛecra n iɣaǧen u ammu uřa d \add řuɛřa n\add* ukirub nneɣni.
\v 27 Netta issbedd ikiruben di řwesṭ n taddart n daxeř. Ifriwen n ikiruben tuɣa bezzɛen \add ařami\add* afriw n ijj ittakkʷaḍ ijj n řḥiḍ u afriw n ukirub nneɣni ittakkwaḍ řḥiḍ nneɣni. Ɣar řwesṭ n taddart mmḥadan ifriwen nsen ayawya, afriw ɣar wefriw. \x ◘ \xo 6:27 \xt Uf. 25:20\x*
\v 28 Netta iɣeǧef ikiruben s wureɣ.
\m 
\v 29 Marra řeḥyuḍ n Taddart ɣar marra iɣezdisen nnes inqec i-ten s uqessi n ineqqicen n ikiruben d tcejjura n tini d nnuwwarat yarezmen, zi daxeř u ɣar barra.
\v 30 Iɣeǧef tisi n Taddart s wureɣ am \add deg wexxam\add* n ḍaxeř am \add deg wexxam\add* n zzat.
\v 31 Ɣar wadaf n \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* igga netta tiwwura \add n ukeccuḍ\add* n uzemmur. Akwadrun s řeḍruf \add ɣar uɣezdis n tewwart\add* \add ittawi\add* ijj n řexmus \add n řḥiḍ\add*.
\v 32 Tnayen n tewwura \add tuɣa atent\add* zeg \add ukeccuḍ n\add* uzemmur. Netta inqec \add daysen\add* ineqqicen n ikiruben d tcejjura n tini d nnuwwarat yarezmen, uca iɣeǧef \add tiwwura\add* s wureɣ. \add Uřa d\add* ikiruben d tcejjura n tini ibezzeɛ i-ten s wureɣ.
\v 33 Igga ɛawed řeḍruf \add i tnayen n iɣezdisen\add* n wadaf \add n Wexxam\add* n Zzawect Tameqqrant zeg \add ukeccuḍ n\add* uzemmur, zeg ict n terbaɛt \add n řḥiḍ\add*.
\v 34 Tnayen n tewwura \add tuɣa atent\add* zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi. Tnayen n tɣemmura \add ɣar ṭṭarf\add* n ict n tewwart tuɣa ttquwwarent di \add barra\add* u tnayen n tɣemmura ttwaneqcent \add ɣar ṭṭarf\add* n tenneɣnit tuɣa ttquwwarent di \add daxeř\add*.
\v 35 Netta inqec \add daysent\add* ikiruben d tcejjura n tini d nnuwwarat yarezmen uca icellel i-tent s wureɣ, s ijj n wudem n teqcurt iřeɣɣen x wenqac.
\m 
\v 36 Netta ibna řemraḥ ɣar daxeř s třata n iseddiyyen n tṣuḍar ittwassuydan u s yijj n useddi n \add tḥenya n tcejjart n\add* tengelt.
\m 
\v 37 Deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa ittwassars dsas n Taddart n SIDI, deg uyur Ziw.
\v 38 Deg useggʷas wiss ḥiṭac n uyur Bul, aqa-t d ayur wiss tmenya, tᵉttwakemmeř Taddart s marra tiseqqar nnes u ɛlaḥsab marra lfarayiḍ nnes. Netta ibna i-tt \add deg ijj n řmijař n\add* sebɛa n iseggʷusa.
\b
\b
\c 7
\s1 Řeqṣar n Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Di taddart nnes ibna Suliman třeṭṭac n iseggʷusa, uca ikemmeř marra taddart nnes. \x ◘ \xo 7:1 \xt 1 Ij. 9:10\x*
\v 2 Netta ibna Taddart n Wezɣar n Lubnan. \add Tuɣa-tt\add* di mya n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart u xemsin n iɣaǧen n tiru u třatin n iɣaǧen n řuɛřa, \add tᵉttwagg\add* x arebɛa n iseddiyyen n ipilaren n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt u \add ttwassarsent\add* tḥenya n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt tiwa i ipilaren. \f ◼ \fr 7:2 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’. \fk řuɛřa\ft - niɣ ‘tiddi’.\f*
\v 3 Tuɣa s ict n tzeqqa zeg ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt tiwa i tḥenya n uɛarreḍ nni \add iǧan\add* x xemsa u-rebɛin n ipilaren \add nni\add*, aqa xemmesṭac \add n tḥenya\add* x ijj n useddi \add n ipilaren\add*.
\v 4 Tuɣa tiwwura \add n řekwazi\add* di třata n iseddiyyen, \add ict n\add* tburjet ajemmaḍ i tburjet \add nneɣni\add*, třata n twařawin.
\v 5 Marra tiwwura d řeḍruf \add nsent ɣar iɣezdisen\add* \add tuɣa aten d\add* akwadrun, uca arzam \add n ict n tewwart\add* \add tuɣa-tt\add* ajemmaḍ n warzam \add n ict n tewwart nneɣni\add*, třata n twařawin.
\v 6 Asqif igga i-t s ipilaren \add ɣar zzat n taddart\add*, xemsin n iɣaǧen n tuzzeggart u třatin n iɣaǧen n tiru. Ɣar wudem n \add ipilaren nni\add* tuɣa ict n tesqift \add nneɣni\add* ak-d ipilaren, uca ɛawed uřa d ijj n useqqef ɣar wudem n \add ipilaren nni\add*.
\v 7 Netta igga \add ɛawed\add* axxam i řɛarc mani tuɣa icarreɛ, axxam n taddart n ccraɛ, uca issduriy i-t zi tisi \add swadday\add* ař tisi \add nneɣni sennej\add* s ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt.
\v 8 Taddart nnes, mani tuɣa izeddeɣ, di řemraḥ nneɣni nni iǧan \add ktar\add* ɣar daxeř zeg wexxam \add n taddart n ccraɛ\add*, aqa tᵉttwagg amenni. Netta igga \add ɛawed\add* ict n taddart i yeǧis n firɛun, tenni yiwi Suliman \add d tamɣart\add*, am wexxam-a wanita. \x ◘ \xo 7:8 \xt 1 Ij. 3:1\x*  *
\b
\m 
\v 9 Man aya marra \add tuɣa-t zi\add* tṣuḍar iɣřan, ttwassuydant ɛlaḥsab řeqyas, zi daxeř u zi barra ttwancaren s řmencar, u man aya zi dsas ař iẓra n sennej qaɛ u zi barra ař řemraḥ ameqqran.
\v 10 Dsas ittwagg s tṣuḍar iɣřan, iẓra imeqqranen, iẓra n ɛecra n iɣaǧen u iẓra n tmenya n iɣaǧen,
\v 11 u tiwa nsen tiṣuḍar iɣřan, ttwassuydant ɛlaḥsab řeqyas, uřa d akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt.
\v 12 Řemraḥ ameqqran i d as dd-innḍen \add tuɣa-t ɛawed\add* zi třata n iseddiyyen n tṣuḍar ittwassuydan d ijj n useddi n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt, \add am mammec\add* i řemraḥ n daxeř i Taddart n SIDI am i wesqif n wadaf n Taddart.
\b
\s1 Řxedmet n Ḥiram i Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 13 Ajeǧid Suliman issekk ɣar Ḥiram zi Ṣur, ḥima ad dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 7:13 \xt [2 Im. 3:15-17; 2 Im. 4; 2 Im. 5:1] — 2 Im. 2:12\x*
\v 14 Wanita tuɣa d mmis n ict n tajjač zi teqbič n Naftali u babas tuɣa-t d ijj n weryaz zi Ṣur, ijj n wemziř n nnḥas. Netta tuɣa iccur s řefhamet d řeɛqeř d tussna ḥima ad issuffeɣ qaɛ řxedmet n nnḥas. Netta yusa-dd ɣar ujeǧid Suliman u marra min igga, igga i-t \add n nnḥas\add*. \x ◘ \xo 7:14 \xt Uf. 31:3\x*
\m 
\v 15 Netta igga \bd tnayen n ipilaren n nnḥas\bd*. Řuɛřa n ijj n upilar tuɣa-tt tmenṭac n iɣaǧen uca s yijj n ufiřu n tenɛac n iɣaǧen \add izemmar\add* ad inneḍ i upilar nneɣni. \x ◘ \xo 7:15 \xt 2 Ij. 25:16, 17; Irm. 52:21\x*
\v 16 Netta igga tnayen n ttijan n nnḥas ifesyen ḥima ad ten ssarsen x izeǧifen n ipilaren. Řuɛřa n ijj n ttaj tuɣa-t xemsa n iɣaǧen u řuɛřa n ttaj nneɣni tuɣa-t uřa d xemsa n iɣaǧen.
\v 17 \add Uřa d\add* tijeṭṭayin ttwaggent s ict n řxedmet n umudi, \add am\add* ifiřan ggin tent s ssnaseř i ttijan \add i iǧan\add* x izeǧifen n ipilaren. Sebɛa i yijj n ttaj u sebɛa i ttaj nneɣni.
\v 18 Igga ipilaren d tnayen n iseddiyyen \add n iremmamen\add* i d as dd-innḍen i dd-yusin ak-d řxedmet n umudi i ittwaggen maḥend ad \add zzayes\add* issduriy ttijan \add i iǧan\add* tiwa i \add iseddiyyen n\add* iremmamen. Ammu i igga uřa i ttaj nneɣni.
\v 19 Ttijan x uzeǧif n ipilaren nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar wesqif n wadaf ttwaggen \add am\add* tlillicin, \add s ijj n řuɛřa n\add* arebɛa n iɣaǧen. \f ◼ \fr 7:19 \fk tilillicin\ft - ict n marka n nnuwarat daysen aẓri aṭṭas.\f*
\v 20 Ttijan \add i iǧan\add* x tnayen n ipilaren \add dewřen\add* sennej ak-d wudem n uqurar nni tuɣa i-dd-ittasen ak-d řxedmet imuden. Uca mitayen n iremmamen quwwaren asen-dd s tnayen n iseddiyyen, uřa x ttaj nneɣni.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* issbedd netta ipilaren ɣar wesqif n wadaf n Zzawect Tameqqrant. Issbedd apilar afusi, igga as Yaxin, uca issbedd uřa d apilar azeřmaḍ, igga as Buɛaz.
\v 22 X uzeǧif n ipilaren tuɣa \add din\add* ict n řxedmet \add izewwqen\add* di furma n \add ijj n řkas am\add* ict n tlillect. \add Ammu\add* tᵉttwakemmeř řxedmet n ipilaren.
\m 
\v 23 Netta igga \bd tarimant ifesyen i waman\bd*. \add Tuɣa-t\add* řeɛbar nnes zi ṭṭarf ař ṭṭarf nnes \add nneɣni\add* ɛecra n iɣaǧen, d aqurar qaɛ, uca tiddi nnes \add tuɣa-t\add* di xemsa n iɣaǧen u tzemmared ad as tennḍed s ict n ufiřu n řeɛbar n třatin n iɣaǧen. \f ◼ \fr 7:23 \fk tarimant\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řebḥar’ niɣ ‘il’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:23 \xt 2 Im. 4:2; Irm. 52:20\x*
\v 24 Swadday i tma nnes i d as dd-innḍen qaɛ, tuɣa \add din\add* tiɛebbuzin \add ak-d nnuwwarat yarezmen\add*. Ɛecra di kuř ijj n uɣiř nnḍent i trimant. Tnayen n iseddiyyen nni n tɛebbuzin \add ak-d nnuwwarat yarezmen\add* tuɣa ttwafesyen akides. \x ◘ \xo 7:24 \xt 2 Im. 4:3\x*
\v 25 Tarimant tbedd x tenɛac n ifunasen. Třata zzaysen arrin s wudem nsen ɣar ccamal, třata zzaysen arrin s wudem nsen ɣar řɣarb, třata zzaysen arrin s wudem nsen ɣar ljanub u třata zzaysen arrin s wudem nsen ɣar ccarq. Tarimant \add tarsa\add* xasen u marra zzɛenquqat nsen tuɣa dewřent xezzarent ɣar daxeř.
\v 26 Tegdar \add n trimant\add* d ijj cbar n ufus u tma nnes tuɣa am řxedmet izewwqen n tma n ijj n ufenjař, am tnewwact n tlillect. Twawit nnes tuɣa ařfayen ibatuten. \f ◼ \fr 7:26 \fk abatu\ft - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*
\m 
\v 27 Netta igga \bd ɛecra n tkarrutin n nnḥas\bd*. Tuɣa tuzzeggart n ict n tkarrut arebɛa n iɣaǧen u tiru nnes arebɛa n iɣaǧen u řuɛřa nnes třata n iɣaǧen.
\v 28 Ammu i ttwaggent tkarrutin. Nitenti tuɣa ɣarsent tiřwiḥin ɛarrḍent u teřwiḥin ɛarrḍent \add tuɣa atent\add* jar ccafud.
\v 29 X teřwiḥin ɛarrḍent jar ccafud, \add tuɣa din\add* \add arcamen n\add* weyraden, ifunasen d ikiruben. Ɣar sennej x ccafud tuɣa \add din\add* ijj n usennad. Sadu weyraden d ifunasen ttwaggent tiseddiyin n tefray nni yuyřen ɣar wadday .
\v 30 Ict n tkarrut tuɣa ɣares arebɛa n tjarrarin n nnḥas d řeḥzamat n nnḥas. Arebɛa n iḍaren tuɣa ɣarsen tiɣarḍin. Tiɣarḍin ifesyen nni \add tuɣa atent\add* sadu i tbanyut i usird, zzat i kuř taɣarḍt \add tuɣa din\add* tiseddiyin n tefray.
\v 31 Aqemmum nnes \add tuɣa-t\add* ɣar daxeř n ttaj n tkarrut, ijj n uɣiř ɣar sennej. Aqemmum nnes tuɣa-t d aqurar, ijj n uɣiř d wezyen, ammu i ittwagg. X uqemmum \add tuɣa din\add* ɛawed tinqacin, u tiřwiḥin nsen ɛarrḍent tuɣa atent s arebɛa n tɣemmura, war ǧint d tiqurarin.
\v 32 Arebɛa n tjarrarin \add tuɣa atent\add* sadu teřwiḥin ɛarrḍent u řeḥzamat n tjarrarin \add tuɣa atent ceddnent\add* ɣar tkarrut. Řuɛřa n ict n tjarrart \add tuɣa-t\add* ijj n uɣiř d wezyen.
\v 33 Tijarrarin ttwaggent am ttwaggent tjarrarin n ijj n ukarru. Řeḥzamat nsent, yantat nsent, arradyawat nsent d iɣuřaf \add n řeḥzamat\add* nsent ttwafesyent marra.
\v 34 \add Tuɣa din\add* arebɛa n tɣarḍin ɣar arebɛa n tɣemmura n ict n tkarrut. Tiɣarḍin nnes ffɣent zi tkarrut.
\v 35 Sennej i tkarrut \add tuɣa din\add* ijj n ṭṭarf n wezyen n uɣiř ibedd iquwwar as-dd zi marra iɣezdisen nnes. Sennej i tkarrut \add tuɣa din\add* ɛawed ifassen ɣar teřwiḥin nnes.
\v 36 X teřwiḥin ak-d ifassen nsent u x teřwiḥin tiqebbarin nsent inqec ikiruben, iyraden d tcejjura n tini, x kuř ijj n wemcan ixřa, uřa d tiseddiyin n tefray ɣar marra iɣezdisen.
\v 37 Ammu i igga netta ɛecra n tkarrutin, marra s yijj n webrid n ufesyi, s yijj n řeqyas, s yijj n waddud.
\m 
\v 38 Igga \add ɛawed\add* \bd ɛecra n tbanyutin n nnḥas\bd*. Ict n tbanyut iksi arebɛin ibatuten. Ict n tbanyut \add tuɣa-tt\add* dayes arebɛa n iɣaǧen. X qaɛ ict zi ɛecra n tkarrutin \add nni\add* \add tuɣa tekkar as-dd\add* ict n tbanyut. \f ◼ \fr 7:38 \fk abatu\ft - ijj n ‘ubatu’ ɛraḥař 20 niɣ 40 litru.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:38 \xt 2 Im. 4:6\x*
\v 39 Igga xemsa n tkarrutin ɣar uɣezdis n zzat afusi n Taddart u xemsa ɣar uɣezdis n zzat azeřmaḍ n Taddart, maca tarimant \add tameqqrant\add* i waman igga i-t ɣar uɣezdis n zzat afusi n Taddart, ɣar uɣezdis n ccarq, ɣar ljanub \add nnes\add*.
\v 40 Igga Ḥiram \add ɛawed\add* tibanyutin \add i usird\add*, iɣenjayen d ṭṭawyat i urucci. Ikemmeř Ḥiram marra řxedmet nni igga i ujeǧid Suliman \add i\add* Taddart n SIDI:
\m 
\v 41 tnayen n ipilaren d tnayen n iquraren n ttijan nni \add iǧan\add* x izeǧifen n tnayen n ipilaren \add nni\add*, uřa d tnayen n řexdayem n umuddi i d asent-i-dd-innḍen i tnayen n iquraren n ttijan inni \add iǧan\add* x izeǧifen n tnayen n ipilaren,
\v 42 arebɛa-mya n iremmamen i tnayen n řexdayem n umuddi \add ttwammsebḍan\add* x tnayen n iseddiyyen n iremmamen i kuř řxedmet n umuddi i zi dřin nitni tnayen n iquraren n ttijan inni x wudem sennej n ipilaren,
\v 43 d ɛecra n tkarrutin d ɛecra n tbanyutin \add nni iǧan\add* x tkarrutin \add nni\add*,
\v 44 d tarimant d tenɛac n ifunasen sadu i trimant,
\v 45 d teydurin d iɣenjajen d ṭṭawyat i urucci.
\b
\m Marra řeqcuɛ-a i igga Ḥiram i ujeǧid Suliman \add i\add* Taddart n SIDI, \add tuɣa aten\add* zi nnḥas ittwassuydan.
\v 46 Ajeǧid ikebb i-ten deg udewwar n L’Urdun di třaxt igdaren jar Sukkut d Ṣartan. \x ◘ \xo 7:46 \xt Yac. 3:16\x*
\v 47 Suliman issɛizz x \add wewzan n\add* marra řeqcuɛ-a di ssibbet n řqedd nsen d ameqqran aṭṭas. War beqqcen di řewzen n nnḥas.
\b
\m 
\v 48 Suliman igga marra řeqcuɛ i Taddart n SIDI:
\m aɛalṭar n wureɣ, tazewḍa n wureɣ min xef \add ittwassars\add* weɣrum n wescan, \x ◘ \xo 7:48 \xt Uf. 25:23; 30:1\x*
\v 49 řa d řeqnadeř, xemsa ɣar yefus d xemsa ɣar uzeřmaḍ, zzat i \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add* zeg wureɣ izedgen, řa d \add nnuwarat\add* yarezmen d řefnarat d tjeqqaḍin \add n teftič\add* n wureɣ,
\v 50 uřa d ṭṭawyat d tjeqqaḍin d ṭṭawyat i urucci d tɣenjayin d tmejmarin n wureɣ izedgen. \add Xenni igga ɛawed\add* řemfaseř i tewwura n Taddart n daxeř, i Weqdas x Uqeddas, uřa \add řemfaseř\add* i tewwura n \add Wexxam n\add* Zzawect Tameqqrant n Taddart zeg wureɣ.
\b
\m 
\v 51 Ammu i tᵉttwakemmeř marra řxedmet i igga ujeǧid Suliman i Taddart n SIDI. Uca Suliman issidef tiwhibin iqeddsen n babas. Issars nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ deg ixxamen n txubay n Taddart n SIDI. \f ◼ \fr 7:51 \fk tiwhibin iqeddsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘timesřayin iqeddsen’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 7:51 \xt 2 Ṣm. 8:7, 11; 2 Im. 5:1\x*
\b
\b
\c 8
\s1 Adeccen n Zzawect Tameqqrant
\m 
\v 1 Xenni issmun Suliman imɣaren n Israil, marra izeǧifen n tqebbař, řḥukkam \add n tudrin\add* n řejdud n ayt n Israil ɣar ujeǧid Suliman di Urcalim, ḥima ad ssgeɛɛden Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI zi tendint n Dawud, tenni d Ṣihyun. \x ◘ \xo 8:1 \xt [2 Im. 5:2-14; 2 Im. 6; 2 Im. 7:1-10] — 2 Ṣm. 5:9; 6:12, 17; 2 Im. 5:2\x*
\v 2 Marra iryazen n Israil munen-dd ɣar ujeǧid Suliman ɣar řɛid deg uyur n Itanim, aqa-t d ayur wiss sebɛa.
\v 3 Marra imɣaren n Israil usin-dd u ikehhanen ssgeɛɛden Ttabut.
\v 4 Nitni ssgeɛɛden Ttabut n SIDI ak-d Uqiḍun n Umsagar uřa d marra řeqcuɛ iqeddsen i tuɣa iǧan deg Uqiḍun. Ssgeɛɛden tt ikehhanen d Ilawiyyen.
\v 5 Ajeǧid Suliman ak-d marra tamesmunt n Israil i tuɣa ɣares dd-tmun u tuɣa-tt akides zzat i Ttabut, \add marra nitni\add* wehhben uǧi d ifunasen d tfunasin, inni war zemmaren ad ttwaḥesben zi ssibbet n řqedd ameqqran nsen.
\m 
\v 6 Ikehhanen iwyen Ttabut n Řɛahd n SIDI ɣar wemcan nnes, ɣar \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř n Taddart, deg Weqdas x Uqeddas, ař sadu wafriwen n ikiruben. \f ◼ \fr 8:6 \fk ikiruben\ft - ict n marka n lmalakat.\f*
\v 7 Maɣar ikiruben bezzɛen tnayen n wafriwen nsen tiwa n wemcan n Ttabut, uca ikiruben dřin Ttabut d iɛumad nnes \add i tarebbut\add* zi sennej.
\v 8 Iɛumad nnes \add n tarebbut\add* tuɣa ffɣen-dd ařami ttwaẓarren ixfawen n iɛumad nnes zeg Uqeddas zzat i wudem n \add Wexxam n\add* Daxeř \add n Zzawect\add*, \add maca\add* zi barra war zemmaren ad ten ẓaren. \add Iɛumad\add* qqimen dinni ař ass-a.
\v 9 War iǧi uřa d ca di Ttabut mɣir tnayen n teřwiḥin i tuɣa dayes issars Musa ɣar Hurib, řami igga SIDI \add Řɛahd\add* ak-d ayt n Israil umi dd-ffɣen zi Miṣra. \x ◘ \xo 8:9 \xt Uf. 34:27\x*
\m 
\v 10 Řami dd-ffɣen ikehhanen zeg Uqeddas \add ɣar barra\add*, imsar, aqa ijj n useynu iccur Taddart n SIDI.
\v 11 War zemmaren ikehhanen ad qqimen bedden ḥima ad sexxaren zi ssibbet n useynu, minzi aɛuǧi n SIDI tuɣa iccur Taddart n SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 8:11 \xt Uf. 40:34, 35; 2 Im. 7:2\x*
\v 12 Xenni inna Suliman: “SIDI inna aqa Netta ad izdeɣ deg ijj n useynu ibbumbes. \x ◘ \xo 8:12 \xt Uf. 20:21; Lawi 16:2; Aɛwd. 4:11; 5:22; 2 Im. 6:1\x*
\v 13 \add S tidett\add*, necc bniɣ ict n Taddart, ict n Tzeddiɣt i Cek, ijj n wemcan imten i Cek, ḥima ad \add din\add* tzedɣed i řebda.”
\m 
\v 14 Inneqřeb ujeǧid s uɣembub nnes uca ibarek marra agraw-a \add n řgens\add* n Israil u marra agraw n Israil tuɣa ibedd.
\v 15 Netta inna: “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni issiwřen s uqemmum nnes i baba Dawud d \add wenni\add* \add t\add* ikemmřen s ufus nnes umi inna:
\v 16 ‘Zeg wass i di nedheɣ řgens inu Israil zi Miṣra, war ixḍareɣ uřa d ict n tendint zi marra tiqebbař n Israil, ḥima ad \add dinni\add* bniɣ ict n Taddart, ḥima ad \add din\add* yiři Isem inu, \add maca\add* Necc ixḍareɣ Dawud, ḥima ad yiři d řḥakem x řgens inu Israil.’ \x ◘ \xo 8:16 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:8; 2 Im. 6:5\x*
\v 17 Tuɣa deg wuř n baba Dawud, ḥima ad ibna ict n Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 8:17 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:2; 1 Im. 17:1; 2 Im. 6:7\x*
\v 18 Inna SIDI i baba Dawud: ‘Umi teggid deg wuř nnec ḥima ad tebnid ict n Taddart i Yisem inu, di man aya i teggid mliḥ umi tt tuɣa deg wuř nnec.
\v 19 Maca war iǧi cek i ɣa ibnan Taddart nni, maca mmic i dd-iffɣen zi tejɛinna nnec. D netta ad ibna Taddart i Yisem inu.’
\v 20 SIDI issemten awař nnes nni issiweř, maɣar necc dewřeɣ beddeɣ deg wemcan n baba Dawud u qqimeɣ x řɛarc n Israil, am mammec tuɣa issiweř SIDI, u necc bniɣ Taddart i Yisem n SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 21 Necc ggiɣ din ijj n wemcan i Ttabut tenni di iǧa Řɛahd n SIDI i igga Netta ak-d řejdud nneɣ umi ten dd-indeh zi Miṣra.”
\m 
\v 22 Suliman ibedd zzat i uɛalṭar n SIDI arendad n marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil, uca netta iksi ifassen nnes ɣar ujenna, \x ◘ \xo 8:22 \xt 2 Im. 6:12\x*
\v 23 inna:
\b
\m “\add A\add* SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, war iǧi uřa d ijj n AREBBI am Cek deg ujenna sennej u x temmurt swadday, wenni iḥḍan Řɛahd d tmexsiwt icewwařen i imsexxaren nnec nni igguren zzat i wudem nnec s marra uř nsen,
\v 24 wenni iḥḍan di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud, x min xef akides tessiwřed, minzi s uqemmum nnec i tessiwřed u s ufus nnec i dd-tarrid ad ittwakemmeř, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.
\v 25 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, ḥḍat di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud, x min kides tessiwřed umi tennid: ‘War ittwaqess zzayek uřa d ijj n weryaz zi zzat i wudem inu wenni iqqimen x řɛarc n Israil, min ɣa kken iḥenjiren nnec ad ḥḍan ad uyuren abrid nsen zzat i wudem inu am mammec tuyured cek zzat i wudem inu!’ \x ◘ \xo 8:25 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12, 16; 1 Ij. 2:4; Izhd. 132:12\x*
\v 26 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, \add a\add* AREBBI n Israil, egget ad dewřen d tidett awařen nni tessiwřed ak-d umsexxar nnec, baba Dawud.
\m 
\v 27 Maɣar ma s tidett ad izdeɣ AREBBI x temmurt? Xzar, ajenna, \add wah,\add* ajenna n ijenwan war izemmar ad Cek iksi, mecḥař s drus Taddart-a nni ssbeddeɣ necc! \x ◘ \xo 8:27 \xt 2 Im. 2:5; Ica. 66:1; Irm. 23:24; Řex. 7:49\x*
\v 28 Meyyeř ɣar tẓaǧit n umsexxar nnec u ɣar uzaweg nnes, \add a\add* SIDI, AREBBI inu, ḥima ad tesřed ɣar uřaɣi u ɣar tẓaǧit nni iẓẓuǧ umsexxar nnec ass-a zzat i wudem nnec.
\v 29 Ejj tiṭṭawin nnec ad ttwarezment ǧiřet d wass tiwa i Taddart-a, tiwa i wemcan i x tennid: ‘Aqa Isem inu ad din yiři i useǧi ɣar tẓaǧit i iẓẓuǧ umsexxar nnec deg wemcan-a.’ \x ◘ \xo 8:29 \xt Aɛwd. 12:11\x*
\v 30 Seř \add xenni\add* i uzaweg n umsexxar nnec u n řgens nnec Israil, \add i uzaweg\add* nni ttaren nitni deg wemcan-a, u seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg wemcan n Tzeddiɣt nnec, deg ujenna, \add wah,\add* seř uca ɣfar.
\m 
\v 31 Mařa ixḍa ijj ak-d jjar nnes u tᵉttwagg xas ict n tjaǧit, ḥima ad tt ijjuǧ u wanita yusa-dd uca ijjuǧ zzat i uɛalṭar nnec di Taddart-a,
\v 32 seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg ujenna, kkar, ḥkem x imsexxaren nnec, \add ḥima\add* ad ittwaḥkem x uɛeffan ařami abrid nnes ad dd-ihwa x uzeǧif nnes, u \add ḥima\add* ad tᵉttwagg tsegda i umsegged ařami ad as tᵉttwaɣ tesɣart ɛlaḥsab tasegda nnes.
\v 33 Mařa ittwaɣřeb řgens nnec Israil zzat i wudem n řeɛdu, minzi nitni xḍan akidek, \add maca\add* nitni ad ɣarek dd-dewřen uca ad qadan Isem nnec u ad ẓaǧen ad ksin s řmeɛruf i Cek di Taddart-a,
\v 34 seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg ujenna u ɣfar ddnub n řgens nnec Israil u ndeh i-ten ad dd-dewřen ɣar temmurt nni tewcid i řejdud nsen.
\m 
\v 35 Mařa ibelleɛ ujenna, xmi war din ittiři wenẓar, minzi nitni xḍan akidek u nitni ad ẓẓaǧen am nnqeřben ɣar wemcan-a, ad qadan Isem nnec u ad dd-dewřen x ddnub nsen umi Cek ten teḥṣared,
\v 36 seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg ujenna u ɣfar asen ddenb n imsexxaren nnec u n řgens nnec Israil, minzi Cek tesseřmaded i-ten abrid aṣebḥan nni ittxeṣṣa ad uyuren, u ewc Cek \add xenni\add* anẓar x temmurt nni tewcid d řwart i řgens nnec.
\m 
\v 37 Mařa din řaẓ di temmurt, \add niɣ\add* ṭṭaɛun, \add niɣ\add* ittwassecmeḍ \add imendi zeg usemmiḍ\add*, \add niɣ\add* jjriḥect n wefsu \add niɣ\add* tamuɣri \add tenni\add* iṣarrḍen, \add niɣ\add* mařa iḥṣar i-t řeɛdu \add ɣar\add* tewwura nnes, \add niɣ\add* teřqef i-t mammec ma tegga ca n jjriḥect \add niɣ\add* ca n řeḥřac,
\v 38 \add xenni\add* man ma i ɣa iẓẓuǧ niɣ ɣa ittar ijj n bnadem \add niɣ\add* marra řgens nnec Israil, \add am\add* nitni, kuř ijj \add zzaysen\add*, ssnen jjriḥect n wuř nsen, u netta iksi \add xenni\add* ifassen nnes ɣar Taddart-a,
\v 39 seř Cek \add ɣares\add* zeg ujenna, amcan imten n Tzeddiɣt nnec, ɣfar, kkar u ewc kuř ijj ɛlaḥsab tibridin nnes - am mammec tessned Cek uř nnes, maɣar Cek waha i issnen uř n kuř bnadem -
\v 40 ḥima nitni ad Cek ggʷeden marra ussan i ɣa kken ddaren x wudem n temmurt nni tewcid i řejdud nneɣ,
\v 41 \add Uca seř Cek\add* uřa ɣar ubarrani nni war \add iǧan\add* zi řgens nnec Israil, \add maca\add* ad dd-yas di ṭṭweɛ n Yisem nnec zeg ict n temmurt iggʷejen.
\v 42 Maɣar nitni ad sřen x Yisem nnec ameqqran, x ufus nnec ijehden u x uɣiř nnec isswiẓẓḍen! Mařa netta dd-yusa u ad iẓẓaǧ di Taddart-a,
\v 43 seř Cek \add xenni\add* zeg ujenna, amcan imten n Tzeddiɣt nnec, u egg ɛlaḥsab marra min xef d ɣarek ɣa iřaɣa ubarrani, ḥima marra řegnus n ddunect ad ssnen Isem nnec, ḥima nitni ad Cek ggʷeden, am řgens nnec Israil, u ad ucin, aqa Isem nnec ittwabarreḥ tiwa i Taddart-a i bniɣ.
\m 
\v 44 Mařa řgens iffeɣ ɣar umenɣi ak-d řeɛdu nnes deg webrid min xef ten tessekked u nitni ad ẓẓaǧen i SIDI \add am\add* nnqeřben ɣar tendint-a i tixḍared Cek u ɣar Taddart i bniɣ necc i Yisem nnec,
\v 45 seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg ujenna i tẓaǧit nsen u i uzaweg nsen uca taɣed asen tasɣart.
\m 
\v 46 Mařa nitni xḍan akidek - maɣar war iǧi uřa d ijj bnadem i war ixḍan - u Cek tesɛared xasen, ad ten tsellmed zzat i wudem n řeɛdu uca nitni ad ten nedhen d imeḥbas ɣar temmurt n řeɛdu, ma teggʷej niɣ tudes \add i teǧa\add*, \x ◘ \xo 8:46 \xt 2 Im. 6:36; Awřn. 20:9; Amb. 7:20; 1 Yḥ. 1:8, 10\x*
\v 47 u nitni ad tuben deg wuř nsen di temmurt mani ttwaḥebbsen, \add wah\add*, ad tuben u ad xak dd-řaɣan di temmurt n yinni ten iḥebbsen, ad inin: ‘Neccin nexḍa u negga min war iseggden, aqa negga tuɛeffna!’,
\v 48 u nitni ad ɣarek dd-dewřen s marra uř nsen u s marra řeɛmar nsen di temmurt n řɛedyan nsen inni ten iḥebbsen uca ad ɣarek ẓẓaǧen \add am\add* nnqeřben ɣar temmurt nni tewcid i řejdud nsen, ɣar tendint-a i tixḍared Cek u ɣar Taddart-a i bniɣ necc i Yisem nnec,
\v 49 seř Cek \add xenni\add* deg ujenna, amcan imten n Tzeddiɣt nnec, i tẓaǧit nsen u i uzaweg nsen uca aɣ asen tasɣart.
\v 50 Ɣfar i řgens nnec min zi xḍan akidek u \add ɣfar asen\add* marra ixeṭṭan nsen i kidek ixḍan, u ewc asen arreḥmet zzat i wudem n yinni i ten iḥebbsen, ḥima nitni ad xasen areḥmen.
\v 51 Nitni maɣar d řgens nnec d tasɣart nnec nni dd-tessuffɣed zi Miṣra, zi řwesṭ n uferran n wuzzař.
\m 
\v 52 Ejj tiṭṭawin nnec ad ttwarzment i uḥeccem n umsexxar nnec u i uḥeccem n řgens nnec Israil, maḥend ad ɣarsen tesřed ak-d marra min ɣarek i ɣa řaɣan,
\v 53 maɣar Cek tfarzed i-ten i Yixef nnec d řwart zi marra řegnus n temmurt, am mammec tessiwřed Cek s tsexxart n Musa, umsexxar nnec, umi tessuffɣed řejdud nneɣ zi Miṣra, \add a\add* Sidi inu, SIDI!” \x ◘ \xo 8:53 \xt Uf. 19:5; Aɛwd. 4:20; 7:6; 9:26, 29; 14:2\x*
\b
\m 
\v 54 Řami tuɣa Suliman ikemmeř marra tẓaǧit-a u \add marra\add* aḥeccem-a ɣar SIDI, imsar, aqa netta ikkar zi zzat n uɛalṭar n SIDI, am t tuɣa x ifadden nnes s weɛrur iqwes am ttwasswiẓẓaḍen ifassen nnes ɣar ujenna.
\v 55 Netta tuɣa ibedd \add din\add* uca ibarek marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil, inna s tmijja ijehden:
\b
\m 
\v 56 “Ad ittwabarek SIDI, wenni issareyyḥen řgens nnes Israil ɛlaḥsab marra min tuɣa iqqar! Zi marra awař\add en\add* iṣebḥanen i zi issiweř s tsexxart n umsexxar nnes Musa, war dd-iwḍi uřa d ijj. \x ◘ \xo 8:56 \xt Yac. 21:45\x*
\v 57 Ad yiři SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, akidneɣ am tuɣa iǧa ak-d řejdud nneɣ, maḥend Netta war d aneɣ ittejji u war d aneɣ ineṭṭar,
\v 58 \add maca\add* ad indeh uřawen nneɣ ɣares, maḥend neccin ad nuyur x tebridin nnes u ad neḥḍa řumurat nnes d tweṣṣa nnes d lfarayiḍ nnes nni yumur i řejdud nneɣ.
\v 59 Ejj awařen-a i ssiwřeɣ s uḥeccem zzat i wudem n SIDI, ass d ǧiřet, ad iřin udsen ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ḥima Netta ad yaɣ tasɣart i umsexxar nnes d řgens nnes Israil, kuř ass \add s\add* min \add i ittřiqen\add* i wass nni,
\v 60 maḥend marra řegnus n temmurt ad ssnen aqa SIDI d AREBBI, war din nneɣni, \x ◘ \xo 8:60 \xt Aɛwd. 4:35, 39\x*
\v 61 maḥend uř nwem ad yiři imun ak-SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, ḥima ad tuyurem ɛlaḥsab tiweṣṣa nnes, ad teḥḍam řumurat nnes, am \add teǧa\add* ass-a.”
\b
\m 
\v 62 Iɣarṣ ujeǧid d marra Israil akides tiɣarṣa zzat i wudem n SIDI.
\v 63 Suliman iɣarṣ tiɣarṣa n řehna nni iɣarṣ i SIDI: tnayen u-ɛicrin-ařaf n ifunasen d tfunasin d mya u-ɛicrin-ařaf n wuǧi d taɣarṣt n řehna. Ammu i ideccen ujeǧid Taddart n SIDI \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d marra ayt n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 8:63 \xt 2 Im. 7:5-10\x*
\m 
\v 64 Deg wass d ijjen issqeddes ujeǧid řwesṭ n řemraḥ n zzat wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i Taddart n SIDI, minzi issewjed din taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* uřa d tadunt n tɣarṣa n řehna. Maɣar aɛalṭar n nnḥas wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i wudem n SIDI, tuɣa d ameẓyan ḥima ad iksi tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tewhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add* d tadunt n tɣarṣa n řehna. \x ◘ \xo 8:64 \xt 2 Im. 7:7\x*
\m 
\v 65 Di řweqt nni igga Suliman Řɛid \add ɛawed\add* d marra Israil akides, zi mani ɣa tiwḍed ɣar Ḥamat ař Taɣzart n Miṣra: ijj n wegraw \add n řgens\add* ameqqran zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nneɣ, sebɛa n wussan uřa d sebɛa n wussan ktar, arbeɛṭac n wussan. \x ◘ \xo 8:65 \xt 1 Ij. 8:65-66\x*
\v 66 Deg wass wiss tmenya yarxu netta i řgens, uca nitni barken ajeǧid. \add Awarni uya\add* uyuren ɣar iqiḍan nsen s wuř ifarḥ u s řxaḍar x marra řxar i tuɣa igga SIDI i umsexxar nnes Dawud u i řgens nnes Israil.
\b
\b
\c 9
\s1 Aḍhar wiss tnayen n SIDI i Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Awarni řami ikemmeř Suliman řebni n Taddart n SIDI u \add řebni n\add* taddart n ujeǧid, \add wah,\add* marra min tuɣa immeẓri u tuɣa ixs ad t igg, \x ◘ \xo 9:1 \xt [2 Im. 7:11-22] — 2 Im. 7:11\x*
\v 2 iban-dd SIDI i Suliman i twařa wiss tnayen, am mammec i d as dd-iban di Jibɛun. \x ◘ \xo 9:2 \xt 1 Ij. 3:5\x*
\v 3 Inna as SIDI: “Necc sřiɣ i tẓaǧit nnec u i uḥeccem nnec i zi tḥeccmed zzat i wudem inu. Taddart i tebnid, ssqeddseɣ tt, ḥima ad ssmetneɣ din Isem inu i řebda uca tiṭṭawin inu d wuř inu ad din iřin i řebda! \x ◘ \xo 9:3 \xt Aɛwd. 12:11; 1 Ij. 8:29\x*
\v 4 Mařa cek tuyured zzat i wudem inu am mammec tuɣa iggur babac Dawud s wuř imun u s řeṣfayet, ad tegged am mammec marra i d ac umureɣ u ad teḥḍid tiweṣṣa inu d lfarayiḍ inu,
\v 5 \add xenni\add* ad ssmetneɣ řɛarc n tgelda nnec x Israil i řebda, am mammec ssiwřeɣ ɣar babac Dawud, nniɣ: ‘War zzayek ittwaqessi ca n weryaz zi řɛarc n Israil!’ \x ◘ \xo 9:5 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:12, 16; 1 Ij. 6:12; 2:4; 1 Im. 22:10; Izhd. 132:12\x*
\m 
\v 6 Maca mařa kenniw, cek d iḥenjiren nwem, ad tḥeyydem zi ḍeffar inu u kenniw war tḥeṭṭam ɛad řumurat inu d tweṣṣa inu nni wciɣ zzat i wudem nwem, u kenniw ad tuyurem ad tsexxarem i irebbiten nneɣni, ad asen tbendqem, \x ◘ \xo 9:6 \xt 2 Ṣm. 7:14; Izhd. 89:30, 31\x*
\v 7 xenni ad qḍiɣ Israil zi temmurt nni d asen wciɣ uca Taddart-a i ssqeddseɣ i Yisem inu ad tt mmenḍareɣ zeg wudem inu u Israil ad idweř d ijj n umedya d \add ict n řqecɛet\add* n ustehzi jar marra řegnus. \x ◘ \xo 9:7 \xt Aɛwd. 28:37; Irm. 7:15\x*
\v 8 U x Taddart-a tenni yuɛřan qaɛ, marra wi xas i ɣa ikken, ad itebhet ad iṣeffar. Nitni ad inin: ‘Mayemmi igga SIDI ammu di temmurt-a u di Taddart-a?’ \x ◘ \xo 9:8 \xt Aɛwd. 26:19; 28:1; 29:23; 2 Im. 7:21; Irm. 22:8\x*
\v 9 Ad inin: ‘Minzi nitni semḥen di SIDI, AREBBI nsen, wenni dd-issuffɣen řejdud nsen zi temmurt n Miṣra, u minzi nitni cebbaren di irebbiten nneɣni, uyuren ad asen bendqen u ad asen ɛebden, x uya issiweḍ SIDI marra řɣar-a xasen.’”
\b
\s1 Řebniyat n Suliman
\m 
\v 10 Awarni ɛicrin n iseggʷusa i di ibna Suliman tnayen n tudrin, Taddart n SIDI u taddart n ujeǧid, imsar \x ◘ \xo 9:10 \xt [2 Im. 8:1-18] — 2 Im. 8:1\x*
\v 11 - \add am\add* iwca Ḥiram, ajeǧid n Ṣur, i Suliman ɛlaḥsab meẓri nnes akeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* tengelt d ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* umerzi d wureɣ - aqa Suliman iwca i Ḥiram ɛicrin n tneddam di temmurt n Ljalil. \f ◼ \fr 9:11 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\v 12 Ḥiram iffeɣ-dd zi Ṣur, ḥima ad ixzar tineddam nni d as iwca Suliman, maca tuɣa atent war cnant di tiṭṭawin nnes.
\v 13 Netta inna: “Mana tineddam-a i d ayi tewcid, awma?” U netta iřaɣa asent: ‘Tammurt n Kabul’. \add Nitenti ttwařaɣant ammu\add* ař ass-a.
\v 14 Ḥiram tuɣa issekk i ujeǧid mya u-ɛicrin talint n wureɣ.
\m 
\v 15 D wa d awař x ljizya i tuɣa issgeɛɛed ujeǧid Suliman, maḥend ad ibna Taddart n SIDI d taddart nnes d lqelɛa d řḥiḍ n Urcalim d Ḥaṣur d Majiddu d Jazar.
\v 16 Firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra, tuɣa igeɛɛed, iṭṭef Jazar, iqedd as timessi. Inɣa ayt n Kenɛan i tuɣa izeddɣen di tendint uca iwca i-tt d tarzeft n tesřit i yeǧis, tamɣart n Suliman.
\v 17 Suliman ibna \add xenni\add* Jazar d Bayt-Ḥurun n wadday
\v 18 d Baɛlat di temmurt \add nni\add* d Tadmar di řexřa \x ◘ \xo 9:18 \xt 2 Im. 8:4-6\x*
\v 19 d marra tineddam n řexzen nni ɣares ɣar Suliman uřa d tineddam n ikarruten d tineddam n imnayen, u marra min tuɣa immeẓri Suliman ad \add t\add* ibna di Urcalim, x \add idurar n\add* Lubnan u di marra tammurt i x iḥkem.
\m 
\v 20 Marra řgens i iqqimen n Imuriyyen, Iḥittiyyen, Ifiriziyyen, Iḥiwiyyen d Iyabusiyyen, inni war \add iǧin\add* ca zeg ayt n Israil,
\v 21 tarwa nsen nni iqqimen awarni asen di temmurt, inni war zemmaren ayt n Israil ad ten ḥarrmen \add i uteḥḥi\add*, igga xasen Suliman ljizya n tesmuɣi ař ass-a.
\v 22 Zeg ayt n Israil war iggi Suliman uřa d ijj d ismeɣ, minzi nitni tuɣa aten d iɛeskariyyen d imsexxaren nnes d řḥukkam nnes d ineɣrafen nnes \add n řɛeskar\add* d imeqqranen n ikarruten nnes d imnayen nnes. \x ◘ \xo 9:22 \xt Lawi 25:39\x*
\v 23 Ina d imeḥḍayen imeqqranen nni tuɣa ittwařeqqmen x řxedmet di ṭṭweɛ n Suliman, xemsa-mya u-xemsin \add n yeryazen\add* nni tuɣa iḍebbaren x řgens nni tuɣa itteṭṭfen di řxedmet.
\m 
\v 24 Maca yeǧis n firɛun tgeɛɛed zi tendint n Dawud ɣar taddart i tuɣa i d as ibna. Řexdenni ibna lqelɛa. \x ◘ \xo 9:24 \xt 2 Im. 8:11\x*
\m 
\v 25 Třata n twařawin deg useggʷas issgeɛɛed Suliman tiɣarṣa n wecmaḍ d tewhibin n řehna x uɛalṭar i tuɣa ibna i SIDI. \add Ɛawed\add* issbexxar x \add uɛalṭar n řebxur\add* nni iǧan zzat i wudem n SIDI, uca \add ammu\add* i isellem netta Taddart am tekmeř \add i SIDI\add*.
\m 
\v 26 Ajeǧid Suliman ibna uřa d ijj n wagraw n iɣarruba di Ɛiṣyun-Jabar i iǧan ɣar Ilat, ɣar tma n Řebḥar n Telga, di temmurt Idum.
\v 27 Ḥiram issekk imsexxaren nnes s wagraw n iɣarruba nni, ibeḥriyyen inni issnen řebḥar, \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d imsexxaren n Suliman.
\v 28 Nitni iwḍen ɣar Ufir u ksin ssenni arebɛa-mya u-ɛicrin talint n wureɣ u iwyen t ɣar ujeǧid Suliman.
\b
\b
\c 10
\s1 Anewjew n tjeǧidt n Saba
\m 
\v 1 Tajeǧidt n Caba tesřa x ccennɛet n Suliman tenni i dd-yusin ak-d Yisem n SIDI u nettat tusa-dd, ḥima ad t tqeǧeb s tḥuja n twafit. \x ◘ \xo 10:1 \xt [2 Im. 9:1-12]\x*
\v 2 Nettat tusa-dd ɣar Urcalim s ijj n ukaravan i d as dd-iḍfaren s ddqeř \add n wagřa\add* aṭṭas, s iřeɣman nni yarebbun řeɛṭur d waṭṭas n wureɣ d iẓra iɣřan, u nettat tusa-dd ɣar Suliman u tessiweř akides x marra min ɣares deg wuř. \x ◘ \xo 10:2 \xt 2 Im. 9:1; Mt. 12:42; Lk. 11:31\x*
\v 3 Suliman icarḥ marra awařen i tḥaja \add nettat\add*. War din uřa d ijj n wawař \add s řemɛani\add* innuffaren i war izemmar ujeǧid ad as t icarreḥ.
\m 
\v 4 Tajeǧidt n Caba teẓra marra tiɣit n Suliman d taddart i ibna,
\v 5 d macca x ṭṭabřa nnes, d mammec qqimen imsexxaren nnes, d mammec bedden ixeddamen nnes d warruḍ nsen, d iwarraden nnes, d ddruj nnes \add izewwqen\add* i xef dd-igeɛɛed ɣar Taddart n SIDI, uca war iqqim dayes \add ɛřaḥař\add* buḥbeř \add ɛad\add*. \x ◘ \xo 10:5 \xt 2 Ij. 16:18; 1 Im. 9:18\x*
\v 6 Nettat tenna i ujeǧid: “Awař nni sřiɣ di temmurt inu x wawařen nnec u x tiɣit nnec, nican d tidett.
\v 7 Necc war umineɣ ca s wawařen nni, ařami dd-usiɣ danita u \add xenni\add* tiṭṭawin inu ẓrint aya. Xzar azyen \add zi kuř man aya\add* war d ayi ittwanna. Tiɣit d tcuni ɛlaḥsab ccennɛet i x sřiɣ, aqa cek sennej nsent.
\v 8 Sseɛd n yeryazen nnec, sseɛd n imsexxaren nnec, inni ibedden zzat i wudem nnec řebda, inni zemmaren ad sřen tiɣit nnec.
\v 9 Ad ittwabarek SIDI, AREBBI nnec, wenni umi dd-tusid x řxaḍar, ḥima ad cek yegg x řɛarc n Israil. Minzi SIDI ittexs Israil i řebda, \add s uya\add* igga cek d ajeǧid, maḥend ad tegged řḥeqq d tsegda.”
\v 10 Nettat tewca i ujeǧid mya u-ɛicrin talint n wureɣ d waṭṭas n řeɛṭur d yeẓra iɣřan. Ijj n ufeyyeḍ n řeɛṭur am wanita i iwcin tajeǧidt n Caba i ujeǧid Suliman, ɛemmarṣ ɛad war dd-yusi ca.
\m 
\v 11 Agraw n iɣarruba n Ḥiram i-dd yiwyen ureɣ zeg Ufir, yiwyi-dd ɛawed aṭṭas n ukeccuḍ n \add tcejjart n\add* ṣandal d yeẓra iɣřan zi Ufir.
\v 12 Ajeǧid igga zeg ukeccuḍ n ṣandal wanita afrayen izewwqen i Taddart n SIDI u i taddart n ujeǧid uřa d řgambriyat d lharpat i imedyazen. Akeccuḍ n sandal am wanita ɛemmarṣ war dd-yusi niɣ ittwaẓar ɛad ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 10:12 \xt 2 Im. 9:11\x*
\m 
\v 13 Ajeǧid Suliman iwca i tjeǧidt n Caba marra di min tuɣa temmeẓri, min ma tuɣa tᵉttar sennej i min d as iwca \add ɛad\add*, ɛlaḥṣab \add tacrimt n\add* ufus n ujeǧid Suliman. \add Xenni\add* tenneqřeb, tedweř ɣar temmurt nnes, nettat d imsexxaren nnes.
\b
\s1 Agřa aṭṭas n Suliman
\m 
\v 14 Řqedd n wureɣ i ittadfen ɣar Suliman deg ijj n useggʷas tuɣa setta-mya u-setta u-settin talint n wureɣ, \x ◘ \xo 10:14 \xt [2 Im.9:13-28] — 2 Im. 9:13; Ɛiz. 2:13; Asa. 17:9. \x*
\v 15 břa \add min iksi\add* zeg ittijariyyen u zi tsebbabt n isebbaben u zi marra ijeǧiden n Ɛarabiyya u zi lwulat n temmurt.
\m 
\v 16 Ajeǧid Suliman igga \add ɛawed\add* mitayen n tseddariyin \add n uɛeskari\add* timeqqranin s wureɣ ittwaddzen. X ict n tseddart ttwaggen setta-mya \add ciqlu\add* n wureɣ. \x ◘ \xo 10:16 \xt 1 Ij. 14:26\x*
\v 17 \add Yarni igga netta\add* teřt-mya n tseddariyin n uɛeskari s wureɣ ittwaddzen. Ttwaggent teřt minayat n wureɣ x ict n tseddart. Ajeǧid issars i-tent di taddart n Wezɣar n Lubnan. \f ◼ \fr 10:17 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:17 \xt 1 Ij. 7:2\x*
\m 
\v 18 Ajeǧid Suliman igga \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řɛarc ameqqran zi řɛaj uca iɣeǧef i-t s wureɣ ittwaṣeffan. \f ◼ \fr 10:18 \fk řɛaj\ft - ixs ad yini ‘accawen n lfil’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 10:18 \xt 2 Im. 9:17\x*
\v 19 Řɛarc wanita ɣares setta n tareffidin u azeǧif n řɛarc tuɣa-t iquwwar ɣar ḍeffar nnes u ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen n řkursi tuɣa ǧan iɣaǧen, u tnayen n wayraden tuɣa bedden zzat i iɣaǧen.
\v 20 Tenɛac n wayraden bedden ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen x setta n tareffidin. Am netta war ittwagg ɛad uřa deg ict n tgeldit.
\m 
\v 21 Marra iɣarrafen n tissit n Suliman \add tuɣa aten\add* n wureɣ u marra řeqcuɛ n Taddart n Wezɣar n Lubnan \add tuɣa aten\add* s wureɣ izedgen, war din nnuqart \add dayes\add*, \add maɣar\add* deg wussan n Suliman tuɣa ḥessben tt d walu. \f ◼ \fr 10:21 \fk azɣar\ft - niɣ ‘řɣabet’ niɣ ‘tazgant’.\f*
\v 22 Maɣar ajeǧid tuɣa ɣares ijj n wagraw n iɣarruba n Tarcic x řebḥar \add jmiɛ\add* ak-d wegraw n iɣarruba n Ḥiram. Ict n twařa di třata n iseggʷusa yudef wegraw n iɣarruba n Tarcic, yiwi ureɣ d nnuqart, řɛaj d ibaɣusen d iṭawsen.
\v 23 Ajeǧid Suliman iɛdu marra ijeǧiden n ddunect deg wagřa d tiɣit. \x ◘ \xo 10:23 \xt 1 Ij. 3:12, 13\x*
\v 24 Marra ddunect yarzu \add ad ẓaren\add* udem n Suliman, maḥend ad sřen tiɣit nnes i tuɣa issars AREBBI deg wuř nnes.
\v 25 \add S uyenni\add* usin-dd nitni aseggʷas awarni i umas, kuř ijj s tarzeft nnes, \add s\add* řeqcuɛ n nnuqart, řeqcuɛ n wureɣ, arruḍ, řesnaḥ, řeɛṭur, iysan d isardan. Aqa d man aya imsar aseggʷas awarni i umas.
\v 26 Suliman issmun ikarruten d imnayen. Netta tuɣa ɣares ařef u-arebɛa-mya n ikarruten d tenɛac-ařef n imnayen, uca yiwyi ten ɣar tneddam n ikarruten u ɣar ujeǧid di Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 10:26 \xt 1 Ij. 5:20; 2 Im. 1:14; 9:25\x*
\m 
\v 27 Ajeǧid igga nnuqart \add aṭṭas\add* di Urcalim, amecnaw iẓra, u \add ticejjura n\add* tengelt igga \add i-tent\add* aṭṭas amecnaw izemmuren nni \add iǧan\add* di Temmurt Iwaṭan. \x ◘ \xo 10:27 \xt 2 Im. 1:15; 9:27\x*
\m 
\v 28 Iysan i Suliman ttwassuffɣen zi Miṣra, zi Qiwi. Isebbaben n ujeǧid iwyen \add ten\add* s yijj n ttaman \add imetnen\add* zi Qiwi. \x ◘ \xo 10:28 \xt 2 Im. 1:16; 9:28\x*
\v 29 Ijj n ukarru igeɛɛed-dd u ittwassuffeɣ-dd zi Miṣra s \add ijj n ttaman n\add* setta-mya \add ciqlu\add* n nnuqart u ijj n uyis s mya u-xemsin \add ciqlu\add*. Nitni ssuffɣen ten s ufus nsen \add ɛawed\add* i marra ijeǧiden n Iḥittiyyen u i ijeǧiden n Aram. \x ◘ \xo 10:29 \xt 2 Im. 1:17\x*
\b
\b
\c 11
\s1 Aɛbed n l’aṣnam zi Suliman
\m 
\v 1 Ajeǧid Suliman tuɣa ittexs aṭṭas n temɣarin tibarraniyyin, \add am mammec tuɣa ittexs\add* uřa d yeǧis n firɛun: \add timɣarin\add* zi Mu’ab, zi Ɛammun, zi Idum, zi Ṣidun u zeg Iḥittiyyin, \x ◘ \xo 11:1 \xt Aɛwd. 17:17\x*
\v 2 \add timɣarin\add* zi řegnus i x tuɣa inna SIDI i ayt n Israil: “Kenniw war ɣarsen ttadfem uca uřa d nitni war ɣarwem ttadfen. S tidett ad ɣwan nitni uř nwem, ḥima ad tuyurem awarni i irebbiten nsen!” \add Maca\add* Suliman iqqen ɣarsen s tayri. \x ◘ \xo 11:2 \xt Uf. 34:16; Aɛwd. 7:3\x*
\v 3 Netta tuɣa ɣares sebɛa-mya n temɣarin, tijeǧidin, u teřt-mya n tiyya. Timɣarin nnes ɣwant uř nnes.
\v 4 Řami dd-tiweḍ tewsar ɣar Suliman ɣwant temɣarin nnes uř nnes, \add ařami yuyur\add* awarni i irebbiten nneɣni. Uř nnes war iqqim imun i SIDI, AREBBI nnes, am wuř n babas Dawud.
\v 5 Suliman yuyur awarni i Acturit, tarebbit n Iṣiduniyyen, u awarni i Milkum, nnɛi n l’aṣnam n ayt n Ɛammun. \x ◘ \xo 11:5 \xt Řqḍ. 2:13; 2 Ij. 23:13\x*
\v 6 Suliman igga \add min iǧan d\add* aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta war tuɣi icḍar aṭṭas i SIDI am babas Dawud.
\v 7 Xenni ibna Suliman ict n řgeɛɛdet i Kamuc, nnɛi n ṣṣanam n ayt n Mu’ab, deg wedrar wenni \add iǧan\add* zzat i Urcalim, uca \add uřa d ict n řgeɛɛdet\add* i Mulik, nnɛi n ṣṣanam n ayt n Ɛammun. \x ◘ \xo 11:7 \xt 2 Ij. 23:13\x*
\v 8 Ammu i igga i marra timɣarin nnes tibarraniyyin, tinni iwyen řebxur d tɣarṣa n wecmaḍ i irebbiten nsent.
\m 
\v 9 \add S uyenni\add* isɛar SIDI x Suliman, minzi uř nnes tuɣa iḥeyyed x SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, i tuɣa ɣares-dd iban tnayen n twařawin, \x ◘ \xo 11:9 \xt 1 Ij. 3:5; 9:2\x*
\v 10 \add waxxa\add* tuɣa ɣares dd-yusa řumur \add nican\add*, maḥend war iggur awarni i irebbiten nneɣni u netta \add xenni\add* war iḥḍa min d as yumur SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 11:10 \xt 1 Ij. 6:12\x*
\v 11 \add S uyenni\add* inna SIDI i Suliman: “Minzi imsar ac ammu ařami war teḥḍid ca Řɛahd inu d tweṣṣa inu nni cek umureɣ, s tidett ad zzayek qeřɛeɣ tageldit-a uca ad tt wceɣ i umsexxar nnec. \x ◘ \xo 11:11 \xt 1 Ij. 12:15\x*
\v 12 Deg wussan nnec war t ggeɣ \add ɛad\add* di ṭṭweɛ n babac Dawud, \add maca\add* ad tt qeřɛeɣ zeg ufus n mmic.
\v 13 Maca Necc war xak qeřɛeɣ tageldit marra. Ad wceɣ ict n teqbič i mmic di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud u di ṭṭweɛ n Urcalim nni farzeɣ Necc.”
\b
\s1 Řɛedyan n Suliman
\m 
\v 14 SIDI issekkar-dd i Suliman ijj n řeɛdu Hadad, zi Idum. Tuɣa Hadad zi tarwa n ujeǧid n Idum. \f ◼ \fr 11:14 \fk tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’.\f*
\v 15 Umi tuɣa Dawud di Idum u Yuwab, akumandar nnes n řɛeskar, igeɛɛed maḥend ad inḍeř inni ittwassnuqqben, imsar, aqa Yuwab inɣa marra \add min iǧan d\add* awtem di Idum. \x ◘ \xo 11:15 \xt 2 Ṣm. 8:14; 1 Im. 18:12, 13\x*
\v 16 Maɣar Yuwab iqqim dinni setta n iyuren ak-d marra Israil, ařami iteḥḥa marra \add min iǧan d\add* awtem di Idum. \f ◼ \fr 11:16 \fk iteḥḥa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘iqḍeɛ’.\f*
\v 17 Maca Hadad izemmar ad yarweř, netta d ca n yeryazen Idumiyyen zeg imsexxaren n babas akides, ařami dd-usin ɣar Miṣra. Tuɣa Hadad \add ɛad\add* d ijj n uḥenjir d ameẓyan.
\v 18 Nitni tuɣa kkaren zi Midyan uca iwḍen ɣar Faran. Dinni ksin nitni iryazen n Faran akidsen uca usin-dd ɣar Miṣra ɣar firɛun, ajeǧid n Miṣra. Wanita iwca as ict n taddart, iwca as awař \add ad as iwc\add* macca u iwca as ict n temmurt.
\v 19 Hadad yufa arḍa ameqqran di tiṭṭawin n firɛun, ařami wanita iwca as učmas n temɣart nnes d tamɣart, učmas n tjeǧidt Taḥfanis.
\v 20 Učmas n Taḥfanis turuw as-dd mmis Janubat, wenni tessuṭṭuḍ Taḥfanis di taddart n firɛun, ařami \add xenni\add* Janubat \add iyma\add* di řwesṭ n ayt n firɛun.
\m 
\v 21 Isřa Hadad di Miṣra belli Dawud tuɣa igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes uca Yuwab, akumandar n řɛeskar, immut. \add Xenni\add* inna Hadad i firɛun: “Sekk ayi-dd, ad raḥeɣ ɣar temmurt inu!”
\v 22 \add Maca\add* firɛun inna: “Min cek ixeṣṣen ɣari, řami dayek ẓriɣ, cek texsed ad tɛeqbed ɣar temmurt nnec?” Netta inna: “Walu, maca \add waxxa amenni\add* sekk ayi-dd din!”
\m 
\v 23 AREBBI issekkar xas \add ɛawed\add* ijj n řeɛdu nneɣni, Razun, mmis n Ilidaɛ, wenni tuɣa yarewřen zi sidi nnes Hadad-Ɛazar, ajeǧid n Ṣuba. \x ◘ \xo 11:23 \xt 2 Ṣm. 8:3; 10:18\x*
\v 24 Tuɣa issmun iryazen, idweř d řqebṭan n bandiyya \add nsen\add* řami tuɣa ixs Dawud ad ten ineɣ. \add Maca\add* nitni ruḥen ɣar Dimacq, zeddɣen din u areyysen di Dimacq. \x ◘ \xo 11:24 \xt 2 Ṣm. 8:3\x*
\v 25 Netta tuɣa-t d ijj n řeɛdu n Israil marra ussan n Suliman d man aya sennej i řɣar \add i igga\add* Hadad. Netta iɛiff Israil u yareyyes am ujeǧid x Aram.
\m 
\v 26 Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, ijj n Ifrati zi Ṣaradata, ijj n umsexxar n Suliman issgeɛɛed afus nnes x ujeǧid. Yemmas qqaren as Ṣaruɛa, tuɣa-tt d tajjač. \f ◼ \fr 11:26 \fk Yarubɛam\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘řgens d aṭṭas’ niɣ ‘řgens imcubbec’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 11:26 \xt 2 Im. 13:6\x*
\v 27 D man aya d ssibbet i zi tuɣa dd-issgeɛɛed afus nnes x ujeǧid, \add řami\add* tuɣa Suliman ibenna lqelɛa, iqqen tazzit di tendint n babas Dawud. \f ◼ \fr 11:27 \fk tazzit\ft - niɣ ‘řxawi’.\f*
\v 28 Tuɣa Yarubɛam d ijj n bu-teɣruḍt imeḥḍen. Iẓra Suliman aqa aḥudri imḥeḍ di řxedmet uca netta igga i-t x marra řxedmet n tarebbut n taddart n Yusuf.
\v 29 Di řweqt nni imsar aqa Yarubɛam iffeɣ zi Urcalim uca yufa i-t unabi Axiya deg webrid. Wanita tuɣa yarḍ ijj n warruḍ n jdid u nitni s tnayen idsen tuɣa aten weḥḥedsen deg iyyar.
\v 30 Axiya iṭṭef arruḍ n jdid nnes wenni yarḍen u icarreg i-t di tenɛac n iziynat.
\v 31 Inna i Yarubɛam: “Ksi ɛecra n iziynat i cek, maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Xẓar, Necc ad carrgeɣ tageldit zeg ufus n Suliman uca ad ac wceɣ ɛecra n tqebbař, \x ◘ \xo 11:31 \xt 1 Ṣm. 15:28\x*
\v 32 \add maca\add* ict n teqbič ad tiři i netta di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud u di ṭṭweɛ n Urcalim, tandint nni farzeɣ Necc zi marra tiqebbař n Israil.
\v 33 Maɣar nitni semḥen dayi u sejden i Acturit, tarebbit n Iṣiduniyyen, i Kamuc, arebbi n ayt n Mu’ab, u i Malkam, arebbi n ayt n Ɛammun. War uyuren nitni di tebridin inu maḥend ad ggen min \add iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin inu u \add war ḥḍin\add* tiweṣṣa inu d lfarayiḍ inu am \add t igga\add* babas Dawud.
\v 34 Maca war d as ttekkseɣ ca marra tageldit zeg ufus nnes, maca ad t ssmetneɣ d řḥakem marra ussan n tudart nnes di ṭṭweɛ n umsexxar inu Dawud, wenni farzeɣ d wenni iḥḍan řumurat inu d tweṣṣa inu,
\v 35 \add maca\add* ad kkseɣ tagelda zeg ufus n mmis u ad cek wceɣ ɛecra n tqebbař zzayes,
\v 36 u i mmis ad as wceɣ ict n teqbič, maḥend ad teqqim i umsexxar inu Dawud řebda ict n tfawt zzat i wudem inu di Urcalim, tandint nni farzeɣ Necc i Yixef inu, ḥima ad din ssmetneɣ Isem inu. \x ◘ \xo 11:36 \xt 1 Ij. 15:4; Izhd. 132:17\x*
\v 37 Necc ad cek ksiɣ u cek ad tḥekmed x marra min immeẓri řeɛmar nnec u ad tiřid d ajeǧid x Israil.
\v 38 Mařa cek tesřid ɣar marra min zi cek umureɣ, ad tuyured x tebridin inu u ad tegged min \add iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin inu umi i ɣa teḥḍid tiweṣṣa inu d řumurat inu am t igga umsexxar inu Dawud, \add xenni\add* ad imsar aqa Necc ad iřiɣ akidek u ad ac bniɣ ict n taddart i ɣa teqqim am mammec tt bniɣ i Dawud u Necc ad ac wceɣ Israil,
\v 39 Necc ad ssehwiɣ tarwa n Dawud i man aya, maca war iǧi i řebda.” \f ◼ \fr 11:39 \fk tarwa\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzariɛet’.\f*
\m 
\v 40 Suliman tuɣa yarezzu ad ineɣ Yarubɛam, maca Yarubɛam ikkar, yarweř ɣar Miṣra, ɣar Cicak, ajeǧid n Miṣra. Netta iqqim di Misra ař řmewt n Suliman.
\b
\m 
\v 41 Min iqqimen n imezruyen n Suliman d marra min igga d tiɣit i ɣares, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n Suliman? \x ◘ \xo 11:41 \xt 2 Im. 9:29-31\x*
\v 42 Řweqt nni iḥkem Suliman x marra Israil di Urcalim, tuɣa arebɛin n iseggʷusa. \x ◘ \xo 11:42 \xt 2 Im. 9:30\x*
\v 43 Suliman igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř di tendint n babas Dawud u mmis Raḥabɛam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 12
\s1 Abeṭṭu n tgeldit
\m 
\v 1 Raḥabɛam yuyur ɣar Cakim, maɣar marra Israil yusa-dd ɣar Cakim, ḥima ad t ggen d ajeǧid. \x ◘ \xo 12:1 \xt [2 Im. 10:1-19; 11:1-4] — 2 Im. 10:1; \x*
\v 2 Umi isřa Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, x man aya, umi tuɣa ɛad di Miṣra - aqa netta tuɣa yarweř zi zzat n wudem n ujeǧid Suliman u Yarubɛam tuɣa izdeɣ di Miṣra - imsar \x ◘ \xo 12:2 \xt 1 Ij. 11:40\x*
\v 3 aqa ssekken-dd ɣares ireqqasen, jjin ad xas řaɣan. Yarubɛam d marra agraw \add n řgens\add* n Israil usin-dd, ssiwřen ak-d Raḥabɛam, nnan:
\v 4 “Babac igga xaneɣ ijj n uzayřu iqseḥ. \add Xenni\add* řexxu, sarxu cek řxedmet iqesḥen n babac uřa d azayřu iḍeqřen i xaneɣ igga, \add xenni\add* ad cek nexdem.” \x ◘ \xo 12:4 \xt 2 Im. 10:4\x*
\v 5 Netta inna asen: “Uyurem u ɛeqbem awarni i třata n wussan.” Uca yuyur řgens.
\m 
\v 6 Imcawar ujeǧid Raḥabɛam ak-d imeqqranen, inni tuɣa ibedden zzat i wudem n babas Suliman umi tuɣa ɛad iddar, inna: “S min zi d ayi tweṣṣam ad dd-arreɣ x řgens-a?”
\v 7 Nitni ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Mařa cek teggid ixef nnec ass-a d amsexxar i řgens-a, ad xasen tsexxared, ad xasen dd-tarred u ad kidsen tessiwřed s wawařen icnan, xenni ad dewřen nitni d imsexxaren nnec i řebda.”
\v 8 \add Maca\add* netta inḍar ccwar i d as tuɣa wcin imeqqranen uca imcawar ak-d iḥudriyyen nni tuɣa akides imɣaren u bedden řexxu zzat i wudem nnes.
\v 9 Netta isseqsa ten: “Man tᵉttcawarem ad t dd-narr x wawař n řgens, minzi ssiwřen akidi, nnan \add ayi\add*: ‘Sarxu azayřu i xaneɣ igga babac.’”
\v 10 Iḥudriyyen nni akides tuɣa imɣaren ssiwřen akides, nnan: “Ammu i dd ɣa tarred x řgens i kidek issiwřen, innan: ‘Babac isseḍqeř azayřu nneɣ, maca \add řexxu\add* cek sarxu t xaneɣ!’ u ammu i kidsen i ɣa tessiwřed: ‘\add Aḍaḍ\add* ameẓyan inu ad yiři d ameqqran x tejɛinna n baba.
\v 11 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, aqa baba iqqen awem ijj n uzayřu iqesḥen, \add xenni\add* necc ad t ssḍeqřeɣ ɛad. Baba yarebba kenniw s urekkuḍ, necc ad kenniw arebbiɣ s iɣarḍmiwen.’”
\m 
\v 12 Deg wass wiss třata usin-dd Yarubɛam d marra řgens ɣar Raḥabɛam, am mammec tuɣa issiweř ujeǧid, inna: “Ɛeqbem-dd ɣari awarni i třata n wussan!”
\v 13 Ajeǧid yarra-dd řgens s ict n temwarrit iqesḥen, \add maɣar\add* netta inḍar ccwar i d as wcin imeqqranen.
\v 14 Issiweř akidsen ɛlaḥsab ccwar n iḥudriyyen, inna: “Baba isseḍqeř azayřu nwem, maca necc ad ssḍeqřeɣ ɛad azayřu nwem. Baba yarebbi kenniw s urekkuḍ, necc ad kenniw arebbiɣ s iɣarḍmiwen.”
\m 
\v 15 Ajeǧid war isři ca ɣar řgens, maɣar aneqřeb-a tuɣa i dd-yusa zi SIDI, ḥima ad issemten awař i tuɣa issiweř SIDI s ufus n Axiya, Aciluni, i Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ. \x ◘ \xo 12:15 \xt 1 Ij. 11:11, 31\x*
\m 
\v 16 \add Umi\add* marra Israil iẓra aqa ajeǧid war ɣarsen isři ca, yarra-dd řgens x ujeǧid, nnan: “Man tasɣart i ɣarneɣ di Dawud? Neccin war ɣarneɣ bu tesɣart ɣar mmis n Yassa. Ɣar iqiḍan nnec, \add a\add* Israil! Řha řexxu ak-d taddart nnec, \add a ayt n\add* Dawud!” Uca yuyur Israil ɣar iqiḍan nsen. \x ◘ \xo 12:16 \xt 2 Ṣm. 20:1\x*
\v 17 \add Maca\add* x ayt n Israil inni tuɣa izeddɣen di tneddam n Yahuda, aqa Raḥabɛam tuɣa xasen d ajeǧid.
\v 18 Ajeǧid Raḥabɛam issekk \add ɣarsen\add* Aduram, wenni \add iǧan\add* x ljizya n tesmuɣi, u marra Israil yarjem i-t s yeẓra ařami immut. Ajeǧid Raḥabɛam iqeǧeb, maḥend ad yenya deɣya x ijj n ukarru ḥima ad yarweř ɣar Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 12:18 \xt 1 Ij. 4:6; 5:14\x*
\v 19 Ammu i iɣewweɣ Israil x taddart n Dawud, ař ass-a. \x ◘ \xo 12:19 \xt 2 Ij. 17:21\x*
\v 20 \add Umi\add* marra Israil isřa aqa Yarubɛam iɛqeb-dd, imsar, aqa ssekken ɣares maḥend ad as dd-řaɣan, ḥima ad dd-yas ɣar tmesmunt uca ggin t d ajeǧid x marra Israil. Uřa d ijj war iqqim iḍeffar ɛad taddart n Dawud mɣir taqbič n Yahuda.
\m 
\v 21 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa Raḥabɛam ɣar Urcalim, issmun marra taddart n Yahuda d teqbič n Binyamin, mya u-tmenyin-ařef \add n iryazen\add* ittwafarzen, ttwadarrben i umenɣi, ḥima ad mmenɣen ak-d taddart n Israil, ḥima ad dd-arren tageldit ɣar Raḥubɛam, mmis n Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 12:21 \xt 2 Im. 11:1\x*
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n AREBBI ɣar Camɛiya aryaz n AREBBI, inna: \x ◘ \xo 12:22 \xt 2 Im. 11:2\x*
\v 23 “Siweř ak-d Raḥabɛam, mmis n Suliman, ajeǧid n Yahuda, u ak-d marra taddart n Yahuda u tenni n Binyamin u i \add marra\add* min iqqimen n řgens, ini:
\v 24 ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: War ttgeɛɛdem u war ttmenɣam ak-d aytmatwem, ayt n Israil. Ittxeṣṣa ad iɛqeb \add kuř ijj n\add* weryaz ɣar taddart nnes, maɣar d man aya i imsaren zzayi.’” Nitni sřin ɣar wawař n SIDI uca ɛeqben uca uyuren \add ɣar wemcan nsen\add* ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI. *
\b
\m 
\v 25 Yarubɛam ibna Cakim x idurar n Ifrayim uca izdeɣ dinni. Ssenni iffeɣ uca ibna Fanuwil. \x ◘ \xo 12:25 \xt Uf. 32:30\x*
\v 26 Inna Yarubɛam deg wuř nnes: “Řexxu ad dd-teɛqeb tgeldit ɣar taddart n Dawud.
\v 27 \add Maɣar\add* mařa řgens-a ad dd-igeɛɛed, ḥima ad yawi tiwhibin di Taddart n SIDI di Urcalim, \add xenni\add* ad dd-idweř wuř n řgens-a ɣar siditsen, ɣar Raḥabɛam, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Ad ayi nɣen u ad dd-ɛeqben ɣar Raḥabɛam, ajeǧid n Yahuda.”
\v 28 Imcawar ujeǧid, \add xenni\add* igga \bd tnayen n iɛejmiyyen n wureɣ\bd*, inna asen \add i řgens\add*: “D aṭṭas i kenniw maḥend ad tgeɛɛdem ɣar Urcalim. Xzar, irebbiten nnec, \add a\add* Israil, inni cek i dd-issuffɣen zi Miṣra.” \f ◼ \fr 12:28 \fk iɛejmiyyen\ft - niɣ ‘amwa’, ‘ayenduz’ niɣ ‘yuggu’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 12:28 \xt Uf. 32:8; 2 Ij. 17:16\x*
\v 29 Netta issbedd ijj \add n ṣṣanam\add* n ufunas di \bd Bayt-Il\bd* u wenneɣni issbedd i-t di \bd Dan\bd*.
\v 30 Aya idweř d aɛraḍ ɣar ddnub. Řgens izwar yuyur zzat i wudem n ijj \add n ufunas\add* ař Dan.
\m 
\v 31 Netta issbedd ict n zzawect x řegɛudi. Igga ikehhanen \add i dd-iqqarṣen\add* zi marra ṭṭrufa n řgens inni war \add iǧin\add* zeg ayt n Lawi. \x ◘ \xo 12:31 \xt Řxř. 3:10; 1 Ij. 13:33; 2 Ij. 17:32; 2 Im. 11:15\x*
\m 
\v 32 Deg uyur wiss tmenya, deg wass wiss xemmesṭac n uyur, igga Yarubɛam ijj n řɛid, am řɛid i tteggen di Yahuda, u netta issgeɛɛed tiɣarṣa x uɛalṭar. Igga ammu di Bayt-Il ḥima ad iqeddem tiɣarṣa i iɛejmiyyem i yegga. Igga ɛawed ikehhanen di Bit-Il x řegɛudi nni igga.
\m 
\v 33 Deg wass wiss xemmesṭac deg uyur wiss tmenya n uyur i tuɣa ixarreṣ netta deg wuř nnes, issgeɛɛed tiɣarṣa x uɛalṭar nni igga di Bayt-Il. Ammu i issbedd ijj n řɛid i ayt n Israil uca issbexxar řebxur x uɛalṭar.
\b
\b
\c 13
\s1 Aryaz n Arebbi zi temmurt n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Xzar, s wawař n SIDI yusa-dd ijj n weryaz n AREBBI zi Yahuda ɣar Bayt-Il. Yarubɛam tuɣa ibedd zzat i uɛalṭar, ḥima ad iwehheb řebxur.
\v 2 Netta iřaɣa x uɛalṭar s wawař n AREBBI, inna: “\add A\add* aɛalṭar, aɛalṭar, ammu i iqqar SIDI, ad dd-ittwaxřeq ijj n mmis di taddart n Dawud, ad as qqaren Yuciya. Netta ad xak igg d taɣarṣt ikehhanen n řegɛudi nni xak iwehhben řebxur, u ad xak cemḍen iɣsan n iwdan.” \x ◘ \xo 13:2 \xt 2 Ij. 23:15-20\x*
\v 3 Deg wass nni d ijjen iwca ict n řeɛřamet, inna: “Ta d řeɛřamet i x issiweř SIDI. Xzar, aɛalṭar ad icarreg u iɣɣeḍ n min iqqimen n tadunt i xas \add iǧan\add* ad zzayes dd-iḥruǧeḍ.”
\m 
\v 4 Umi isřa ujeǧid awař n weryaz n AREBBI wenni iřaɣan x uɛalṭar di Bayt-Il, imsar, aqa isswiẓẓeḍ Yarubɛam afus nnes x uɛalṭar, inna: “Ṭṭef i-t!” \add Maca\add* afus nnes nni tuɣa ɣares isswiẓẓḍen, yuẓeɣ, ařami war izemmar ɛad ad t-i-dd-yarr ɣares.
\v 5 Icarreg uɛalṭar uca iḥřuǧed zzayes \add yiɣɣed n\add* tadunt ɛlaḥsab řeɛřamet i iwca weryaz n AREBBI s wawař n SIDI.
\v 6 Xenni yarra-dd ujeǧid, inna i weryaz n AREBBI: “Zawg zzat i wudem n SIDI, AREBBI nnec, uca ẓaǧ xafi \add ḥima\add* afus inu ad ɣari dd-idweř!” Uca izawg weryaz n AREBBI i wudem n SIDI uca afus n ujeǧid idweř-dd ɣares uca idweř am mammec t tuɣa qbeř. \x ◘ \xo 13:6 \xt Uf. 8:4; 9:28; 10:17; Řxř. 21:7; Řex. 8:24\x*
\v 7 \add Xas uca\add* issiweř ujeǧid ak-d weryaz n AREBBI: “As-dd ɣar taddart inu uca areyyeḥ! Uřa d necc ad ac wceɣ ict n terzeft.”
\v 8 \add Maca\add* yarra-dd weryaz n AREBBI x ujeǧid: “Waxxa cek tewcid ayi azyen n taddart nnec, necc war \add a\add*kidek ggureɣ u war tticeɣ aɣrum deg wemcan-a uřa war \add da\add* sesseɣ. \x ◘ \xo 13:8 \xt Řxř. 22:18\x*
\v 9 Maɣar ammu i d ayi iweṣṣa s wawař n SIDI, inna: ‘Cek war \add dinni\add* tᵉttᵉtted u war \add dinni\add* tsessed u war tɛiqqibed x webrid i x dd-tusid.’”
\v 10 Uca netta iruḥ x ijj n webrid nneɣni u war dd-iɛqib ca x webrid i x dd-yusa ɣar Bayt-Il.
\m 
\v 11 Di Bayt-Il tuɣa izeddeɣ \add ɛad\add* ijj n unabi iwsar. Mmis nnes yusa-dd, iḥaja as min tuɣa igga weryaz n AREBBI deg wass nni di Bayt-Il, uřa d awařen i inna i ujeǧid. Iḥenjiren nnes ḥajan as ten i babatsen.
\v 12 Inna asen babatsen: “X man abrid i yuyur netta?” Iḥenjiren nnes tuɣa ẓrin man abrid tuɣa iṭṭef weryaz n SIDI wenni tuɣa i dd-yusin zi Yahuda.
\v 13 Netta inna i iḥenjiren nnes: “Bardɛem ayi i weɣyuř!” Nitni bardɛen as i weɣyuř uca netta inya xas iruḥ.
\v 14 Netta yareddef aryaz n AREBBI uca yufa i-t am iqqim sadu ict n tcejjart n yigg. Netta inna as: “Ma cek d aryaz n AREBBI wenni dd-iffɣen zi Yahuda?” Netta inna: “D necc!”
\v 15 \add Xenni\add* inna as: “As-dd akidi ɣar taddart inu u ecc aɣrum.”
\v 16 \add Maca\add* netta inna: “Necc war zemmareɣ akidek ɛeqbeɣ u necc war akidek dd-ttaseɣ. Uřa d necc war ttᵉtteɣ, war sesseɣ deg wemcan-a.
\v 17 Maɣar yusa-dd ɣari wawař n SIDI, \add inna\add*: ‘Cek war tzemmared ad \add dinni\add* tecced aɣrum u war tsessed aman. Cek war tzemmared ad dd-tɛeqbed x webrid i x dd-tusid.’”
\v 18 Netta inna as: “Uřa d necc d ijj n unabi am cek, u ijj n lmalak issiweř akidi s wawař n SIDI, inna: ‘Awyi t ɣarek di taddart nnec, ḥima ad yecc aɣrum, ad isess aman.’” \add Ammu\add* i issxarreq xas.\x ◘ \xo 13:18 \xt Gal. 1:8\x*
\v 19 Uca netta iɛqeb akides, icca aɣrum di taddart nnes u iswa aman.
\m 
\v 20 Umi qqimen nitni ɣar ṭṭabřa, aqa yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar unabi wenni tuɣa t-i-dd-yarrin,
\v 21 u netta iřaɣa i weryaz n AREBBI i dd-yusin zi Yahuda, inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘Maɣar cek tɣewwɣed x wawař n SIDI u war teḥḍid řumur i d ac yumur SIDI, AREBBI nnec,
\v 22 \add maca\add* tɛeqbed u teccid aɣrum u teswid aman deg wemcan i x i d ac inna: ‘War tzemmared ad \add din\add* tecced aɣrum u war \add din\add* tssesed aman, x uya řxecbet nnec war dd-tusa deg wenḍeř n řejdud nnec.’”
\m 
\v 23 Awarni umi tuɣa icca d iswa, ibardeɛ as i weɣyuř i unabi i d igga ad dd-idweř.
\v 24 Ammu dd-iffeɣ uca imsagar akides ijj n weyrad, inɣa i-t. Řxecbet nnes tuɣa temmenḍar \add din\add* x webrid u aɣyuř ibedd zzates uca uřa d ayrad ibedd zzat i řxecbet. \x ◘ \xo 13:24 \xt 1 Ij. 20:36\x*
\v 25 U xzar, ɛdun \add ca n\add* yeryazen, ẓrin řxecbet temmenḍar x webrid uřa d ayrad ibedd zzat i řxecbet. Nitni iwḍen ɣar tendint n unabi iwsaren uca ssiwřen x man aya.
\v 26 \add Umi\add* anabi wenni i-t-i-dd-yarrin zeg webrid, isřa man aya, inna netta: “Wa d aryaz n AREBBI, wenni tuɣa iɣewwɣen x wawař n SIDI. \add X uyenni\add* iwca i-t SIDI i weyrad u wanita imezzeq i-t uca inɣa i-t ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI wenni tuɣa kides issiwřen.”
\v 27 Uca netta issiweř ak-d iḥenjiren nnes, inna: “Bardɛem ayi i weɣyuř!” Nitni bardɛen as,
\v 28 uca netta iffeɣ, yufa řxecbet temmenḍar x webrid uřa d aɣyuř d wayrad i ibedden zzat i řxecbet. Ayrad war yecci řxecbet u war imezzeq aɣyuř.
\v 29 Xenni issgeɛɛed unabi řxecbet, issars i-tt x weɣyuř uca yiwyi tt akides. Ammu i dd-yusa unabi iwsaren di tendint, ḥima ad xas iwwet agejdur u ad t inḍeř.
\v 30 Netta inḍeř řxecbet deg wenḍeř nnes u nitni wtin xas agejdur: “Uh, uma inu!”
\v 31 Awarni umi tuɣa t inḍeř, imsar, aqa issiweř ak-d iḥenjiren nnes, inna: “Xmi ɣa mmteɣ, neḍřem ayi deg wenḍeř i di immenḍar weryaz n AREBBI u ssarsem iɣsan inu x uɣezdis n iɣsan nnes!
\v 32 Maɣar awař i ibarreḥ s wawař n SIDI x uɛalṭar-a nni \add iǧan\add* di Bayt-Il u x marra tizawiyyin n řegɛudi nni \add iǧan\add* di tneddam n Samarya, ad dd-iffeɣ nican.” \x ◘ \xo 13:32 \xt 2 Ij. 23:16\x*
\m 
\v 33 Awarni i wawař-a war dd-iddekkʷiř ca Yarubɛam zeg webrid aɛeffan nnes, \add maca\add* yařeqqem ɛawed ikehhanen zi \add marra\add* ṭṭrufa n řgens x řegɛudi. Wenni t ixsen, yařeqqem i-t u wanita idweř d akehhan n řegɛudi. \x ◘ \xo 13:33 \xt 1 Ij. 12:31, 32\x*
\v 34 Zi tmesřact-a tewḍa taddart n Yarubɛam di ddnub, ařami dd-tqarreb ɣar uteḥḥi d wareddeǧ zi temmurt.
\b
\b
\c 14
\s1 Yarubɛam d unabi Ahiya
\m 
\v 1 Di řweqt nni idweř Abiya, mmis n Yarubɛam, ihřec.
\v 2 Inna Yarubɛam i temɣart nnes: “Kkar, beddeř arruḍ nnem, maḥend war iɛeqqeř uřa d ijj aqa cem d tamɣart n Yarubɛam, ad tuyured ɣar Cilu. Aqa dinni anabi Axiya wenni xafi innan aqa necc ad dewřeɣ d ajeǧid x řgens-a. \x ◘ \xo 14:2 \xt 1 Ij. 11:31\x*
\v 3 Ksi akidem ɛecra n iɣrumen d tefḍiřin d ijj n uqdiḥ n tamment uca uyur ɣares! Netta ad am ini min ɣa imsaren ak-d uḥenjir.”
\v 4 Uca ammu i tegga temɣart n Yarubɛam. Nettat tekkar, tuyur ɣar Cilu, tiweḍ ɣar taddart n Axiya. Axiya tuɣa war itwiři maɣar tiṭṭawin nnes tuɣa dewřent ṭṭemmsent di tewsar nnes.
\v 5 \add Maca\add* SIDI inna i Axiya: “Xzar, ad dd-tas temɣart n Yarubɛam, ḥima ad cek tesseqsa x mmis, minzi wanita ihřec. Ta d ta i d as ɣa tinid. Xmi i dd ɣa tas, ad imsar, nettat ad tessniɛmiř ixef nnes d icten nneɣnit.”
\m 
\v 6 Umi isřa Axiya řḥess n iṣuraf nnes ɣar tewwart, imsar, aqa netta inna: “Adef-dd ɣar daxeř, a tamɣart n Yarubɛam! Mayemmi tessniɛmiřed ixef nnem amecnaw cem d icten nneɣnit? Necc ttwassekkeɣ-dd ɣarem s \add ict n tebrat\add* iqesḥen.
\v 7 Uyur, ini i Yarubɛam: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: Minzi Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ cek zi jar řwesṭ n řgens u ggiɣ cek d řḥakem x řgens inu Israil, \x ◘ \xo 14:7 \xt 1 Ij. 12:15\x*
\v 8 uca carrgeɣ tageldit zi taddart n Dawud uca wciɣ ac tt, \add maca\add* cek war teǧid ca am umsexxar inu Dawud, wenni iḥḍan řumurat inu d wenni dd ayi iḍfaren, ḥima ad yegg mɣir min iǧan nican di tiṭṭawin inu,
\v 9 u minzi teggid tt d taɛeffant mahu x \add min ggin\add* marra \add inni iǧan\add* qbeř i cek, uca cek tuyured teggid irebbiten nneɣni d řexyařat nneɣni ifesyen, ḥima ad ayi tesɛared, uca tenḍared ayi awarni i weɛrur nnec,
\v 10 s uya, xzar, ad awyeɣ tuɛeffna x taddart n Yarubɛam u ad teḥḥiɣ zi Yarubɛam marra wi \add t\add* itteggen x řḥiḍ, \add am\add* wenni ittwaṭṭfen, \add am\add* wenni umi jjin di Israil, u Necc ad mḥiɣ min iqqimen n taddart n Yarubɛam, am mammec farḍen řeɣbar ař ɣa iqḍa. \x ◘ \xo 14:10 \xt 1 Ṣm. 25:22, 34; 1 Ij. 16:11; 21:21; 15:29; 2 Ij. 9:8\x*
\v 11 Man wen zi taddart n Yarubɛam i ɣa immten di tendint, ad t ccen yiṭan u wi ɣa immten deg iyyar, ad t ccen ijḍaḍ n ujenna, maɣar SIDI d wenni tt innan.”
\m 
\v 12 “U cem, kkar, uyur ɣar taddart nnem! Mařa iḍaren nnem ad awyen ɣar tendint, ad immet uḥenjir.
\v 13 Marra Israil ad xas wten agejdur u nitni ad t neḍřen, maɣar netta waha zi taddart n Yarubɛam ad iṭṭef anḍeř, maɣar di taddart n Yarubɛam ittwaf dayes netta \add waha\add* min icnan i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\v 14 SIDI ad dd-issekkar i Yixef nnes ijj n ujeǧid x Israil nni i ɣa iteḥḥan taddart n Yarubɛam, ass aqa d wa. Min din? \add Wah\add*, ɛad řexxu! \x ◘ \xo 14:14 \xt 1 Ij. 15:28, 29\x*
\v 15 SIDI ad iwwet Israil, ad t issenhezz ssa d ssa am uɣanim deg waman, u Netta ad iqřeɛ Israil zi temmurt-a iṣebḥen i iwca i řejdud nsen u Netta ad ten yareyyec x ujemmaḍ n iɣzar \add n Lfuraṭ\add*, minzi nitni ggin i yixef nsen tirebbin n cwarti u sɛaren \add zzaysent\add* SIDI. \x ◘ \xo 14:15 \xt 2 Ij. 17:18\x*
\v 16 Netta ad isellem Israil di ssibbet n ddnub i igga Yarubɛam, i zi yarra Israil ad ixḍa.”
\m 
\v 17 Uca tekkar temɣart n Yarubɛam, tᵉṭṭef abrid uca tiweḍ ɣar Tirṣa. Umi dd-tusa ɣar tnebdat n taddart, immut uḥenjir.
\v 18 Nitni neḍřen t u marra Israil iwta xas agejdur, ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i issiweř s ufus n umsexxar nnes, anabi Axiya.
\m 
\v 19 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yarubɛam, mammec immneɣ d mammec iḥkem, xzar, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil.
\v 20 Ussan i iḥkem Yarubɛam tuɣa tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa. Netta igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes u mmis Nadab idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Řmewt n Raḥubɛam, mmis n Suliman
\m 
\v 21 Raḥabɛam, mmis n Suliman, tuɣa d ajeǧid di Yahuda. Tuɣa ɣares waḥit u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa umi idweř netta d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem sbeɛṭac n iseggʷusa di Urcalim, di tendint i ixḍar SIDI zi jar marra tiqebbař n Israil, ḥima ad din issemten Isem nnes. Yemmas qqaren as Niɛma, nettat zi \add temmurt\add* n Ɛammun. \x ◘ \xo 14:21 \xt [2 Im. 12:1-16] — 2 Im. 12:13\x*
\v 22 Yahuda igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u nitni sɛaren t mahu x marra min tuɣa ggin řejdud nsen s ddnub nsen i zi xḍan.
\v 23 \add Maɣar\add* uřa d nitni bnan řegɛudi i yixef nsen d imayḍuten \add iqeddsen\add* d tirebbin n cwarti, di marra tiwririn yuɛřan u sadu kuř tacejjart tazizit. \f ◼ \fr 14:23 \fk tacejjart\ft - niɣ ‘addag’ (‘iddagen’).\f*
\v 24 Tuɣa din uřa d imetleyyen di temmurt. Nitni ggin marra jjɛayef n řegnus i tuɣa issuffeɣ SIDI zi řwart zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 25 Deg useggʷas wiss xemsa n ujeǧid Raḥabɛam, imsar, aqa igeɛɛed Cicak, ajeǧid n Miṣra, ḍidd i Urcalim. \x ◘ \xo 14:25 \xt 2 Im. 12:2\x*
\v 26 Netta ikkes řeknuz zi Taddart n SIDI u řeknuz zi taddart n ujeǧid, \add iwa\add*, netta yiwi marra. Yiwi uřa d marra tiseddariyin n uɛeskari n wureɣ nni igga Suliman. \x ◘ \xo 14:26 \xt 1 Ij. 10:16, 17; 2 Im. 9:15\x*
\v 27 Deg wemcan nsent igga ujeǧid Raḥabɛam tiseddariyin n uɛeskari ittwaggen zi nnḥas. Igga i-tent deg ifassen n imeqqranen x ireqqasen n tazřa nni tuɣa ttɛessan ɣar wadaf n taddart n ujeǧid.
\v 28 Meřmi ma i ɣa yadef ujeǧid ɣar Taddart n SIDI, imsar, aqa ireqqasen n tazřa arebbun tent u iwyen tent xenni ɛawed ɣar wexxam n ireqqasen n tazřa.
\v 29 Imezruyen iqqimen n Raḥabɛam d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?
\v 30 Tuɣa iǧa umenɣi jar Raḥabɛam d Yarubɛam marra ussan nsen.
\v 31 Raḥabɛam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n Dawud. Yemmas qqaren as Niɛma, ict n \add temɣart\add* Taɛammunit. Mmis Abiyam idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\b
\c 15
\s1 Abiyam, ajeǧid x temmurt n Yahuda
\m 
\v 1 Deg useggʷas wiss tmenṭac n ujeǧid Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, idweř Abiyam d ajeǧid x Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 15:1 \xt [2 Im. 13:1-23] — 2 Im. 13:1\x*
\v 2 Netta iḥkem třata n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Maɛka, yeǧis n Abicalum. \x ◘ \xo 15:2 \xt 2 Im. 13:2\x*
\v 3 Netta yuyur di marra ddnub n babas nni tuɣa igga qbeř nnes uca uř nnes war tuɣi ca icḍar ɣar SIDI, AREBBI nnes, am wuř n babas Dawud.
\v 4 Maca di ṭṭweɛ n Dawud iwca as SIDI, AREBBI nnes, ijj n řefnar di Urcalim umi igga ad issekkar mmis awarni as, u umi igga ad teqqim tbedd Urcalim, \x ◘ \xo 15:4 \xt 1 Ij. 11:36\x*
\v 5 maɣar Dawud tuɣa igga \add min iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u netta tuɣa war iḥeyyed di marra tudart nnes x marra min i d as yumur Netta, mɣir di tmesřact n Uriya, Aḥitti. \x ◘ \xo 15:5 \xt 2 Ṣm. 11:4, 15; 12:9\x*
\v 6 Tuɣa \add din\add* amenɣi jar Raḥabɛam d Yarubɛam, marra ussan n tudart nnes.
\m 
\v 7 Imezruyen iqqimen n Abiyam d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda? Tuɣa din ɛawed amenɣi jar Abiyam d Yarubɛam.
\v 8 Abiyam igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Neḍřen t di tendint n Dawud. Mmis Asa idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.\x ◘ \xo 15:8 \xt 2 Im. 13:23\x*
\b
\s1 Asa, ajeǧid x temmurt n Yahuda
\m 
\v 9 Deg useggʷas wiss ɛicrin n Yarubɛam, ajeǧid n Israil, idweř Asa d ajeǧid x Yahuda. \x ◘ \xo 15:9 \xt [2 Im. 14:1-2; 15:16; 16:6; 11-14]\x*
\v 10 Netta iḥkem waḥit u-rebɛin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Ḥennas qqaren as Maɛka, yeǧis n Abicalum.
\v 11 Asa igga \add min iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am igga babas Dawud.
\v 12 Netta issuffeɣ imetleyyen zi temmurt uca iḥeyyed marra imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam nsen\add* i tuɣa ggin řejdud nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:12 \xt 1 Ij. 22:47\x*
\v 13 Netta issḥeyyed uřa d ḥennas Maɛka zi jjehd nnes, maɣar nettat tuɣa tegga ijj n řexyař d jjɛifect i trebbit n cwarti. Asa iqess jjɛifect nnes uca isscemḍ \add i-tt\add* ɣar teɣzart n Qidrun. \x ◘ \xo 15:13 \xt 2 Im. 15:16\x*
\v 14 War ttwaḥeyydent řegɛudi, maca uř n Asa tuɣa icḍar nican i SIDI, marra ussan \add n tudart\add* nnes.
\v 15 Netta yiwi tiwhibin iqeddsen n babas uřa d tiwhibin nni issqeddes netta s yixef nnes di Taddart n SIDI: nnuqart d wureɣ d řeqcuɛ \add nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 15:15 \xt Lawi 5:15\x*
\m 
\v 16 Tuɣa \add din\add* amenɣi jar Asa d Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil, marra ussan nsen.
\v 17 Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil, igeɛɛed \add ɣar umenɣi\add* ḍidd i Yahuda uca ibna Rama, ḥima war ittejji uřa d ijj ad yuyur ɣar Asa, ḥima ad \add ɣares\add* dd-yas. \x ◘ \xo 15:17 \xt 2 Im. 16:1\x*
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* iksi Asa marra nnuqart d wureɣ i tuɣa iqqimen deg ixxamen n txubay n Taddart n SIDI uřa d txubay n taddart n ujeǧid, uca isellem \add marra\add* aya i imsexxaren nnes. Uca ajeǧid Asa issekk i-ten ɣar Binhadad, mmis n Tabrimun, mmis n Ḥazyun, ajeǧid n Aram, wenni tuɣa izeddɣen di Dimacq, ḥima ad yini: \x ◘ \xo 15:18 \xt 1 Ij. 20:1; 2 Im. 16:2-14\x*
\v 19 “\add Aqa din\add* ijj n řɛahd jar ayi d cek, jar baba d babac. Xzar necc ad ac dd-ssekkeɣ ict n terzeft n nnuqart d wureɣ. Ruḥ, fsi řɛahd nnec ak-d Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil, maḥend ad ikkar ad xafi iggʷej.”
\v 20 Binhadad isřa ɣar ujeǧid Asa uca issekk ikumandaren n řɛeskar nnes ɣar tneddam n Israil. Netta iɣřeb x Ɛiyun d Dan d Abal-Bayt-Maɛka d marra Kinnarut. \add Aqa issekk i-ten\add* ɣar marra tammurt n Naftali.
\v 21 Umi Baɛca isřa x uya, imsar, aqa netta issbedd di řebni n Rama uca iqqim izeddeɣ di Tirṣa.
\v 22 Ajeǧid Asa ijja ad barrḥen di marra Yahuda, war ittɣimi ḥed, ḥima nitni ad kksen iẓra zi Rama d ukeccuḍ i zi tuɣa ibenna Baɛca. U s man aya ibna ujeǧid Asa \add tandint n\add* Jibɛa di Binyamin d Miṣfa.
\m 
\v 23 Imezruyen iqqimen n Asa, marra timegga nnes imeḥḍen d marra min igga uřa d tineddam nni ibna, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda? Maca umi iwsar, ihřec netta zeg iḍaren nnes s tnayen.
\v 24 Asa igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n babas Dawud. Mmis Yahucafaṭ idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 15:24 \xt 2 Im. 16:13; 17:1\x*
\b
\s1 Nadab, ajeǧid x temmurt n Israil
\m 
\v 25 Nadab, mmis n Yarubɛam, idweř d ajeǧid x Israil deg useggʷas wiss tnayen n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Netta iḥkem tnayen n iseggʷusa x Israil.
\v 26 Netta igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI uca yuyur deg webrid n babas u di ddnub nnes i zi yarra Israil ad ixḍa.
\m 
\v 27 Baɛca, mmis n Abiya, zi taddart n Issakar, igga xas ict n tmeɛmuč u Baɛca iɣřeb xas di Jibbatun nni \add iǧan\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen, umi Nadab d marra Israil tuɣa innḍen i Jibbatun.
\v 28 Inɣa i-t Baɛca deg useggʷas wiss třata n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, u netta idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\v 29 Umi idweř netta d ajeǧid, imsar, aqa iqḍa x marra taddart n Yarubɛam. Uřa d ca n Yarubɛam nni \add yarrin\add* nnefs, war t ijji ad iqqim iddar, ařami t iteḥḥa ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI nni tuɣa issiweř s uqemmum n umsexxar nnes Axiya, Aciluni, \x ◘ \xo 15:29 \xt 1 Ij. 14:10, 14\x*
\v 30 di ssibbet n ddnub n Yarubɛam i zi ixḍa netta u i zi yarra Israil ad ixḍa s tmegga nnes ixewwjen i zi isɛar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil.
\m 
\v 31 Imezruyen iqqimen n Nadab, d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?
\v 32 Tuɣa \add din\add* amenɣi jar Asa d Baɛca, ajeǧid n Israil, marra ussan nsen.
\b
\s1 Baɛsa, ajeǧid n Israil
\m 
\v 33 Deg useggʷas wiss třata n ujeǧid Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Baɛca, mmis n Axiya, d ajeǧid x marra Israil di Tirṣa, \add u netta iḥkem\add* arebɛa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa.
\v 34 Netta igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI u yuyur deg webrid n Yarubɛam u di ddnub nnes i zi yarra Israil ad ixḍa.
\b
\b
\c 16
\s1 Aɛřem n ujeǧid Baɛsa s unabi Yahu
\m 
\v 1 Yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Yahu, mmis n Ḥanani. Awař tuɣa ḍidd i Baɛca, inna:
\v 2 “Minzi Necc ssgeɛɛdeɣ-dd cek zi tɛejjajt u ggiɣ cek d řḥakem x řgens inu Israil, uca cek tuyured x webrid n Yarubɛam u tarrid řgens inu Israil ad ixḍa umi i d ayi tesɛared s ddnub nsen, \x ◘ \xo 16:2 \xt 1 Ij. 14:7\x*
\v 3 xzar, \add s uya\add* ad mḥiɣ min iqqimen n Baɛca d min iqqimen n taddart nnes, u Necc ad ggeɣ taddart nnec am taddart n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ. \x ◘ \xo 16:3 \xt 1 Ij. 15:29\x*
\v 4 Man wen zi taddart n Baɛca i ɣa immten di tendint, ad t ccen yiṭan u man wen zzayes i ɣa immuten deg iyyar, ad t ccen yijḍaḍ n ujenna.” \x ◘ \xo 16:4 \xt 1 Ij. 14:11; 15:29; 16:12\x*
\m 
\v 5 Imezruyen iqqimen n Baɛca, d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?
\v 6 Baɛca igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes u netta ittwanḍeř di Tirṣa. Mmis Ila idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\v 7 Ammu dd-yusa wawař n SIDI s ufus n unabi Yahu, mmis n Ḥanani, uřa x Baɛca d taddart nnes zi ssibbet n marra taɛeffant i igga di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, umi t isɛar s řexdayem n ifassen nnes u umi idweř am taddart n Yarubɛam, uca uřa minzi netta tuɣa iqḍa wanita.
\b
\s1 Iyla, ajeǧid n Israil
\m 
\v 8 Deg useggʷas wiss setta u-ɛicrin n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Ila, mmis n Baɛca, d ajeǧid x Israil di Tirṣa, \add i ijj n řmijař n\add* tnayen n iseggʷusa.
\v 9 Zimri, amsexxar nnes, wenni d akumandar x ijj n wezyen n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*, igga xas ict n tmeɛmuč umi t tuɣa di Tirṣa, tuɣa iscar di taddart n Arṣa, wenni tuɣa d ameḥḍay x taddart di Tirṣa.
\v 10 Zimri yudef, iwta i-t uca inɣa i-t deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-ɛicrin n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Netta idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes. \x ◘ \xo 16:10 \xt 2 Ij. 9:31\x*
\v 11 Řami idweř d ajeǧid uca inya x řɛarc nnes, imsar, aqa iqḍa x marra taddart n Baɛca. Netta war ijji uřa d ijj wenni t iggin x řḥiḍ \add ad iddar\add*, u \add war ijji uřa d ijj\add* wenni \add izemmaren\add* ad as intaqem u \add uřa d ijj\add* zeg imeddukkař nnes.
\v 12 \add Ammu\add* i iteḥḥa Zimri marra taddart n Baɛca ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI nni issiweř Baɛca s ufus n unabi Yahu,
\v 13 di ssibbet n marra ddnub n Baɛca d ddnub n mmis Ila i zi xḍan nitni u i zi arrin Israil ad ixḍa am sɛaren SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, s \add l’aṣnam\add* nsen ibeṭṭřen.
\m 
\v 14 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ila, d marra min igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?
\b
\s1 Zimri, ajeǧid n Israil
\m 
\v 15 Deg useggʷas wiss sebɛa u-ɛicrin n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, tuɣa Zimri sebɛa n wussan d ajeǧid di Tirṣa. Řgens tuɣa iḥeṣṣar i Jibbatun nni \add iǧan\add* n Ifilisṭiniyyen.
\v 16 Řgens i tuɣa iwtin iqiḍan nnes \add din\add*, isřa aqa qqaren: “Zimri tuɣa igga d ict n tmeɛmuč uca inɣa ajeǧid.” Deg wass nni marra řgens yarra Ɛumri, wenni d akumandar x řɛeskar, d ajeǧid x Israil di řmargeḥ n řɛeskar.
\v 17 Ɛumri igeɛɛed-dd zi Jibbatun d marra Israil akides uca nnḍen as-dd i Tirṣa.
\v 18 Umi iẓra Zimri aqa tandint tuɣa tᵉttwaṭṭef, yudef ɣar lqelɛa n taddart n ujeǧid, iqedd tiwa nnes timessi i taddart n ujeǧid, ařami immut
\v 19 di ssibbet n ddnub nnes i tuɣa igga, umi igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, umi yuyur deg webrid n Yarubɛam uřa di ssibbet n ddnub i igga am d yarra Israil ad ixḍa.
\m 
\v 20 Imezruyen iqqimen n Zimri, d tameɛmuč i igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?
\b
\s1 Ɛumri, ajeǧid n Israil
\m 
\v 21 Xenni ittwammsebḍa řgens n Israil x tnayen n iziynat. Ijj n wezyen n řgens \add ibedd\add* awarni i Tibni, mmis n Jinat, maḥend ad t ggen d ajeǧid, u ijj n wezyen \add nneɣni\add* \add ibedd\add* awarni i Ɛumri.
\v 22 Řgens nni \add ibedden\add* awarni i Ɛumri, tuɣa ijhed x řgens nni \add ibedden\add* awarni i Tibni, mmis n Jinat. \add Xenni\add* immut Tibni u Ɛumri idweř d ajeǧid.
\m 
\v 23 Deg useggʷas wiss waḥit u-třatin n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda, idweř Ɛumri d ajeǧid x Israil. \add Netta iḥkem\add* tenɛac n iseggʷusa. Di Tirṣa iḥkem setta n iseggʷusa.
\v 24 Isɣa adrar n Samarya zi Camir s tnayen talint n nnuqart, u netta \add ibda\add* ad ibna \add x\add* wedrar n Samarya. Iřaɣa as i tendint i ibna ‘Samarya’, ɛlaḥsab isem n Camir, bab n wedrar.
\v 25 Ɛumri igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta tuɣa igga \add min iǧan d aɛeffan\add* mahu x marra inni tuɣa d as izwaren.
\v 26 Netta yuyur di kuř tabridt n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, u di ddnub nnes i zi yarra Israil ad ixḍa, umi sɛaren nitni SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, s \add l’aṣnam\add* nsen ibeṭṭřen.
\m 
\v 27 Imezruyen iqqimen n Ɛumri d min igga d ṣṣulṭa nnes i zi igga, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil?
\v 28 Ɛumri igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř di Samarya. Mmis Axab idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, ak-d temɣart nnes Izabil
\m 
\v 29 Axab, mmis n Ɛumri, idweř d ajeǧid x Israil deg useggʷas wiss tmenya u-třatin n Asa, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Axab mmis n Ɛumri, iḥkem tnayen u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa x Israil di Samarya.
\v 30 Axab, mmis n Ɛumri, igga \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, mahu x marra inni tuɣa zzayes izwaren.
\v 31 Tuɣa tuyurt nnes di ddnub n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, drus waha, \add maɣar\add* netta yiwi Izabal, yeǧis n It-Baɛal, ajeǧid n Iṣiduniyyen, d tamɣart, uca yuyur ad iɛbed i Baɛl, isjed as.
\v 32 Netta issbedd ijj n uɛalṭar i Baɛl di zzawect n Baɛl nni ibna netta di Samarya.
\v 33 Netta igga ɛawed ict n trebbit n cwarti. Axab iɛdu s wesɛar nnes i SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, x marra ijeǧiden nni tuɣa i d as izwaren.
\m 
\v 34 Deg wussan nnes ibna Ḥiyil, zi Bayt-Il, \add tandint n\add* Ariḥa. Issars dsas nnes di ssum n mmis amenzu Abiram u di ssum n mmis amaẓuẓ Sajub yarekkeb tiwwura nnes ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i issiweř s \add uqemmum\add* n Yacuwa, mmis n Nun. \x ◘ \xo 16:34 \xt Yac. 6:26\x*
\b
\b
\c 17
\s1 Anabi Iliya ɣar yeɣzar n Krit
\m 
\v 1 Iliya, zi Ticbi, zeg imeɛzab n Jilɛad, inna i Axab: “S tidett am iddar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, wenni umi beddeɣ zzat i wudem nnes, mařa ad dd-yas nnda niɣ anẓar deg iseggʷusa-ya, \add ad yiři\add* aya mɣir s wawař inu!” \f ◼ \fr 17:1 \fk Aticbi\ft - ijj n weryaz zi Ticbi zi jjwayeh n Jilɛad.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 17:1 \xt Yaɛ. 5:17\x*
\v 2 Yusa-dd ɣares wawař n SIDI, inna:
\v 3 “Uyur ssenni, arr \add s uzeǧif\add* ɣar ccarq uca snuffar ixef nnec ɣar tiɣzart n Krit wenni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun. \f ◼ \fr 17:3 \fk ɣar ujemmaḍ n ...\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘zzat i wudem n ...’ Uřa di ayet 5.\f*
\v 4 Ad imsar ad teswed zi teɣzart u Necc umureɣ i ibaɣřiwen, aqa ad cek dinni sseccen.”
\v 5 Netta yuyur \add deg webrid\add* uca igga ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI. Netta yuyur ad izdeɣ ɣar teɣzart n Krit nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar ujemmaḍ n L’Urdun.
\v 6 Ibaɣřiwen iwyen as-dd aɣrum d weysum ɣar tuffut uřa d aɣrum d weysum ɣar tameddit u netta iswa zi teɣzart.
\b
\s1 Iliya d tajjač n Ṣarfat
\m 
\v 7 Awarni waṭṭas n wussan, imsar, aqa yuẓeɣ tiɣzart, maɣar war iwti ca wenẓar di temmurt.
\v 8 Yusa as-dd wawař n SIDI, inna:
\v 9 “Kkar, uyur ɣar Ṣarfat nni \add iǧan\add* ɣar Ṣidun, zdeɣ dinni. Xzar, necc umureɣ dinni i yict n tajjač, maḥend ad cek tessecc.” \x ◘ \xo 17:9 \xt Lk. 4:25, 26\x*
\v 10 Netta ikkar, yuyur ɣar Ṣarfat. \add Umi\add* dd-yusa ɣar tewwart n tendint, xzar, ict n tajjač tᵉttḥarwac akeccuḍ. Netta iřaɣa xas, inna: “Awi ayi-dd ca n waman deg uɣarraf-a, \add ḥima\add* ad sweɣ.”
\v 11 \add Umi\add* tuyur nettat ḥima ad dd-tawi aya, iřaɣa-dd netta xas: “Awi ayi-dd uřa d ijj n uřeqqim n weɣrum deg ufus nnem.
\v 12 \add Maca\add* nettat tenna: “S tidett am iddar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, min ɣari d tafdiřt, aqa mɣir ict n wuru n waren deg ubuqař d ca n zzect deg uɣarraf! Xzar necc ḥarwceɣ tnayen n ikeccuḍen u ad t sswejdeɣ i necc d mmi, xenni ad t necc ad nemmet.”
\v 13 Inna as Iliya: “War tteggʷed ca. Uyur, egg min tuɣa tennid, maca egg ayi-dd d amezwaru ict n tefḍiřt u awi tt-i-dd da ɣari. Awarni uya ad tessewjed \add ca\add* i cem u i ixef nnem d mmim.
\v 14 Maɣar ammu i iqqar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil: ‘Aren deg ubuqař war ixekkʷi u zzect deg uɣarraf war tneqqiṣ ař ass i di i ɣa iwc SIDI anẓar x wudem n temmurt.’”
\v 15 Nettat tuyur uca tegga ɛlaḥṣab awař n Iliya. \add Ammu\add* i icca nettat, uca \add uřa\add* d nettat d taddart nnes, aṭṭas n wussan.
\v 16 Aren deg ubuqař war ixekkʷi d zzect deg uɣarraf war tneqqiṣ ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i issiweř s uqemmum n Iliya.
\m 
\v 17 Awarni man aya, imsar, aqa ihřec mmis n temɣart-a, mmis n llala n taddart. Řehřac nnes yarni aṭṭas ařami war ittari ɛad nnefs.
\v 18 Nettat tenna i Iliya: “Min din jar ayi d cek, \add a\add* cek, aryaz n AREBBI? Ma tusid-dd ɣari ḥima ad ayi tessɛeqřed x ddnub inu u ḥima ad tenɣed mmi?”
\v 19 Netta yarra-dd xas: “Ewc ayi-dd mmim!” U netta iksi t zeg weḥsin nnes, yarbu t ɣar sennej ɣar wexxam n nnej mani tuɣa izdeɣ netta simant nnes, uca issars i-t x qama nnes.
\v 20 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa ɣar SIDI, inna: “SIDI, AREBBI inu, ma teggid xenni ɛad tuɛeffna di tajjač-a i ɣar zeddɣeɣ necc \add am ubarrani\add*, ařami tenɣid mmis?”
\v 21 Netta isarreḥ ixef nnes třata n twařawin tiwa i uḥenjir u iřaɣa ɣar SIDI, inna: “SIDI, AREBBI inu, ejj ad ɣares dd-yeɛqeb řeɛmar n uḥenjir-a!”
\v 22 SIDI isřa i tmijja n Iliya uca iɛqeb-dd řeɛmar n uḥenjir ɛawed ɣares \add ařami\add* dd-idweř iddar.
\v 23 Iliya iksi aḥenjir uca issehwa t zeg wexxam n nnej di taddart uca iwca as t i yemmas. Inna Iliya: “Xzar, mmim iddar!”
\v 24 Tenna temɣart i Iliya: “Řexxu ssneɣ aqa cek d ijj n weryaz n AREBBI u aqa awař n SIDI deg uqemmum nnec d tidett.”
\b
\b
\c 18
\s1 Iliya d inabiyyen n Baɛal x wedrar n Karmil
\m 
\v 1 Awarni waṭṭas n wussan, imsar, aqa yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Iliya deg useggʷas wiss třata, inna: “Uyur, scen ixef nnec i Axab, \add maɣar\add* Necc ad wceɣ anẓar di temmurt.”
\v 2 Uca yuyur Iliya ḥima ad isscen ixef nnes i Axab. Tuɣa řaẓ imɣar di Samarya.
\v 3 Axab tuɣa iřaɣa i Ɛubadya wenni \add iǧan\add* x taddart \add n ujeǧid\add*. Ɛubadya tuɣa itteggʷed SIDI aṭṭas.
\v 4 Umi Izabal iqḍa inabiyyen n SIDI, imsar, aqa Ɛubadya yiwi mya n inabiyyen, issnuffar i-ten, xemsin xemsin deg ijj n yefri, u iɛteq i-ten s weɣrum d waman.
\v 5 Axab inna i Ɛubadya: “Uyur di temmurt ɣar marra tařawin n waman u ɣar marra tiɣezratin. Ad taɣ ad naf aheddu u \add zemmaren\add* iysan d isardan ad qqimen ddaren u ad taf nhřa ma nenɣa řmař.”
\v 6 Nitni bḍan tammurt jar asen ḥima ad tt cuqen. Axab yuyur x ijj n webrid, netta weḥḥdes, u Ɛubadya yuyur x ijj webrid nneɣni, \add uřa d netta\add* weḥḥdes.
\m 
\v 7 \add Umi\add* tuɣa Ɛubadya deg webrid, xzar, aqa immeřqa akides Iliya. Ɛubadya iɛqeř i-t, iwḍa zzates s uɣembub nnes \add ɣar temmurt\add*, inna: “Ma d cek, sidi inu Iliya?”
\v 8 Inna as wanita: “D necc. Uyur, inna i sidi nnec: ‘Xẓar, Iliya \add aqa-t danita\add*!’”
\v 9 \add Maca\add* netta inna: “Man ddenb i \add ggiɣ\add*, aqa cek ad ayi tsellmed deg ifassen n Axab, ḥima ad ayi ineɣ?
\v 10 S tidett am iddar SIDI, AREBBI nnec, war din uřa d ijj n řgens niɣ ict n tgeldit mani sidi inu war ijji ad xak yarzu! \add Mařa\add* nnan nitni: ‘Netta war da iǧi!’, \add xenni\add* ijja řgens nni ad ijjaǧ belli war zemmaren ad cek afen.
\v 11 U řexxu cek tennid: ‘Uyur, ini i sidi nnec: Xzar Iliya \add aqa-t danita\add*!’
\v 12 \add Ad taɣ\add* ad imsar, \add xmi\add* i xak ɣa uyureɣ, aqa Arruḥ n SIDI ad cek iksi, war ssineɣ mani. Mařa xenni necc ad dd-aseɣ, ḥima ad \add t\add* iniɣ i Axab u netta war cek ittif, netta ad ayi ineɣ, waxxa amsexxar nnec itteggʷed SIDI zi temẓi inu.
\v 13 Ma war d ac ɛiwden ca i sidi inu, min ggiɣ necc, umi Izabal inɣa inabiyyen n SIDI? Aqa necc ssnuffareɣ mya n yeryazen zeg inabiyyen, kuř xemsin deg ijj n yefri? Uřa aqa necc ɛetqeɣ ten s weɣrum d waman?
\v 14 U řexxu teqqared ‘Uyur, ini i sidi nnec: Xzar, Iliya \add aqa-t da\add*!’ Netta ad ayi ineɣ.”
\v 15 Inna Iliya: “S tidett am iddar SIDI n řɛeskarat zzat i wudem nnes umi beddeɣ, aqa nican necc ad seccneɣ ixef inu ass-a!”
\m 
\v 16 \add Xenni\add* yuyur Ɛubadya ɣar umsagar ak-d Axab, ixebbar as \add t\add*. Uca Axab yuyur, maḥend ad imsagar ak-d Iliya.
\v 17 Umi iẓra Axab Iliya, imsar, aqa Axab inna as: “Ma cek d aḍeyyeɛ n Israil?” \x ◘ \xo 18:17 \xt Ɛam. 7:10\x*
\v 18 Netta inna: “Necc war ḍiyyɛeɣ ca Israil, maca cek d taddart n babac umi kenniw tejjim řumurat n SIDI \add ɣar uɣezdis\add* u cek tuyured awarni i ‘Ibaɛlen’.
\v 19 Xenni řexxu, smun marra Israil ɣari ɣar wedrar n Karmil uřa d arebɛa-mya u-xemsin n inabiyyen n Baɛl d arebɛa-mya n inabiyyen n trebbit n cwarti nni ittetten zi ṭṭabřa n Izabal.”
\m 
\v 20 Axab issekk \add ijj n ureqqas\add* ɣar marra ayt n Israil u issmun inabiyyen ɣar wedrar n Karmil.
\v 21 Iliya iqarreb-dd ɣar marra řgens, inna: “Mecḥař ɛad i ɣa tekkem ɛad ttneqřabem kenniw ɣar tnayen n iɣezdisen? Mařa SIDI d AREBBI, ḍfarem as-dd, u mařa d Baɛl, \add xenni\add* ḍfarem wanita!” Maca řgens war xas dd-yarri uřa s yijj n wawař. \x ◘ \xo 18:21 \xt Yac. 24:15\x*
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* inna Iliya i řgens: “Necc waha i iqqimen d anabi n SIDI uca inabiyyen n Baɛl aqa aten s arebɛa-mya u xemsin n yeryazen.
\v 23 Ejj ad aneɣ wcen tnayen n ifunasen. Ejj i-ten \add xenni\add* ad farzen afunas ameẓyan amezwaru i yixef nsen, ad t bḍan u ad t ssarsen x ukeccuḍ, \add maca\add* war tteggen timessi \add sadu\add* nnes. Necc ad sswejdeɣ afunas ameẓyan nneɣni, ad t ssarseɣ x ukeccuḍ u war tteggeɣ timessi \add sadu\add* nnes.
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* ad třaɣam isem n arebbi nwem u necc ad řaɣiɣ Isem n SIDI, uca AREBBI wenni i dd ɣa yarren s tmessi, d Netta ad yiři d AREBBI.” Uca iřaɣa marra řgens, nnan: “Awař\add -a\add* d lemliḥ!”
\m 
\v 25 Inna Iliya i inabiyyen n Baɛl: “Xḍarem i yixef nwem afunas ameẓyan amezwaru u sswejdem as t d amezwaru, maɣar kenniw s waṭṭas. Řaɣam \add xenni\add* isem n arebbi nwem, \add maca\add* war srusam ca timessi sadu nnes.”
\v 26 Nitni ksin afunas ameẓyan i d asen iwca netta u sswejden t. Xenni řaɣan i yisem n Baɛl, zi tuffut ař azal, nnan: “\add A\add* Baɛl, arr aneɣ-dd!” \add Maca\add* walu n řḥess uca uřa d ijj war dd-yarri ca. Nitni negzen x uɛalṭar i \add din\add* ittwaggen.
\v 27 Ɣar wazal ibda Iliya ittqessar xasen, inna: “Řaɣam s tmijja ijehden, aqa-t d arebbi. \add Nican\add* netta ittxemmam, niɣ iɛezzeř \add cwayt\add*, niɣ netta \add ɛad\add* deg webrid. Ad taɣ itteṭṭeṣ uca ittxeṣṣa as ad ifaq \add ɛad\add*.”
\v 28 Nitni sɣuyen s tmijja ijehden u qessen ixef nsen s řesyuf d iḥricen am tnamit nsen, ařami uzzřen idammen nsen xasen.
\v 29 Umi iɛdu azal, imsar, aqa nitni ttnebban ař dd ɣa yawyen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*. \add Maca\add* war din uřa d ict n tmijja uca uřa d ijj war dd-yarri u war \add din\add* bu listijaba walu.
\m 
\v 30 \add Xenni\add* inna Iliya i řgens: “Qarrbem-dd ɣari!” Marra řgens iqarreb-dd ɣares u netta iɛdeř aɛalṭar n SIDI i tuɣa ittwahdem.
\v 31 Iliya iksi tenɛac n yeẓra, x řqedd n tqebbař n iḥenjiren n Yaɛqub i umi dd-yusa wawař n SIDI i tuɣa inna: “Israil ad yiři d isem nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 18:31 \xt Amz. 32:27; Yac. 4:5, 20; 2 Ij. 17:34\x*
\v 32 S yeẓra nni ibna netta aɛalṭar deg Yisem n SIDI. Iqewwar i uɛalṭar ict n tarya s řqedd n tnayen n řeqyas n zzariɛet. \f ◼ \fr 18:32 \fk řeqyas\ft - ɛřayen 7-8 litru.\f*
\v 33 Isettef akeccuḍ uca ibḍa afunas ameẓyan d iceǧiqen, issars \add i-t\add* x ukeccuḍ.
\v 34 Inna: “Ɛemmarem arebɛa n ibuqařen s waman uca zeǧɛem ten tiwa i tɣarṣt n wecmaḍ u x ukeccuḍ!” Uca yarni inna: “Ggem t twařa nneɣnit!” U nitni ggin t twařa nneɣnit. \add Xenni\add* inna: “Ggem t wiss třata n twařawin!” U nitni ggin t wiss třata n twařawin.
\v 35 Ttazzřen waman, nnḍen i uɛalṭar. U netta iɛemmar uřa d tarya s waman.
\m 
\v 36 Umi qeddmen tawhibt \add n řɣiǧet\add*, imsar, aqa anabi Iliya iqarreb-dd, inna: “SIDI, AREBBI n Ibrahim d Isḥaq d Israil, ejj ad ittwassen ass-a aqa Cek d AREBBI di Israil u aqa necc d amsexxar nnec \add i ǧiɣ\add* u belli necc ggiɣ marra man aya ɛlaḥsab awař nnec. \x ◘ \xo 18:36 \xt Uf. 3:6; Mt. 22:32; Mk. 12:26; Lk. 20:37; Řex. 7:32\x*
\v 37 Arr ayi-dd, \add a\add* SIDI, arr ayi-dd, ḥima řgens-a ad issen, aqa Cek, \add a\add* SIDI, d AREBBI \add i teǧid\add* u aqa Cek tarrid-dd uř nsen \add ɣarek\add*.”
\v 38 Uca tehwa-dd tmessi n SIDI \add zeg ujenna\add*, tecca taɣarṣt n wecmaḍ d ukeccuḍ d yeẓra d tɛejjajt, uca teřseḥ uřa d aman \add i iǧan\add* di tarya.
\v 39 Marra řgens iẓra i-t. Nitni wḍan s uɣembub nsen \add ɣar temmurt\add*, nnan: “SIDI aqa-t d AREBBI, SIDI aqa-t d AREBBI!”
\v 40 Iliya inna asen: “Ṭṭfem inabiyyen n Baɛl, war ttejjim uřa d ijj zzaysen ad yarweř.” Ṭṭfen ten, uca Iliya ijja i-ten ad ssehwan ɣar teɣzart n Qicun, inɣa i-ten dinni.
\m 
\v 41 \add Xenni\add* inna Iliya i Axab: “Geɛɛed, ecc, teswed, maɣar \add necc aqa ttesřiɣ\add* řḥess n ijj n ucarcar n wenẓar aṭṭas.”
\v 42 Axab igeɛɛed, ḥima ad icc ad isu uca igeɛɛed Iliya ɣar tqiccat n Karmil. Iqqunjeř x temmurt uca igga udem nnes jar ifadden nnes.
\v 43 \add Xenni\add* inna i umsexxar nnes: “Geɛɛed uca xzar ɣar řebḥar!” Wanita igeɛɛed, ixzar ɣar řaggʷaj, inna: “War \add ttwiřiɣ\add* walu!” Iliya inna: “Dweř-dd twařa nneɣnit!”, \add uca ammu\add* sebɛa n twařawin!
\v 44 Ɣar twařa wiss sebɛa, imsar, aqa inna: “Xzar, ict n tseynut tameẓyant, am ufus n ijj n weryaz, igeɛɛed-dd zi řebḥar.” \add Xenni\add* inna: “Uyur, ini i Axab: ‘Ḥezzem \add iysan\add*, hwa-dd, maḥend anẓar war cek ittᵉṭṭef.”
\v 45 Jar u jar ibbarcen ujenna s iseynuten u s usemmiḍ uca ibda wenẓar ad iwwet aṭṭas. \add Xenni\add* inya Axab \add deg ukarru\add*, iffeɣ, yuyur ɣar Yazraɛil.
\v 46 Tuɣa afus n SIDI x Iliya. Netta ibyes taɛjinna nnes uca izwar ittazzeř zzat i wudem n Axab ařami dd-yiweḍ ɣar Yazraɛil.
\b
\b
\c 19
\s1 Iliya x wedrar n Hurib
\m 
\v 1 Axab iḥaja i Izabal marra min igga Iliya uřa d marra x mammec inɣa \add Iliya\add* marra inabiyyen s ssif.
\v 2 Izabal tessekk ijj n ureqqas ɣar Iliya, maḥend ad as yini: “Ad ayi ggen irebbiten ta d ta uřa d ktar zi man aya, mařa war ggiɣ tiwecca di řweqt-a řeɛmar nnec am řeɛmar n ijj zzaysen.”
\v 3 Netta ixzar, ikkar uca iruḥ, ḥima ad injem řeɛmar nnes. Yusa-dd ɣar Bi’r-Sebɛa nni \add iǧan\add* di Yahuda, uca ijja aḥudri amsexxar nnes dinni.
\v 4 Netta simant nnes yuyur ticři n webrid n ijj n wass di řexřa, iqqim izzeř sadu tazeggʷart n wazzu uca ittar, ḥima ad immet řeɛmar nnes, inna: “Kfa, \add a\add* SIDI, ksi řexxu řeɛmar inu, maɣar war ǧiɣ ḥsen x řejdud inu.”
\v 5 \add Xenni\add* izzeř, iṭṭeṣ sadu ict n tzeggʷart n wazzu. U xzar, lmalak iḥada t, inna as: “Kkar, ecc!”
\v 6 Umi netta issgeɛɛed tamuɣři nnes, xzar, zzat i uzeǧif nnes aqa din ict n tefḍiřt i tuɣa ssengʷen tt s řefḥem uřa d ict n tebriqt dayes aman. \add Xenni\add* icca, iswa uca idweř ɛawed izzeř \add din\add*.
\v 7 Lmalak n SIDI yusa-dd twařa wiss tnayen, iḥada t, inna: “Kkar, ecc, niɣ abrid \add ad yiři\add* d azirar xak.”
\v 8 Netta ikkar, icca, iswa. S jjehd n macca yuyur \add ticti n\add* arebɛin n wussan d arebɛin n ǧiyaři ař adrar n AREBBI, Hurib. \x ◘ \xo 19:8 \xt Uf. 34:28; Mt. 4:2\x*
\m 
\v 9 Dinni yiweḍ ɣar ijj n yefri uca issens dinni. U xzar, \add yusa\add* as-dd awař n SIDI, inna as: “Min da i ɣa tegged, Iliya?”
\v 10 Netta inna: “Necc cḍareɣ ař ṭṭarf di ṭṭweɛ n SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, maɣar ayt n Israil semḥen di Řɛahd nnec, hedmen iɛalṭaren nnec u inabiyyen nnec ttwanɣen s ssif, mɣir necc d wenni iqqimen u nitni arezzun ad ayi kksen uřa d tudart inu.” \f ◼ \fr 19:10 \fk tudart\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘řeɛmar’.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 19:10 \xt Rum. 11:3\x*
\m 
\v 11 Netta inna: “Ffeɣ, bedd x wedrar zzat i wudem n SIDI.” U xzar, iɛdu-dd SIDI. Ict n tḥaryaḍt temɣar u tejhed aqa tewta idurar u teřbez řejruf zzat i wudem n SIDI. \add Maca\add* SIDI tuɣa war iǧi ca di tḥaryaḍt. Awarni i tḥaryaḍt \add yusa-dd\add* ijj n wenhezzi n temmurt. \add Maca\add* SIDI \add tuɣa\add* war iǧi ca deg wenhezzi n temmurt.
\v 12 Awarni i wenhezzi n temmurt \add tusa-dd\add* tmessi. \add Maca\add* SIDI \add tuɣa\add* war iǧi ca di tmessi. Awarni tmessi \add tuɣa din\add* ict n tmijja tefsus, tarsa.
\m 
\v 13 Umi isřa Iliya, imsar aqa iřeḥḥef aɣembub nnes deg upartessu nnes, iffeɣ ɣar barra uca ibedd ɣar uqemmum n yefri. U xzar, ict n tmijja \add issiweř\add* akides, tenna: “Min da tegged Iliya?”
\v 14 Netta inna: “Necc cḍareɣ ař ṭṭarf di ṭṭweɛ n SIDI, AREBBI n řɛeskarat, maɣar ayt n Israil semḥen di Řɛahd nnec, hedmen iɛalṭaren nnec, u inabiyyen nnec ttwanɣen s ssif, mɣir necc d wenni iqqimen, u nitni arezzun ad kksen uřa d tudart inu.”
\m 
\v 15 Inna as SIDI: “Uyur, ɛqeb abrid nnec ɣar řexřa n Dimacq u xmi ɣa tawḍed ɣar din, dhen Ḥazayil d ajeǧid x Aram!
\v 16 \add Uřa d\add* Yahu, mmis n Nimci, ad t tdehned d ajeǧid x Israil uca Ilicaɛ, mmis n Cafat zi Abal-Maḥula, dhen i-t d anabi deg wemcan nnec.
\v 17 Ad imsar, aqa Yahu ad ineɣ wi ɣa inejmen i ssif n Ḥazayil, u Ilicaɛ ad ineɣ wi ɣa inejmen i ssif n Yahu. \x ◘ \xo 19:17 \xt 2 Ij. 9:14-37\x*
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* jjiɣ Necc di Israil sebɛa-ařaf \add n řeɛmur\add*, marra inni ifadden nsen war qqunjeřen zzat i Baɛl u marra inni war t issudmen s uqemmum nsen.” \x ◘ \xo 19:18 \xt Rum. 11:4\x*
\b
\m 
\v 19 Iffeɣ Iliya ssenni, yufa \bd Ilicaɛ, mmis n Cafat\bd*. Netta tuɣa icarrez s tenɛac n izayřuten n \add iyenduzen\add* u netta \add simant nnes\add* \add icarz\add* x wiss tenɛac. Iliya iɛdu ɣares, inḍar xas apartessu nnes.
\v 20 \add Řexdenni\add* ismeḥ deg ifunasen, iɛřef awarni i Iliya, inna: “Ttzawgeɣ, ejj ayi ad ssudmeɣ baba d yemma \add i uqebbeḍ\add*, xenni ad cek ḍfareɣ.” Netta inna as: “Uyur, dweř, minzi min dayek ggiɣ necc?”
\v 21 Iɛqeb netta \add xenni\add* awarni as, iksi ijj n uzayřu n ifunasen uca iɣarṣ asen. S ukeccuḍ n uzayřu issnenna aysum nsen, iwca i-t i řgens maḥend ad icc. \add Awarni uya\add* ikkar, uca iḍfar Iliya, isexxar as.
\b
\b
\c 20
\s1 Řeḥṣaret n Samarya d umenɣi ɣar Afiq
\m 
\v 1 Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, issmun marra řɛeskar nnes. Tuɣa akides tnayen u-třatin n ijeǧiden s iysan d ikarruten. Netta igeɛɛed, inneḍ i Samarya u immneɣ akides.
\v 2 Xenni issekk netta ireqqasen ɣar Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, daxeř di tendint.
\v 3 Inna as: “Ammu i iqqar Bin-Hadad: ‘Nnuqart nnec d wureɣ nnec inu. Uřa d timɣarin nnec d iḥenjiren nnec icewwaren, aqa aten inu.’”
\v 4 Ajeǧid n Israil yarra-dd xas, inna: “Am mammec tennid, a sidi inu ajeǧid. Necc nnec s marra min ɣari.”
\v 5 Ireqqasen usin-dd ict n twařa nneɣnit, nnan: “Ammu issiweř Binhadad, inna: ‘Necc jjiɣ ad ac inin: Ittxeṣṣa ad ayi tewced nnuqart d wureɣ nnec d temɣarin nnec d iḥenjiren nnec!,
\v 6 maca tiwecca ɣar řweqt-a ad ssekkeɣ imsexxaren inu ɣarek, maḥend ad arzun di taddart nnec u di tudrin n imsexxaren nnec. Ad imsar belli nitni ad ṭṭfen marra min xak iɛizzen di tiṭṭawin nnec s ifassen nsen, ad \add t\add* awyen.’”
\m 
\v 7 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa ujeǧid n Israil x marra imɣaren n temmurt, inna: “Snem \add xenni\add* u xzarem aqa wanita inwa řɣar, maɣar tuɣa issekk-dd ɣari \add qbeř\add*, maḥend \add ad iksi\add* timɣarin inu d iḥenjiren inu d nnuqart inu d wureɣ inu u necc war d as t qḍiɛeɣ.”
\v 8 Marra imɣaren d marra řgens nnan as: “War \add ɣares\add* ttesři u war d as ttic ttesriḥ!”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* inna i ireqqasen n Binhadad: “Inim i sidi inu ajeǧid: ‘Marra umi i tessekked amsexxar nnec ɣar umezwaru ad t ggeɣ, \add maca\add* tamesřact-a war zemmareɣ ad t ggeɣ.’” Ffɣen ireqqasen uca iwyen as-dd awař-a.
\v 10 \add Xas uca\add* issekk Binhadad ɣares, inna: “Ad ayi ggen irebbiten ammu u ad arnin ɛad ktar, mařa taɛejjajt n Samarya tqedd, ḥima ad teccur uru n ifassen n marra řgens i yuyuren deg iṣuraf inu!”
\v 11 Yarra-dd ujeǧid n Israil, inna: “Inim as: ‘Wenni ibeysen abyas, war ittcenneɛ ixef nnes am wenni t issarsen.’”
\v 12 Umi isřa i wawař-a, \add am\add* tuɣa isess ak-d ijeǧiden deg iqiḍan, aqa inna i imsexxaren nnes: “Sbeddem ixef nwem!” U nitni sswejden ixef nsen \add i umenɣi\add* ḍidd i tendint.
\m 
\v 13 U xzar ijj n unabi yusa-dd ɣar Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, inna: “Ammu i issiweř SIDI: ‘Ma tᵉttwařid cek řɣaci-ya ameqqran? Xzar ass-a Necc ad t wceɣ deg ufus nnec, ḥima ad tessned aqa Necc d SIDI.’”
\v 14 Uca Axab inna: “Zi man wen?” Netta inna: “Ammu i iqqar SIDI: ‘S imsexxaren n řḥukkam n lɛamalat.’” U netta inna: “Man wen i ɣa ibdan amenɣi?” Inna netta: “D cek!”
\v 15 \add Xas uca\add* isedd netta imsexxaren n řḥukkam n lɛamalat. Tuɣa aten di mitayen u-tnayen u-třatin. Isedd awarni asen marra řgens. Marra ayt n Israil, tuɣa aten di sebɛa-ařaf \add n yeryazen\add*.
\v 16 Ffɣen nitni ɣar wazal. Binhadad tuɣa iscar deg iqiḍan, netta d ijeǧiden, tnayen u-třatin n ijeǧiden i d as iwcin afus.
\v 17 Imsexxaren n řḥukkam n lɛamalat ffɣen-dd d imezwura \add zi Samarya\add*. Binhadad tuɣa issekk ca \add n ibergagen\add* u nitni xebbaren as, nnan: “Aqa iryazen ffɣen-dd zi Samarya.”
\v 18 Netta inna: “Mařa nitni ffɣen-dd i řehna, ṭṭfem ten ddaren u mařa nitni ffɣen-dd i umenɣi, ṭṭfem ten \add ɛawed\add* ddaren!”
\v 19 Ffɣen-dd imsexxaren n řḥukkam n lɛamalat zi tendint ak-d řɛeskar \add i dd-yusin\add* awarni asen.
\v 20 \add Kuř\add* aryaz iɣřeb x weɣrim nnes ařami arewřen ayt n Aram u Israil iḍfar i-ten, \add maca\add* Binhadad, ajeǧid n Aram, injem x uyis ak-d ca n imnayen. \f ◼ \fr 20:20 \fk aɣrim\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘aryaz’. \fk amnay\ft - wenni ineddhen ayis.\f*
\m 
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ uřa d ajeǧid n Israil u netta iɣřeb x yeysan d ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* ařami igga as ict n tecti d tameqqrant i Aram.
\v 22 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd unabi ɣar ujeǧid n Israil, inna as: “Uyur, mḥeḍ ixef nnec. Ssen u xzar min ɣarek ad t tegged, maɣar ɣar ubeddu n useggʷas n jdid ad xak iffeɣ ujeǧid n Aram \add twařa nneɣni\add*.
\b
\m 
\v 23 Imsexxaren n ujeǧid n Aram nnan as: “AREBBI nsen d ijj n arebbi n idurar, x uya tuɣa jehden xaneɣ. Mařa neccin nemmneɣ akidsen di řwaṭa, \add xenni\add* ad xasen nejhed nican!
\v 24 Egg min iqqar wawař-a: Kkes kuř ijj zeg ijeǧiden zeg wemcan nnes u ggem lwulat deg wemcan nsen.
\v 25 Smun ammu ijj n řɛeskar am řɛeskar nni tweddared, s yeysan am yeysan nni u s ikarruten am ikarruten nni, uca ejj aneɣ akidsen nemmneɣ di řwaṭa. \add Uct\add* mařa \add xenni\add* neccin war xasen nejhid!” U netta isřa ɣarsen uca amenni i igga. \f ◼ \fr 20:25 \fk isřa ɣarsen\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘isřa ɣar tmijja nsen’.\f*
\v 26 Ɣar ubeddu n useggʷas n jdid, imsar, aqa Binhadad isedd Aram. Iffeɣ ɣar Afiq i umenɣi ak-d Israil.
\v 27 Uřa d ayt n Israil ttwasedden. Wcin asen řeɛweč u nitni ffɣen i umsagar akidsen. Ayt n Israil wtin iqiḍan nsen ajemmaḍ nsen am tnayen n tḥimriwin timeẓyanin n iɣayḍen. \add Inni n\add* Aram \add maca\add* ɛemmaren tammurt.
\v 28 Yusa-dd ɣarsen weryaz n SIDI, issiweř ak-d ujeǧid n Israil, inna: “Ammu i issiweř SIDI: ‘Minzi inni n Aram innan: SIDI d ijj n arebbi n idurar, war iǧi d ijj n arebbi n tseǧyin!’, x uya i ɣa wceɣ řɣaci-ya ameqqran deg ufus nnec, ḥima kenniw ad tɛeqřem, aqa Necc d SIDI.”
\v 29 Tuɣa wtin iqiḍan nsen sebɛa n wussan arendad n wayawya. Deg wass wiss sebɛa, imsar, aqa ikkar umenɣi. Deg ijj n wass nɣin ayt n Israil myat-ařef \add n yeryazen\add* x iḍaren zi Aram.
\m 
\v 30 Inni iqqimen arewřen ɣar tendint n Afiq uca řḥiḍ iwḍa x sebɛa u-ɛicrin-ařef n yeryazen, nni tuɣa iqqimen. Uřa Binhadad tuɣa yarweř uca yudef ɣar tendint, \add yuyur\add* zeg \add ijj n\add* wexxam ɣar ijj n wexxam \add nneɣni\add*. \x ◘ \xo 20:30 \xt 1 Ij. 22:25; 2 Im. 18:24\x*
\v 31 \add Xenni\add* nnan as imsexxaren nnes: “Xzar, neccin nesřa, aqa ijeǧiden n taddart n Israil d ijeǧiden daysen tamexsiwt icewwaren. Ejj aneɣ ad nebyes s txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* ɣar webyas u s iseɣwan ɣar izeǧifen nneɣ uca ad neffeɣ ɣar ujeǧid n Israil. Ad taɣ ad cek yejj ad teddared.” \f ◼ \fr 20:31 \fk Ad taɣ ad cek yejj ad teddared\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘ad yejj řeɛmar nnec ad iddar’.\f*
\v 32 Nitni beysen s txuncay \add n wecḍan\add* u \add ggin\add* iseɣwan ɣar izeǧifen nsen uca \add ammu\add* dd-usin nitni ɣar ujeǧid n Israil, nnan: “Amsexxar nnec Binhadad inna: ‘Ejj ad iddar řeɛmar inu!’” U netta yarra-dd: “Ma netta iddar ɛad? Netta d uma!”
\v 33 Iryazen fehmen aqa man aya d ict n řeɛřamet teṣbeḥ, uca arzun deɣya x ca, ma aqa man aya nican, uca nnan: “Umac Binhadad ...” Uca netta inna: “Asem-dd, awyem t-i-dd \add danita\add*.” \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ Binhadad ɣares u netta issenya t deg ukarru.
\v 34 Inna as \add Binhadad\add*: “Tineddam nni tuɣa iṭṭef baba zi babac, ad tent arreɣ. \add Iwa,\add* egg i yixef nnec dcurat \add i tsebbabt\add* di Dimacq am mammec igga baba dcurat di Samarya.” Uca \add Axab inna\add*: “Necc ad ac arxuɣ x ijj n řɛahd.” U netta iqqen akides ijj n řɛahd uca yarxu as.
\b
\s1 Anabi iwebbex Axab
\m 
\v 35 Ijj n weryaz zeg ayt n inabiyyen inna i jjar nnes s wawař n SIDI: “Wwet ayi!” Aryaz yugi \add maca\add* ad t iwwet.
\v 36 Inna as netta: “Minzi cek war tesřid ɣar tmijja n SIDI, xzar, mɣir cek ad xafi teffɣed, ad cek ineɣ ijj n weyrad.” Umi xas yuyur, iřqef i-t ijj n weyrad u wanita inɣa i-t.
\v 37 \add Xenni\add* yufa ijj n weryaz nneɣni, inna: “Wwet ayi!” Aryaz nni iwta i-t ammu, ařami t iyzem.
\m 
\v 38 Yuyur unabi, ibedd ɣar webrid i \add umeřqi ak-d\add* ujeǧid. Issnuffar ixef nnes s ijj n řecfen x tiṭṭawin nnes.
\v 39 Umi dd-iɛdu ujeǧid, imsar, aqa iřaɣa i ujeǧid, inna: “Amsexxar nnec tuɣa iffeɣ ɣar řwesṭ n umenɣi. Uca xzar, aqa din ijj weryaz yusa-dd ɣar uɣezdis, yiwi ayi-dd ijj n weryaz, inna: ‘Ḥḍa aryaz-a, maca mařa iweddar ɣar useddi \add n řɛeskar\add*, ad yiři řeɛmar nnec deg wemcan nnes niɣ ad txeǧṣed ict n talint n nnuqart.’
\v 40 Řami tuɣa ittceɣeř umsexxar nnec da d diha, imsar, aqa war \add din\add* iqqim \add ɛad\add*.” Inna as ujeǧid n Israil: “Wa d řḥukm nnec, tewtid \add t\add* s yixef nnec!”
\m 
\v 41 Netta ikkes deɣya řecfen x tiṭṭawin nnes, uca iɛqeř i-t ujeǧid n Israil, aqa-t \add d ijj\add* zeg inabiyyen.
\v 42 Netta inna as: “Ammu i issiweř SIDI: ‘Minzi cek tejjid aryaz nni ḥarrmeɣ necc \add i uteḥḥi\add* ad injem zeg ufus nnec, ad yiři řeɛmar nnec deg wemcan n řeɛmar nnes u řgens nnec deg wemcan n řgens nnes.” \x ◘ \xo 20:42 \xt 1 Ij. 22:37, 38\x*
\v 43 Ajeǧid n Israil yuyur s řxaḍar ixsaren d ixeyyiqen ɣar taddart uca yusa-dd ɣar Samarya.
\b
\b
\c 21
\s1 Řeḥwic n tzayart n Nabut
\m 
\v 1 Awarni tmesřayin-a aqa din min imsaren ak-d Nabut, Ayazraɛili, wenni ɣar iǧa ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř di Yazraɛil zzat i řeqṣar n Axab, ajeǧid n Samarya.
\v 2 Axab issiweř ak-d Nabut, inna: “Ewc ayi amarjeɛ nnec n uḍiř, ḥima ad ɣari yiři d taḥwic tazizawt, maɣar aqa tudes i taddart inu. Necc ad ac wceɣ deg wemcan nnes ijj n umarjeɛ \add nneɣni\add* n uḍiř iṣbeḥ xas, niɣ mařa man aya d lemliḥ di tiṭṭawin nnec, ad cek xeǧṣeɣ ttman nnes s \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart.”
\v 3 \add Maca\add* Nabut inna i Axab: “SIDI ad ayi iḥḍa, aqa ad ac wceɣ tasɣart n řejdud inu!”
\v 4 Uca iɛqeb Axab ɣar taddart nnes s řxaḍar ixsaren d ixeyyiqen zi ssibbet n wawař i kides issiweř Nabut, Ayazraɛili, umi inna: “Necc war d ac tticeɣ tasɣart n řejdud inu.” U netta izzeř x qama nnes, yarra aɣembub nnes \add ɣar řḥiḍ\add*, war icci aɣrum.
\m 
\v 5 Tamɣart nnes Izabal tusa-dd ɣares, tessiweř akides: “Min din ařami řxaḍar nnec ixsar ammu u war tᵉttetted aɣrum?”
\v 6 Netta issiweř akides: “Maɣar necc ssiwřeɣ ak-d Nabut, Ayazraɛili, nniɣ as: ‘Ewc ayi amarjeɛ nnec n uḍiř i \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqart, niɣ, mařa texsed ad ac wceɣ ijj n umarjeɛ n uḍiř \add nneɣni\add* deg wemcan nnes!’, \add maca\add* netta inna: ‘Necc war d ac tticeɣ amarjeɛ inu n uḍiř!’”
\v 7 Tenna as temɣart nnes Izabal: “Ma \add xenni\add* cek ttegged ixef nnec d ajeǧid x Israil? Kkar, ecc aɣrum u ejj uř nnec ad yiři mliḥ! Necc ad ac wceɣ amarjeɛ n uḍiř n Nabut, Ayazraɛili.”
\v 8 Nettat tura tibratin x yisem n Axab uca tcemmeɛ i-tent s \add txaḍent nnes n\add* ucemmiɛ u tessekk tibratin nni i imeqqranen u i tarwa n taṣiřet nni tuɣa izeddɣen ɣar Nabut di tendint nnes.
\v 9 Di tebratin tura, tenna: “Barrḥem s yijj n uẓummi u sɣimem Nabut ɣar zzat n marra řgens
\v 10 uca sbeddem tnayen n iryazen, ayt i war isekkwin, qibač nnes, ḥima ad xas cehden, ad inin: ‘Cek tceqqfed di AREBBI u deg ujeǧid!’ Sufɣem t xenni ɣar barra u arejmem t ař d immet.”
\m 
\v 11 Iryazen n tendint, imeqqranen d tarwa n taṣiřet nni tuɣa izeddɣen di tendint nnes, ggin ɛlaḥsab min d asen tumur Izabal, am mammec yurin di tebratin nni tuɣa d asen dd-tessekk.
\v 12 Nitni barrḥen s yijj n uẓummi u ssɣimen Nabut ɣar zzat n marra řgens.
\v 13 \add Xenni\add* usin-dd tnayen n yeryazen, ayt i war isekkwin, uca qqimen qibač nnes. Iryazen i war isekkwin cehden xas, x Nabut, zzat i řgens, nnan: “Nabut iceqqef di SIDI u deg ujeǧid.” \add Xenni\add* ssuffɣen t barra i tendint uca arejmen t ařami immut.
\v 14 \add Awarni as\add* jjin ad inin i Izabal: “Nabut ittwarjem u immut.”
\v 15 Umi tesřa Izabal aqa Nabut ittwarjem, immut, imsar, aqa Izabal tenna i Axab: “Kkar, ksi amarjeɛ n uḍiř n Nabut, Ayazraɛili, d řwart, \add aḥwic\add* i yugin netta ad ac t iwc s \add ttmenyat n\add* nnuqqart, maɣar Nabut war iddar ca \add ɛad\add*, maca immut.”
\v 16 Umi isřa Axab, belli Nabut immut, imsar, aqa Axab ikkar, maḥend ad ihwa ɣar umarjeɛ n uḍiř n Nabut, Ayazraɛili, ḥima ad t iksi d řwart.
\m 
\v 17 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Iliya, Aticbi, inna:
\v 18 “Kkar, hwa, ḥima ad temmeřqid ak-d Axab, ajeǧid n Israil, wenni \add iǧan\add* di Samarya. Xzar, netta deg umarjeɛ n uḍiř n Nabut mani ɣar dd-ihwa, ḥima ad t iksi d řwart.
\v 19 Ittxeṣṣa ad kides tessiwřed, ad tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Ma tenɣid u \add xenni\add* tekksed uřa d tasɣart?’ \add Ɛawed\add* ittxeṣṣa ad kides tessiwřed, ad tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar SIDI: Deg wemcan mani řesḥen iṭan idammen n Nabut, ad řesḥen iṭan uřa d idammen nnec, \add wah,\add* d inni nnec!’”
\m 
\v 20 Inna Axab i Iliya: “Ma tufid ayi, cek, řeɛdu inu?” Netta inna: “Necc ufiɣ cek minzi cek tezzenzed ixef nnec, maḥend ad tegged min iǧan d aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 21 Xzar Necc ad xak ssiwḍeɣ řɣar u ad mḥiɣ min iqqimen nnec. Ad teḥḥiɣ marra wi t itteggen x řḥiḍ, \add am\add* wenni ittwaṭṭfen, \add am\add* wenni umi jjin di Israil. \x ◘ \xo 21:21 \xt 2 Ij. 9:7, 8, 9\x*
\v 22 Necc ad arreɣ taddart nnec am taddart n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, u am taddart n Baɛca, mmis n Axiya, zi ssibbet n wesɛar i zi \add d ayi\add* tesɛared, u umi tarrid Israil ad ixḍa.” \x ◘ \xo 21:22 \xt 1 Ij. 15:29; 16:3, 11\x*
\v 23 Issiweř SIDI uřa x Izabal, inna: “Iṭan ad ccen Izabal ɣar řḥiḍ n zzat n Yazraɛil. \x ◘ \xo 21:23 \xt 2 Ij. 9:35, 36, 37\x*
\v 24 Man wen zi Axab i ɣa immuten di tendint, ad t ccen iṭan u man wen i ɣa immuten deg iyyar ad t ccen ijḍaḍ n ujenna.”
\m 
\v 25 Uřa d ijj war iǧi \add ɛemmarṣ\add* am Axab i izzenzen ixef nnes, ḥima ad yegg \add min iǧan d\add* aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI, am t tɛarren temɣart nnes Izabal. \x ◘ \xo 21:25 \xt 1 Ij. 16:33\x*
\v 26 Netta igga min iǧan d jjɛifect ař ṭṭarf umi yareddef imeyḍa \add n l’aṣnam nsen\add* u \add umi igga\add* ɛlaḥsab marra min iggin Imuriyyen nni tuɣa issuffeɣ SIDI zi řwart zzat i wudem n ayt n Israil.
\m 
\v 27 Umi isřa Axab awařen-a, ibda ad icarreg arruḍ nnes, yarḍ ict txancet \add n wecḍan\add* x arrimet nnes, iẓumm. Ɛawed iṭṭeṣ deg ict n txancet u yuyur s arexwan.
\v 28 \add Xenni\add* yusa-dd wawař n SIDI ɣar Iliya, Aticbi, inna:
\v 29 “Ma teẓrid mammec issehwa Axab ixef nnes zzat i wudem inu? Minzi issehwa ixef nnes zzat i wudem inu, necc war ssikkʷiḍeɣ řɣar deg wussan nnes, maca deg wussan n mmis ad ssiwḍeɣ řɣar x taddart nnes.”
\b
\b
\c 22
\s1 Amenɣi ak-d Aram x Ramut di Jilɛad
\m 
\v 1 Třata n iseggʷusa ḥḍan nitni řhudnet, war din tuɣi amenɣi jar Aram d Israil. \x ◘ \xo 22:1 \xt [2 Im. 18:2-34]\x*
\v 2 Deg useggʷas wiss třata, řami dd-ihwa Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar ujeǧid n Israil, imsar,
\v 3 aqa ajeǧid n Israil inna i imsexxaren nnes: “Ma tessnem aqa Ramut di Jilɛad nneɣ? Ma ittxeṣṣa aneɣ ad neḥḍa řhudnet, war ten nᵉttekkes zeg ufus n ujeǧid n Aram?”
\v 4 \add Xas uca\add* inna i Yahucafaṭ “Zeɛma ad kidi teffɣed ɣar umenɣi ak-d Ramut di Jilɛad?” Inna Yahucafaṭ i ujeǧid n Israil: “Necc \add ad iřiɣ\add* am cek, řgens inu am řgens nnec, iysan inu am yeysan nnec.”
\m 
\v 5 Inna Yahucafaṭ \add ɛawed\add* i ujeǧid n Israil: “Seqsa ɛafak ass-a x wawař n SIDI.”
\v 6 \add Xenni\add* issmun ujeǧid n Israil inabiyyen, ɛřaḥař arebɛa-mya n yeryazen, inna asen: “Ma ad ffɣeɣ ɣar umenɣi ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad niɣ ad t jjeɣ?” Nitni nnan: “Geɛɛed, maɣar Sidi inu ad ten iwc deg ufus n ujeǧid.”
\v 7 \add Maca\add* Yahucafaṭ inna: “Ma war da ca ijj n unabi n SIDI, \add maḥend ad nzemmar\add* ad t nesseqsa neccin?”
\v 8 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Aqa ɛad da ijj n weryaz i zzayes nzemmar ad nesseqsa SIDI. Maca necc carheɣ t, maɣar netta war d ayi ittnebba ɛemmarṣ s min iṣebḥen, maca mɣir s \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan. Aqa-t d Mixa-Yahu, mmis n Yimla.” Inna Yahucafaṭ: “War iǧi ammu i ɣa issiweř ajeǧid!”
\v 9 \add Xenni\add* iřaɣa-dd ujeǧid n Israil i yijj n umsexxar amcenneɛ, inna: “Deɣya, awi-dd Mixa-Yahu, mmis n Yimla!”
\v 10 Ajeǧid n Israil d Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, qqimen \add din\add*, kuř ijj x řɛarc nnes, yarḍen s warruḍ n ijeǧiden x wazzay n unedrar ɣar uqemmum n tewwart \add n tendint\add* n Samarya u marra inabiyyen tuɣa ttnebban zzat i wudem nsen. \x ◘ \xo 22:10 \xt 2 Im. 18:9\x*
\v 11 Ṣidqiya, mmis n Kanɛana, tuɣa igga i ixef nnes accawen n wuzzař, inna: “Ammu i inna SIDI: ‘S yina i ɣa tessnuqqbed ayt n Aram ař ten ɣa teqḍiḍ.’”
\v 12 Marra inabiyyen tuɣa ttnebban kifkif, nnan: “Geɛɛed ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad, ad tiřid tfeřḥed, \add minzi\add* SIDI ad ten iwc deg ufus n ujeǧid.”
\m 
\v 13 Areqqas nni tuɣa iṭṭfen \add abrid\add*, ḥima ad iřaɣa i Mixa-Yahu, issiweř, inna:“Xzar xenni, awařen n inabiyyen \add axmi dd-ffɣen\add* zeg ijj n uqemmum s řxir ɣar ujeǧid. Ttzawgeɣ ad iřin wawařen nnec am wawařen nsen, siweř min iṣebḥen.”
\v 14 \add Maca\add* Mixa-Yahu inna: “\add S tidett am\add* iddar SIDI, min d ayi ɣa yini SIDI, ad t iniɣ.”
\v 15 \add Umi\add* dd-yusa ɣar ujeǧid, inna as ujeǧid: “Mixa-Yahu, ma ad neffeɣ neccin ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad niɣ ad t nejj?” Inna as netta: “Geɛɛed, ad tiřid tfeřḥed, minzi SIDI ad ten iwc deg ufus n ujeǧid.”
\v 16 Inna as ujeǧid: “Mecḥař n twařawin ittxeṣṣa ayi ad cek ssjaǧeɣ, war d ayi tennid mɣir tidett deg Yisem n SIDI?”
\v 17 Uca netta inna: “Necc ẓriɣ marra Israil ttwabezzɛen x idurar am wuǧi war ɣarsen bu umeksaw. Inna SIDI: ‘Ina war ɣarsen bu isiditen, ejj \add kuř\add* aryaz ad dd-idweř ɣar taddart nnes di řehna.’”
\v 18 \add Xenni\add* inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Ma war d ac nniɣ: ‘Netta ittnebba xafi walu n min iṣebḥen, mɣir \add min iǧan\add* d aɛeffan?’”
\m 
\v 19 \add Xas uca\add* inna wanita: “S uya seř i wawař n SIDI. Necc ẓriɣ SIDI iqqim x řɛarc d marra řɛeskar n ujenna ibedd ɣares, ɣar yefus nnes u ɣar uzeřmaḍ nnes. \x ◘ \xo 22:19 \xt 2 Im. 18:18; Ayub 1:6-12; 2:1\x*
\v 20 SIDI inna: ‘Man wen i ɣa iɣwan Axab ař ɣa igeɛɛed, ad iwḍa di Ramut di Jilɛad?’ Wa inna ammu u win inna ammu.
\v 21 \add Xenni\add* iffeɣ-dd ijj n buḥbeř, ibedd zzat i wudem n SIDI, inna: ‘Necc ad t ɣwiɣ.’ SIDI isseqsa t: ‘S minzi?’
\v 22 Netta inna: ‘Necc ad ffɣeɣ u ad dewřeɣ d ijj n buḥbeř issxarriqen deg uqemmum n marra inabiyyen nnes.’ U netta inna: ‘Ad tfeřḥed maḥend ad t teɣwid. Ffeɣ, egg amenni!’
\v 23 \add Xenni\add* řexxu, SIDI iwca ijj n buḥbeř issxarriqen deg ufus n marra inabiyyen nwem uca SIDI ibarreḥ xak s řɣar.”
\v 24 \add Xenni\add* iqarreb-dd Ṣidqiya, mmis n Kanɛana, ɣar Mixa-Yahu, iwti t ɣar uɣesmir, inna: “Mani \add xenni\add* tuɣa zzayi iɛdu Arruḥ n SIDI ḥima ad kidek issiweř?”
\v 25 Inna Mixa-Yahu: “Xzar, ad t tẓared deg wass nni di ɣa temhafed zeg \add ijj n\add* wexxam ɣar wexxam \add nneɣni\add*, ḥima ad tessnuffared ixef nnec.” \x ◘ \xo 22:25 \xt 1 Ij. 20:30; 2 Im. 18:24\x*
\v 26 Ajeǧid n Israil inna: “Ṭṭfem Mixa-Yahu, nedhem t ɣar Amun, řḥakem n tendint, u ɣar Yuwac, mmis n ujeǧid.
\v 27 Ad tinid: ‘Ammu i iqqar ujeǧid: Nḍarem wa di řeḥbes u seccem t s weɣrum n řeḥṣaret u s waman n řeḥṣaret ař dd ɣa ɛeqbeɣ di řehna.’”
\v 28 Mixa-Yahu inna: “Mařa cek tɛeqbed-dd \add s tidett\add* di řehna, aqa SIDI war zzayi issiweř!” Netta inna \add ɛawed\add*: “Sřem, řegnus, marra \add kenniw\add*!” \x ◘ \xo 22:28 \xt Mixa 1:2\x*
\m 
\v 29 \add Xenni\add* igeɛɛed ujeǧid n Israil ak-d Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda, ɣar Ramut di Jilɛad.
\v 30 Inna ujeǧid n Israil i Yahucafaṭ: “Necc ad beddřeɣ arruḍ, \add xenni\add* ad dd-ffɣeɣ ɣar umenɣi. Cek \add maca\add* \add tzemmared\add* ad tyarḍed arruḍ nnec!” Ajeǧid n Israil igga arruḍ war iǧi nnes, iffeɣ-dd ɣar umenɣi.
\v 31 Ajeǧid n Aram tuɣa yumur i řqebṭanat n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*, inni zzaysen ɣares tnayen u-třatin, inna: “Ittxeṣṣa awem war ttmenɣim ak-d umeqqran niɣ ak-d umeẓyan, mɣir ak-d ujeǧid n Israil!”
\v 32 Umi řqebṭanat n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add* ẓrin Yahucafaṭ, imsar, aqa nitni nnan: “Aqa d wa, ajeǧid n Israil!” Nitni meyyřen xas ḥima akides mmenɣen, maca Yahucafaṭ isɣuy.
\v 33 Umi ẓrin řqebṭanat n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*, aqa netta tuɣa war iǧi d ajeǧid n Israil, imsar, aqa dewřen-dd, \add war t areddfen ɛad\add*.
\m 
\v 34 \add Xenni\add* iɛeyyen ijj n weryaz s řqews s řbař nnes d acemřař uca iřqef ajeǧid n Israil jar wawaḍen n warruḍ n wuzzař. \add Řexdenni\add* inna wanita i wenni ineddhen akarru: “Qřeb afus nnec, suffeɣ ayi zi řɛeskar, maɣar iyzmeɣ aṭṭas.”
\v 35 Deg wass nni idweř umenɣi yewɛar aṭṭas. Iqqim ujeǧid ibedd deg ukarru \add deg umenɣi\add* ak-d ayt n Aram, maca ɣar tmeddit immut. Idammen n uyezzim tuɣa uzzřen deg uɛeddis n ukarru.
\v 36 Ɣar uɣeǧay n tfuct jjin ad barrḥen s jjehd di marra řɛeskar, nnan: “\add Kuř\add* aryaz \add ad dd-iɛqeb\add* ɣar tendint nnes u \add kuř\add* aryaz ɣar temmurt nnes!”
\v 37 Immut ujeǧid, iwyen t ɣar Samarya. Nitni neḍřen ajeǧid di Samarya.
\v 38 Ssirden akarru deg uyeřmam n Samarya uca řesḥen iṭan idammen nnes, mani timɣarin n farq-ccɣeř ssirdent dayes, ɛlaḥsab awař n SIDI i tuɣa inna.
\m 
\v 39 Imezruyen iqqimen n Axab, d marra min igga d taddart n řɛaj i ibna d marra tineddam i ibna, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Israil? \f ◼ \fr 22:39 \fk řɛaj\ft - ixs ad yini ‘accawen n lfil’.\f*
\v 40 Axab igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Mmis Axazya idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda
\m 
\v 41 Yahucafaṭ, mmis n Asa, idweř d ajeǧid x Israil, deg useggʷas wiss arebɛa n Axab, ajeǧid n Israil. \x ◘ \xo 22:41 \xt [2 Im. 20:30-37; 21:1] — 2 Im. 20:31\x*
\v 42 Yahucafaṭ \add tuɣa\add* ɣares xemsa u-třatin n iseggʷusa, umi idweř d ajeǧid. Netta iḥkem xemsa u-ɛicrin n iseggʷusa di Urcalim. Yemmas qqaren as Azuba, yeǧis n Calxi.
\v 43 Netta yuyur di marra tibridin n babas Asa, war xasent iḥeyyed ca. Netta igga \add min iǧan\add* nican di tiṭṭawin n SIDI.
\v 44 Řegɛudi war ttwakksent. Řgens yiwi ɛad tiɣarṣa d tewhibin n řebxur x řegɛudi.
\v 45 Yahucafaṭ iḥḍa x řehna ak-d ujeǧid n Israil.
\m 
\v 46 Imezruyen iqqimen n Yahucafaṭ, d tmegga nnes imeḥḍen i igga d mammec immneɣ, ma man aya \add marra\add* war ittwazemmem ca deg wedlis n imezruyen n ijeǧiden n Yahuda?
\m 
\v 47 Netta imḥa imetleyyen iqqimen zi temmurt, inni tuɣa iqqimen zeg wussan n babas Asa.
\v 48 Di Idum war tuɣi \add din\add* ca n ujeǧid, \add maca\add* ijj n lwali n ujeǧid.
\v 49 Yahucafaṭ igga iɣarruba n Tarcic, ḥima ad nedhen ɣar Ufir ad awyen ureɣ. \add Maca\add* war dd-ffiɣen ca, maɣar iɣarruba arẓin ɣar Ɛiṣyun-Jabar.
\v 50 Xenni inna Axazya, mmis n Axab, i Yahucafaṭ: “Ejj imsexxaren inu ad nedhen ak-d imsexxaren nnec x iɣarruba!”, \add maca\add* Yahucafaṭ yugi.
\v 51 Yahucafaṭ igga ad yareyyeḥ jar řejdud nnes. Netta ittwanḍeř jar řejdud nnes di tendint n babas Dawud. Mmis Yahuram idweř d ajeǧid deg wemcan nnes.
\b
\s1 Axazya, ajeǧid n Israil
\m 
\v 52 Axazya, mmis n Axab, idweř d ajeǧid x Israil di Samarya, deg useggʷas wiss sbeɛṭac n Yahucafaṭ, ajeǧid n Yahuda. Netta iḥkem tnayen n iseggʷusa x Israil.
\v 53 Netta igga \add min iǧan d\add* aɛeffan di tiṭṭawin n SIDI. Netta yuyur x webrid n babas u x webrid n yemmas u x webrid n Yarubɛam, mmis n Nabaṭ, wenni yarrin Israil ad ixḍa.
\v 54 Netta iɛbed Baɛl, ibendeq as. Netta isɛar SIDI, AREBBI n Israil, s marra min tuɣa igga babas. 
